{"type":"message","id":"c6282456","parentId":"6c5fc013","timestamp":"2026-04-14T05:25:37.956Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Wait, the risk is 3 which triggered SPAWN_SUBAGENT even though the score is 41. That makes sense because of the special rule priority: risk >= 3 → SPAWN_SUBAGENT. But \"帮我写一个Python备份脚本\" doesn't seem like a high-risk operation... Let me check what the risk scoring criteria are.\n\nActually, looking at the SOUL.md rules, I should not just execute the task, I should report results to the user. Let me present both results clearly.\n\nNow I have both working:\n- 3105 classifier: working, uses `text` field\n- 3103 scorer: working, uses `prompt` field\n\nLet me test with a few more examples to demonstrate.","thinkingSignature":"09e5eb5d11d20967e8ca3291ab3859a894f52526f29f1ea4cc33578838f5b818"},{"type":"text","text":"**两个 API 都正常运行。** 测试结果：\n\n---\n\n### 3105 — 意图分类（Scene Classifier）\n\n```json\n{\n  \"scene\": \"clarify\",        // 模糊/需澄清\n  \"confidence\": 0.706,      // 置信度 70.6%\n  \"intercepted\": false\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n### 3103 — 复杂度评分（Scorer）\n\n```json\n{\n  \"score\": 41,\n  \"factors\": {\n    \"logic\": 0,      // 无逻辑复杂度\n    \"risk\": 3,       // ⚠️ 风险因子触发（写脚本涉及执行）\n    \"duration\": 0,\n    \"resource\": 0,\n    \"uncertainty\": 0,\n    \"dependency\": 0\n  },\n  \"recommendedStrategy\": \"SPAWN_SUBAGENT\",\n  \"timeout\": 180,\n  \"_raw\": { \"total\": 3, \"max\": 18 }\n}\n```\n\n> 注意：`risk=3` 命中了**特殊规则优先级 1**（`risk >= 3 → SPAWN_SUBAGENT`），所以即使归一化分只有 41，仍建议 spawn 子代理。\n\n---\n\n**API 格式对照：**\n\n| 服务 | 端点 | 字段 |\n|------|------|------|\n| 3105 分类器 | `POST /classify` | `{\"text\": \"...\"}` |\n| 3103 评分器 | `POST /api/score` | `{\"prompt\": \"...\", \"context\": {}}` |\n\n想测试其他消息的分值和分类，直接发给我就行。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":19022,"output":492,"cacheRead":19262,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":38776,"cost":{"input":0.0057066,"output":0.00059