{"type":"message","id":"7c2e39d6","parentId":"8a878c5c","timestamp":"2026-04-14T05:28:49.672Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I have a clear picture. Let me check the actual running processes and identify the issue with the wiki-auto-learn. It seems like the cron is firing the wiki-learn job every hour, but the script is taking longer than an hour to complete (210 iterations with some sleep between each). The staggerMs is 300000 (5 minutes), so the cron should stagger but the underlying issue is the script runs too long.\n\nActually wait - the lastRunStatus is \"ok\" for wiki-learn, lastDurationMs is 26472 (26 seconds), which seems reasonable. But then why are there 6+ concurrent processes?\n\n\nLet me look at the session-summary and entities directories more carefully.","thinkingSignature":"8e542b4427ca412da7fcb105f2021023e08a7cc84aac1c9d8034d28b71c237f4"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_zek8veghwqgu_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# Find all session-summary directories\nfind /home/ai/.openclaw -name \"session-summary\" -type d 2>/dev/null\necho \"---\"\nfind /home/ai/.openclaw -name \"entities\" -type d 2>/dev/null\necho \"---\"\n# Check wiki-auto-learn processes (are they actually running or zombies?)\nps aux | grep wiki-auto-learn | grep -v grep | awk '{print $2, $8, $9, $10}'"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_zek8veghwqgu_2","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# Check the actual wiki-learn script\ncat /home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/scripts/wiki-auto-learn.py 2>/dev/null | head -60"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":25848,"output":316,"cacheRead":19262,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":45426,"cost":{"input":0.0077544,"output":0.0003792,"cacheRead":0.0011557199999999998,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00928932}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776144515999,"responseId":"062d03835f06aaa5fd031c4559ed6dbc"}}
{"type":"message","id":"b443bfc5","parentId":"7c2e39d6","timestamp":"2026-04-14T05:28:49.972Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_zek8veghwqgu_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"/home/ai/.openclaw/hooks/session-summary\n---\n/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/memory/entities\n---\n300477 Ss 06:41 0:00\n300479 S 06:41 0:00\n310527 Ss 07:44 0:00\n310528 S 07:44 0:00\n320538 Ss 08:47 0:00\n320539 S 08:47 0:00\n330558 Ss 09:50 0:00\n330559 S 09:50 0:00\n340548 Ss 10:53 0:00\n340549 S 10:53 0:00\n350557 Ss 11:56 0:00\n350558 S 11:56 0:00\n362126 Ss 12:58 0:00\n362127 S 12:58 0:00"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":265,"aggregated":"/home/ai/.openclaw/hooks/session-summary\n---\n/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/memory/entities\n---\n300477 Ss 06:41 0:00\n300479 S 06:41 0:00\n310527 Ss 07:44 0:00\n310528 S 07:44 0:00\n320538 Ss 08:47 0:00\n320539 S 08:47 0:00\n330558 Ss 09:50 0:00\n330559 S 09:50 0:00\n340548 Ss 10:53 0:00\n340549 S 10:53 0:00\n350557 Ss 11:56 0:00\n350558 S 11:56 0:00\n362126 Ss 12:58 0:00\n362127 S 12:58 0:00","cwd":"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/main"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1776144529963}}
{"type":"message","id":"ffffb1c2","parentId":"b443bfc5","timestamp":"2026-04-14T05:28:49.981Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_zek8veghwqgu_2","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"#!/usr/bin/env python3\n\"\"\"\nLLM Wiki Auto-Learning Framework\n高鲁棒、高质量、高性能自动化学习循环\n\n基于需求 + LLM Wiki 原文设计\n\"\"\"\n\nimport os\nimport time\nimport subprocess\nimport re\nfrom datetime import datetime\nfrom pathlib import Path\n\n# 配置\nWORKSPACE = \"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace\"\nENTITIES_DIR = f\"{WORKSPACE}/memory/entities\"\nRAW_SOURCES_DIR = f\"{WORKSPACE}/memory/raw\"\nLOG_FILE = f\"{WORKSPACE}/memory/log.md\"\nARCHIVE_DIR = f\"{WORKSPACE}/memory/entities-archive\"\n\n# LLM Wiki 原文核心要点\nCORE_PRINCIPLES = {\n    \"not_rag\": \"不是RAG，是增量构建持久wiki\",\n    \"compile_once\": \"知识编译一次，持续更新\",\n    \"touch_10_15\": \"一个source触发10-15页更新\",\n    \"maintenance_zero\": \"维护成本接近零\",\n    \"human_role\": \"人负责选源、提问、思考\",\n    \"llm_role\": \"LLM负责执行维护\",\n    \"query_writeback\": \"好答案写回wiki\",\n    \"memex\": \"LLM解决维护问题\"\n}\n\nclass WikiAutoLearn:\n    def __init__(self):\n        self.stats = {\n            \"iterations\": 0,\n            \"ingested\": 0,\n            \"fixed\": 0,\n            \"queries\": 0,\n            \"errors\": 0\n        }\n        \n    def log(self, msg):\n        \"\"\"带时间戳的日志\"\"\"\n        timestamp = datetime.now().strftime(\"%Y-%m-%d %H:%M:%S\")\n        print(f\"[{timestamp}] {msg}\")\n        \n    def scan_sources(self):\n        \"\"\"1. 扫描知识源 (Ingest)\"\"\"\n        sources = []\n        \n        # 扫描 docs/\n        docs_dir = Path(f\"{WORKSPACE}/docs\")\n        if docs_dir.exists():\n            for f in docs_dir.glob(\"*.md\"):\n                sources.append((\"doc\", str(f)))\n        \n        # 扫描 skills/"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":65,"aggregated":"#!/usr/bin/env python3\n\"\"\"\nLLM Wiki Auto-Learning Framework\n高鲁棒、高质量、高性能自动化学习循环\n\n基于需求 + LLM Wiki 原文设计\n\"\"\"\n\nimport os\nimport time\nimport subprocess\nimport re\nfrom datetime import datetime\nfrom pathlib import Path\n\n# 配置\nWORKSPACE = \"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace\"\nENTITIES_DIR = f\"{WORKSPACE}/memory/entities\"\nRAW_SOURCES_DIR = f\"{WORKSPACE}/memory/raw\"\nLOG_FILE = f\"{WORKSPACE}/memory/log.md\"\nARCHIVE_DIR = f\"{WORKSPACE}/memory/entities-archive\"\n\n# LLM Wiki 原文核心要点\nCORE_PRINCIPLES = {\n    \"not_rag\": \"不是RAG，是增量构建持久wiki\",\n    \"compile_once\": \"知识编译一次，持续更新\",\n    \"touch_10_15\": \"一个source触发10-15页更新\",\n    \"maintenance_zero\": \"维护成本接近零\",\n    \"human_role\": \"人负责选源、提问、思考\",\n    \"llm_role\": \"LLM负责执行维护\",\n    \"query_writeback\": \"好答案写回wiki\",\n    \"memex\": \"LLM解决维护问题\"\n}\n\nclass WikiAutoLearn:\n    def __init__(self):\n        self.stats = {\n            \"iterations\": 0,\n            \"ingested\": 0,\n            \"fixed\": 0,\n            \"queries\": 0,\n            \"errors\": 0\n        }\n        \n    def log(self, msg):\n        \"\"\"带时间戳的日志\"\"\"\n        timestamp = datetime.now().strftime(\"%Y-%m-%d %H:%M:%S\")\n        print(f\"[{timestamp}] {msg}\")\n        \n    def scan_sources(self):\n        \"\"\"1. 扫描知识源 (Ingest)\"\"\"\n        sources = []\n        \n        # 扫描 docs/\n        docs_dir = Path(f\"{WORKSPACE}/docs\")\n        if docs_dir.exists():\n            for f in docs_dir.glob(\"*.md\"):\n                sources.append((\"doc\", str(f)))\n        \n        # 扫描 skills/","cwd":"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/main"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1776144529972}}
{"type":"message","id":"666b71e0","parentId":"ffffb1c2","timestamp":"2026-04-14T05:29:05.000Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I see the problem clearly:\n\n1. **wiki-auto-learn processes**: There are 7 pairs (parent shell + python process) all running simultaneously, each from a different hour (06:41, 07:44, 08:47, 09:50, 10:53, 11:56, 12:58). These are cron-triggered processes that keep running. The script has 210 iterations and they're all still running. The `Ss` state means they're sleeping (waiting for I/O or sleep). The script seems to be designed to run a long time but keeps getting re-triggered by cron every hour. The processes are not completing because they have too many iterations to do in one hour.\n   \nLooking at the cron configuration, the `staggerMs` is set to 5 minutes, but the issue is that the script itself is too long-running—each invocation starts fresh and never finishes before the next one begins. The entities directory exists but is empty, which suggests the ingestion process isn't actually completing. Meanwhile, the session-summary hook directory is there, so I need to check why that pipeline isn't working either.\n\nThe memory-maintain job timed out after running for about 9.5 minutes, which is a separate issue. I'm also noticing a discrepancy between what MEMORY.md reported (31 entities as of April 13) and what I'm seeing now (0 entities), which could mean the directory was cleared or the count was inaccurate to begin with. I should focus on identifying the actual blockers rather than getting caught up in the numbers.","thinkingSignature":"ad66e393f727d13eb18d4feeb1f664408f441567bce1b770f69d636e773d25b3"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_g2dt94vmanja_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# Check entities count more carefully\nfind /home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/memory/entities -type f 2>/dev/null | wc -l\necho \"---\"\n# Check if there's a blocklist preventing ingestion\nls /home/ai/.openc