{"type":"message","id":"d5a07a91","parentId":"69c085d8","timestamp":"2026-04-14T05:58:41.614Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I see the issue now. The cron job for `wiki-learn` has:\n- `kind: \"agentTurn\"` \n- `message: \"执行 ~/.openclaw/workspace/scripts/wiki-learn-once.sh ...\"`\n- `sessionTarget: \"isolated\"`\n\nThis means the cron job spawns an **isolated agent session** to run `wiki-learn-once.sh`. This isolated session runs the script and the agent handles the output.\n\nBut there are also **multiple Python processes running directly** (`python3 scripts/wiki-auto-learn.py --mode=ingest --limit=3`). These are the processes that got pile-up.\n \nSo the cron is actually configured correctly to call the shell script, but it seems like someone may have manually started those Python processes directly, or there's another trigger somewhere spawning them outside the cron system. I should check the session history for `agent:main:main` to see what's been happening. Looking at the openclaw.json configuration, the cron job itself seems straightforward, but there's a mismatch between the `sessionTarget: \"isolated\"` setting and the fact that wiki processes are running as children of the sh wrapper - this suggests the isolated session might not be properly isolated, or the cron execution path is different than expected.","thinkingSignature":"5dff15848e17767b3671a75dfeacb6f60df489f3488a4acd90433fb6e202e680"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_knsainy1vszt_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# 检查实际在跑的 wiki-auto-learn 是怎么启动的\ncat /proc/300479/cmdline 2>/dev/null | tr '\\0' ' '\necho \"\"\ncat /proc/310528/cmdline 2>/dev/null | tr '\\0' ' '\necho \"\"\n# 检查 parent process\nps -o pid,ppid,etime,cmd --no-headers -p 300479 2>/dev/null"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_knsainy1vszt_2","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# 检查 wiki-learn-once.sh 存不存在\nls -la /home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/scripts/wiki-learn-once.sh 2>/dev/null\necho \"---\"\ncat /home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/scripts/wiki-learn-once.sh 2>/dev/null | head -40"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":29942,"output":448,"cacheRead":19262,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":49652,"cost":{"input":0.0089826,"output":0.0005376,"cacheRead":0.0011557199999999998,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.010675919999999998}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776146305260,"responseId":"062d0a80c770249d2a9dc06d6f152900"}}
{"type":"message","id":"ed54069b","parentId":"d5a07a91","timestamp":"2026-04-14T05:58:41.165Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_knsainy1vszt_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"python3 scripts/wiki-auto-learn.py --mode=ingest --limit=3\n\n(Command exited with code 1)"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":1,"durationMs":80,"aggregated":"python3 scripts/wiki-auto-learn.py --mode=ingest --limit=3\n\n(Command exited with code 1)","cwd":"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/main"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1776146321154}}
{"type":"message","id":"33f1ba76","parentId":"ed54069b","timestamp":"2026-04-14T05:58:41.177Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_knsainy1vszt_2","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"-rwxrwxr-x 1 ai ai 5304 Apr 13 19:52 /home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/scripts/wiki-learn-once.sh\n---\n#!/bin/bash\n# Wiki Auto-Learn 单次执行脚本\n# 配合 cron 使用，每小时触发一次\n#\n# 策略：\n#   1. 只摄入新 skill（不在 entities/ 且不在 blocklist/ 中）\n#   2. blocklist 防止被删的 entity 重复摄入\n#   3. 有空间才添加，超标才 prune\n\nWORKSPACE=\"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace\"\nENTITIES=\"$WORKSPACE/memory/entities\"\nRAW=\"$WORKSPACE/memory/raw\"\nLOG=\"$WORKSPACE/memory/log.md\"\nSKILLS_DIR=\"$WORKSPACE/skills\"\nARCHIVE=\"$WORKSPACE/memory/entities-archive\"\nBLOCKLIST=\"$WORKSPACE/memory/.wiki-learn-blocklist\"  # 被删除的 skill 名列表\n\nTARGET=28\nBUFFER=3\n\nmkdir -p \"$RAW/docs\" \"$RAW/papers\" \"$RAW/notes\" \"$ARCHIVE\"\n\necho \"[$(date '+%Y-%m-%d %H:%M:%S')] === wiki-learn-once 启动 ===\"\n\n# ===== 辅助：计算可丢弃分数（越小越先删）=====\ndisposability_score() {\n    local f=$1\n    local score\n    if grep -q \"status: auto-ingested\" \"$f\" 2>/dev/null; then\n        score=0\n    else\n        score=500\n    fi\n    local lines=$(wc -l < \"$f\")\n    echo $((score + lines))\n}\n\n# ===== 辅助：从 blocklist 加载已删除 skill 名（去重）=====\nload_blocklist() {\n    [ -f \"$BLOCKLIST\" ] && sort -u \"$BLOCKLIST\" || true"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":80,"aggregated":"-rwxrwxr-x 1 ai ai 5304 Apr 13 19:52 /home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/scripts/wiki-learn-once.sh\n---\n#!/bin/bash\n# Wiki Auto-Learn 单次执行脚本\n# 配合 cron 使用，每小时触发一次\n#\n# 策略：\n#   1. 只摄入新 skill（不在 entities/ 且不在 blocklist/ 中）\n#   2. blocklist 防止被删的 entity 重复摄入\n#   3. 有空间才添加，超标才 prune\n\nWORKSPACE=\"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace\"\nENTITIES=\"$WORKSPACE/memory/entities\"\nRAW=\"$WORKSPACE/memory/raw\"\nLOG=\"$WORKSPACE/memory/log.md\"\nSKILLS_DIR=\"$WORKSPACE/skills\"\nARCHIVE=\"$WORKSPACE/memory/entities-archive\"\nBLOCKLIST=\"$WORKSPACE/memory/.wiki-learn-blocklist\"  # 被删除的 skill 名列表\n\nTARGET=28\nBUFFER=3\n\nmkdir -p \"$RAW/docs\" \"$RAW/papers\" \"$RAW/notes\" \"$ARCHIVE\"\n\necho \"[$(date '+%Y-%m-%d %H:%M:%S')] === wiki-learn-once 启动 ===\"\n\n# ===== 辅助：计算可丢弃分数（越小越先删）=====\ndisposability_score() {\n    local f=$1\n    local score\n    if grep -q \"status: auto-ingested\" \"$f\" 2>/dev/null; then\n        score=0\n    else\n        score=500\n    fi\n    local lines=$(wc -l < \"$f\")\n    echo $((score + lines))\n}\n\n# ===== 辅助：从 blocklist 加载已删除 skill 名（去重）=====\nload_blocklist() {\n    [ -f \"$BLOCKLIST\" ] && sort -u \"$BLOCKLIST\" || true","cwd":"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/main"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1776146321165}}
{"type":"message","id":"a99ff109","parentId":"33f1ba76","timestamp":"2026-04-14T05:58:59.339Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I understand the full picture:\n\n1. The `wiki-learn` cron job in `jobs.json` is correctly configured to run an **isolated agentTurn** that calls `wiki-learn-once.sh`. This is working correctly.\n\n2. BUT there are also multiple `python3 scripts/wiki-auto-learn.py --mode=ingest --limit=3` processes running directly (not through cron). These are the ones piling up.\n\n3. The `wiki-auto-learn.py` is a long-running script (210 iterations), not the `wiki-learn-once.sh` which is a single-pass script.\n\nSo the question is: who started these `python3 scripts/wiki-auto-learn.py` processes?\n \nThe processes are running from the workspace directory and executing the Python script directly with the ingest flag. Looking at the session timestamps in the gateway log, these processes started around 06:41, 07:44, 08:47 and beyond, which corresponds to when the cron jobs would have been triggering.\n\nBut here's the issue—the cron job is configured to spawn an agent that runs `wiki-learn-once.sh`, not the Python script directly. So either someone ran these manually, or there's another mechanism triggering them that I haven't identified yet. Let me look for a systemd timer or another cron entry that might be responsible.","thinkingSignature":"785ecfcada9d954ab2745dec1a37f7342cc2a5d6227bb67c860816e7f6885896"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_mr6gcv6mbrjl_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# 查看这些 wiki 进程是从哪个用户/父进程启动的\nfor pid in 300479 310528 320539 330559 340549 350558 362127; do\n  echo \"=== PID $pid ===\"\n  ps -o pid,ppid,user,etime,cmd --no-headers -p $pid 2>/dev/null\ndone"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_mr6gcv6mbrjl_2","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# 检查是否有 systemd timer 或其他 crontab 在跑 wiki-auto-learn\ncrontab -l 2>/dev/null\necho \"---\"\nsystemctl list-timers 2>/dev/null | grep