wiki-auto-learn最后运行 ===\\nModify: 2026-04-11 02:17:18.590097782 +0800\\n\\n=== memory维护脚本 ===\\naliyun-monitor.js\\naliyun_selenium.py\\naliyun_spike_simple.py\\nall.py\\nauto-learn-7h.sh\\nauto-lint.sh\\ndaily_weather.sh\\nhealth-check.py\\nmemory-tool.py\\nmemory_keeper.sh\\nmemory_maintain.sh\\nweather_reminder.sh\\nweather_report.sh\\nwiki-7h-loop-v2.sh\\nwiki-7h-loop.sh\\nwiki-auto-learn.py\\nwiki-deep-learn-7h.sh\\nwiki-think-7h.sh\\nwiki-trigger.sh\\n\",\"name\":\"echo \\\"=== raw源目录 ===\\\";\"},\"isError\":false,\"timestamp\":1776066410387}}\n/home/ai/.openclaw/agents/main/sessions/d263827d-6dd2-4f5a-84d7-68ae11ee9e16.checkpoint.2204a1ee-631b-4a8b-93bf-2b6ab1ae34d3.jsonl:{\"type\":\"message\",\"id\":\"3fe1b7c5\",\"parentId\":\"0b608705\",\"timestamp\":\"2026-04-13T07:47:11.423Z\",\"message\":{\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"thinking\",\"thinking\":\"Now I have a clear picture. Let me summarize the knowledge base situation:\\n\\n**Current state:**\\n1. `memory/entities/` - 49 entity files (active knowledge base)\\n2. `memory/knowledge/` - empty directory\\n3. `memory/entities-archive/` - archived entities\\n4. `memory/raw/` - has docs/notes/papers subdirectories (source material)\\n5. `scripts/wiki-auto-learn.py` - exists, last modified Apr 11, but **no cron job** calling it\\n6. Multiple wiki scripts: wiki-7h-loop, wiki-7h-loop-v2, wiki-deep-learn-7h, wiki-think-7h - but no active cron\\n\\n\\n7. The LLM Wiki Pattern operates on compile-once rather than RAG principles, and the MEMORY from April 13 claimed wiki-auto-learn was hourly, but that cron job never actually existed. The wiki-auto-learn script itself hasn't been modified since April 11.\\n\\nThe real cron jobs running are memory-maintain, memory-keeper, and Memory Dreaming Promotion - there's no active wiki learning cycle right now. The system has a solid structure with raw sources feeding into entities and the LLM Wiki Pattern guiding the process, but it's not currently being populated or maintained.\",\"thinkingSignature\":\"a9102c046b5f5b3e67518fa14da8730413aa6bf732aaadcedf875c40d17247cf\"},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"知识库现状：\\n\\n**架构（LLM Wiki 模式）**\\n\\n```\\nraw/ (docs/notes/papers)  →  entities/ (49个)  →  实体页交叉引用\\n                                 ↑\\n                    session-summary 提炼\\n                    ephemeral 捕获碎片\\n```\\n\\n**问题：没有活跃的摄入循环**\\n\\n| 组件 | 状态 |\\n|------|------|\\n| `wiki-auto-learn.py` | 存在，但**无 cron 调用**（最后修改 Apr 11） |\\n| `wiki-7h-loop*.sh` | 多个脚本，无 cron |\\n| `memory-keeper` | ✅ 有 cron，每天 4 点 |\\n| `memory-maintain` | ✅ 有 cron，每天 3 点 |\\n| `Memory Dreaming Promo` | ✅ 有 cron，每天 3 点 |\\n\\nMEMORY 里写的\\\"wiki-auto-learn 每小时\\\"是错的——这个 cron 从来没创建过。\\n\\n**两件事要决定：**\\n\\n1. **要不要重建 wiki-auto-learn cron？**——基于 `scripts/wiki-auto-learn.py`，每小时扫 raw/ 摄取新文档到 entities/\\n2. **还是用 memory-keeper 代替？**——它已经在跑了，可能做了类似的事\\n\\n要不要我跑一下 `wiki-auto-learn.py` 看看它做什么、效果怎么样？\"}],\"api\":\"anthropic-messages\",\"provider\":\"minimax\",\"model\":\"MiniMax-M2.7\",\"usage\":{\"input\":68066,\"output\":528,\"cacheRead\":18714,\"cacheWrite\":0,\"totalTokens\":87308,\"cost\":{\"input\":0.0204198,\"output\":0.0006336,\"cacheRead\":0.00112284,\"cacheWrite\":0,\"total\":0.02217624}},\"stopReason\":\"stop\",\"timestamp\":1776066410407,\"responseId\":\"062bd26af437eb3515d558afcd0dc81e\"}}\n/home/ai/.openclaw/agents/main/sessions/d263827d-6dd2-4f5a-84d7-68ae11ee9e16.checkpoint.2204a1ee-631b-4a8b-93bf-2b6ab1ae34d3.jsonl:{\"type\":\"message\",\"id\":\"c70f7d83\",\"parentId\":\"08c60dcd\",\"timestamp\":\"2026-04-13T07:48:45.494Z\",\"message\":{\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"thinking\",\"thinking\":\"The user is asking if the wiki-auto-learn is integrated into the overall framework. They seem surprised/questioning that wiki-auto-learn doesn't have a cron job and isn't part of the main system.\\n\\nLet me think about this more carefully. The user's question \\\"没进入整体框架吗？\\\" means \\\"It's not integrated into the overall framework?\\\"\\n\\nLooking at what we know:\\n1. `wiki-auto-learn.py` exists as a script but has no cron\\n2. `memory-keeper`, `memory-maintain`, `Memory Dreaming Promo` are the three active crons\\n3. The ephemeral → session-summary → bootstrap chain is the \\\"two-layer memory system\\\"\\n\\n\\n4. The wiki knowledge base appears to be a separate system that was built but never connected to the main cron jobs\\n\\nSo the real issue is that the wiki ingestion pipeline exists in isolation—it's not wired into any of the active scheduled tasks or the bootstrap memory chain. I need to figure out whether the user wants me to integrate it into the existing framework or if they want a completely different approach.\",\"thinkingSignature\":\"b7a74010115f8f3af9e7471a0bb61da75425d9f44b5be612d657fc25c6105745\"},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"没有。从来没进框架。\\n\\n现在的框架只有三层：\\n\\n```\\nephemeral (捕获)\\n    ↓ hook\\nsession-summary (提炼)      ← 每隔一段时间 summary hook 做一次\\n    ↓ bootstrap hook 注入\\n新 session 上下文\\n```\\n\\n而 wiki-auto-learn 是一个独立的 Python 脚本，没人调用它，没有任何调度。它跟上面的框架完全平行、不相交。\\n\\n**这说明之前的实现是散的**：做了很多工具脚本，但没有纳入 cron 体系，也没有和 session-summary / ephemeral 链路打通。\\n\\n如果要让知识库进入框架，有两种接法：\\n\\n| 方案 | 做法 | 改动量 |\\n|------|------|--------|\\n| A. 接到 memory-keeper | 让 keeper 在跑的时候顺便调 wiki-auto-learn | 小 |\\n| B. 接到 session-summary | hook 每次 session 结束时顺便触发一次 wiki 摄取 | 中 |\\n| C. 新建 cron | 每小时跑一次 wiki-auto-learn | 小，但有重复调度 |\\n\\n你倾向哪种？\"}],\"api\":\"anthropic-messages\",\"provider\":\"minimax\",\"model\":\"MiniMax-M2.7\",\"usage\":{\"input\":54,\"output\":416,\"cacheRead\":84290,\"cacheWrite\":2649,\"totalTokens\":87409,\"cost\":{\"input\":0.0000162,\"output\":0.0004992,\"cacheRead\":0.005057399999999999,\"cacheWrite\":0.0009933750000000001,\"total\":0.006566175}},\"stopReason\":\"stop\",\"timestamp\":1776066505528,\"responseId\":\"062bd2c863efbaa6ac8537218bb5632c\"}}\n/home/ai/.openclaw/agents/main/sessions/d263827d-6dd2-4f5a-84d7-68ae11ee9e16.checkpoint.2204a1ee-631b-4a8b-93bf-2b6ab1ae34d3.jsonl:{\"type\":\"message\",\"id\":\"3125e3d9\",\"parentId\":\"76b7e5a2\",\"timestamp\":\"2026-04-13T07:49:51.927Z\",\"message\":{\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"thinking\",\"thinking\":\"The user wants me to think about the best way to integrate wiki-auto-learn into the framework. Let me think deeply about this.\\n\\nCurrent framework:\\n1. ephemeral - captures fragments in real-time via hooks\\n2. session-summary - generates structured summary at end of session\\n3. bootstrap - injects previous session summary into new session context\\n\\nThe wiki-auto-learn system:\\n- Ingests raw sources (docs, notes, papers) into entities/\\n- Has multiple scripts (wiki-auto-learn.py, wiki-7h-loop.sh, etc.)\\n- No cron, no hooks, completely standalone\\n\\nThe question is: what's the right integration point?\\n\\nLet me think about the data flow:\\n\\n\\nWiki ingestion is fundamentally different from session memory—it's long-term knowledge accumulation rather than conversational context. If I trigger it from session-summary hooks, I'd be creating an unbounded loop since wiki updates could themselves generate more sessions. The cleanest path is keeping ephemeral and session-summary focused on conversation state, while routing wiki ingestion through a separate cron job that runs on a different cycle, like memory-keeper. Actually, the cleanest approach is Option D: make wiki-auto-learn a session that's launched by the session-summary hook, similar to how the v8 system works—spawning an isolated sub-agent for complex work. But I need to think through the trigger conditions more carefully. The real question isn't when to run the wiki ingestion, but what should trigger it: when new raw sources appear, when a session produces notable decisions worth capturing as entities, or on a scheduled interval for general maintenance?\\n\\nThe most practical setup would be a cron job running wiki-auto-learn periodically, with session-summary creating/updating entity pages when significant decisions are made during sessions, and the keeper simply monitoring progress without duplicating what the learner already does. I'm thinking through how session-summary could also update entities when key decisions happen, while keeping the architecture clean and avoiding duplication. The cleanest approach would be a cron job running wiki-auto-learn hourly to handle raw source ingestion, then leveraging the session-summary hook to directly create or update entity pages when significant decisions surface during conversations—rather than spawning separate agents. The framework should manage ingestion and entity updates as distinct responsibilities, with a daily maintenance cron to handle cross-references and structural integrity. The architecture I'm settling on has three distinct layers: ephemeral captures conversation fragments in real-time, session-summary extracts entities and updates memory on a schedule, and then there's a separate async process that maintains the actual knowledge base by ingesting raw sources into the entity system.\\n\\nBut I need to think through the timing more carefully—the session-summary hook runs synchronously and can write entities, while wiki-auto-learn runs as a cron job, so I need to clarify whether session-summary is doing the entity extraction or if that's delegated to the async learner. I need to focus on what's actionable here rather than getting caught up in the technical details. The real insight is that the two systems serve different purposes—they don't need to be tightly coupled. What matters is ensuring session-summary can write to entities and the cron jobs actually run.\",\"thinkingSignature\":\"8d4185c1a9e66ea102bd1d9c3ccc39ab53d38e4fbd94634c395807202edc42d8\"},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"想了一下，核心问题在于：\\n\\n**wiki-auto-learn 和 session-summary 是两个不同维度的东西，强行并轨会乱。**\\n\\n| 系统 | 驱动 | 内容 |\\n|------|------|------|\\n| session-summary | /new 触发 | ���会话提炼实体页（决策、发现、偏好） |\\n| wiki-auto-learn | 原始文档 | 从 docs/papers/notes 提炼实体页（知识积累） |\\n\\n**正确的分层：**\\n\\n```\\n┌─────────────────────────────────────────┐\\n│  Raw Sources (docs/notes/papers)        │  ← wiki-auto-learn 摄取\\n└────────────────┬────────────────────────┘\\n                 ↓\\n┌─────────────────────────────────────────┐\\n│  entities/ (49个)                       │  ← 知识沉淀\\n└─────────────────────────────────────────┘\\n                 ↑ session-summary 写入\\n                 │\\n┌─────────────────────────────────────────┐\\n│  ephemeral → session-summary → 实体页   │  ← 对话驱动\\n└─────────────────────────────────────────┘\\n\\ncron: wiki-auto-learn 每小时 (知识积累)\\ncron: memory-keeper 每天4点 (维护/交叉引用)\\n```\\n\\n**session-summary hook 现在的代码已经支持 entity 升格**（看过了），每次 session 结束如果 LLM 判断有值得沉淀的内容，会直接写 entities/。\\n\\n所以实际需要做的事只有一件：\\n\\n> **把 wiki-auto-learn.py 挂到 cron，每小时跑一次。**\\n\\n其他两个 cron（memory-maintain/keeper）职责不变，不碰 wiki-auto-learn 的流程，避免重复调度。\\n\\n要我把这个 cron 建起来吗？\"}],\"api\":\"anthropic-messages\",\"provider\":\"minimax\",\"model\":\"MiniMax-M2.7\",\"usage\":{\"input\":0,\"output\":938,\"cacheRead\":87254,\"cacheWrite\":0,\"totalTokens\":88192,\"cost\":{\"input\":0,\"output\":0.0011256,\"cacheRead\":0.0052352399999999995,\"cacheWrite\":0,\"total\":0.0063608399999999995}},\"stopReason\":\"stop\",\"timestamp\":1776066556641,\"responseId\":\"062bd2fc7162cb529773425ef56bb1e3\"}}\n/home/ai/.openclaw/agents/main/sessions/d263827d-6dd2-4f5a-84d7-68ae11ee9e16.checkpoint.2204a1ee-631b-4a8b-93bf-2b6ab1ae34d3.jsonl:{\"type\":\"message\",\"id\":\"0b0192a8\",\"parentId\":\"156d78ed\",\"timestamp\":\"2026-04-13T07:51:43.733Z\",\"message\":{\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"thinking\",\"thinking\":\"The user wants me to:\\n1. Set up the wiki-auto-learn cron job\\n2. Make sure the whole framework runs through properly\\n\\nLet me first check the wiki-auto-learn.py script to understand what it does and what parameters it needs. Then I'll create a cron job for it.\\n\\nLet me also think about what \\\"整个框架跑通\\\" means:\\n1. ephemeral captures events ✅ (already working)\\n2. session-summary hook generates summaries ✅ (already working)\\n3. bootstrap hook injects summaries into new sessions ✅ (just fixed)\\n4. wiki-auto-learn cron - needs to be set up\\n5. memory-keeper/memory-maintain - already have cron entries\\n\\n\\n6. Need to examine the wiki-auto-learn.py script to see what arguments it accepts and how to properly configure it for the cron job.\",\"thinkingSignature\":\"400cfed86d61a84c5d369b596ca4024b9be15d248f80509063959c0c1eafcf51\"},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"先摸清楚 wiki-auto-learn.py 的用法：\\n\"},{\"type\":\"toolCall\",\"id\":\"call_function_tzzatbevsv3j_1\",\"name\":\"read\",\"arguments\":{\"path\":\"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/scripts/wiki-auto-learn.py\",\"offset\":40,\"limit\":100}}],\"api\":\"anthropic-messages\",\"provider\":\"minimax\",\"model\":\"MiniMax-M2.7\",\"usage\":{\"input\":54,\"output\":234,\"cacheRead\":87586,\"cacheWrite\":0,\"totalTokens\":87874,\"cost\":{\"input\":0.0000162,\"output\":0.0002808,\"cacheRead\":0.005255159999999999,\"cacheWrite\":0,\"total\":0.0055521599999999996}},\"stopReason\":\"toolUse\",\"timestamp\":1776066687856,\"responseId\":\"062bd380af6b72e8c79a73c8bda3decb\"}}\n/home/ai/.openclaw/agents/main/sessions/d263827d-6dd2-4f5a-84d7-68ae11ee9e16.checkpoint.2204a1ee-631b-4a8b-93bf-2b6ab1ae34d3.jsonl:{\"type\":\"message\",\"id\":\"ee8cc0cd\",\"parentId\":\"c21a9c18\",\"timestamp\":\"2026-04-13T07:51:48.359Z\",\"message\":{\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"thinking\",\"thinking\":\"Let me see the rest of the file, especially how it's invoked from command line (if at all) and what arguments it takes.\",\"thinkingSignature\":\"9783d767c4df882a205401c40f3c2855d27a9da29b56b0956743bd5b1026a5de\"},{\"type\":\"toolCall\",\"id\":\"call_function_rq4o25t0k5c1_1\",\"name\":\"read\",\"arguments\":{\"path\":\"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/scripts/wiki-auto-learn.py\",\"offset\":140,\"limit\":120}}],\"api\":\"anthropic-messages\",\"provider\":\"minimax\",\"model\":\"MiniMax-M2.7\",\"usage\":{\"input\":69922,\"output\":86,\"cacheRead\":18714,\"cacheWrite\":0,\"totalTokens\":88722,\"cost\":{\"input\":0.020976599999999998,\"output\":0.0001032,\"cacheRead\":0.00112284,\"cacheWrite\":0,\"total\":0.02220264}},\"stopReason\":\"toolUse\",\"timestamp\":1776066703812,\"responseId\":\"062bd38f0a520d06376473845342007d\"}}\n/home/ai/.openclaw/agents/main/sessions/d263827d-6dd2-4f5a-84d7-68ae11ee9e16.checkpoint.2204a1ee-631b-4a8b-93bf-2b6ab1ae34d3.jsonl:{\"type\":\"message\",\"id\":\"a51adf08\",\"parentId\":\"ffb4f790\",\"timestamp\":\"2026-04-13T07:52:00.996Z\",\"message\":{\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"thinking\",\"thinking\":\"So `wiki-trigger.sh` runs health checks and triggers `auto-lint.sh` if needed, but it doesn't run `wiki-auto-learn.py`. \\n\\nThe `wiki-auto-learn.py` is designed to run as a long 7-hour loop, not as a one-shot. For cron use, I need to adapt it.\\n\\nOptions:\\n1. Create a wrapper that runs a single cycle of wiki-auto-learn\\n2. Modify wiki-auto-learn.py to support a `--once` flag\\n3. Use the existing `wiki-7h-loop.sh` or `wiki-7h-loop-v2.sh` scripts\\n\\nLet me check `wiki-7h-loop-v2.sh` to see if it's more suitable for cron use.\",\"thinkingSignature\":\"8f4ba0d0c6168860c4d9e16b615a36950c7002fce260153d86dc260d7cd8ff03\"},{\"type\":\"toolCall\",\"id\":\"call_function_od627qxzn315_1\",\"name\":\"read\",\"arguments\":{\"path\":\"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/scripts/wiki-7h-loop-v2.sh\"}}],\"api\":\"anthropic-messages\",\"provider\":\"minimax\",\"model\":\"MiniMax-M2.7\",\"usage\":{\"input\":71462,\"output\":190,\"cacheRead\":18714,\"cacheWrite\":0,\"totalTokens\":90366,\"cost\":{\"input\":0.0214386,\"output\":0.00022799999999999999,\"cacheRead\":0.00112284,\"cacheWrite\":0,\"total\":0.022789439999999998}},\"stopReason\":\"toolUse\",\"timestamp\":1776066716305,\"responseId\":\"062bd39aa6fae635a50016fe3dd90959\"}}\n/home/ai/.openclaw/agents/main/sessions/d263827d-6dd2-4f5a-84d7-68ae11ee9e16.checkpoint.2204a1ee-631b-4a8b-93bf-2b6ab1ae34d3.jsonl:{\"type\":\"message\",\"id\":\"6a4a5d48\",\"parentId\":\"80c24a30\",\"timestamp\":\"2026-04-13T07:52:32.517Z\",\"message\":{\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"thinking\",\"thinking\":\"I see - the `wiki-7h-loop-v2.sh` is a long-running 7-hour loop (210 iterations × 2 minutes = 420 minutes = 7 hours). This is NOT suitable for cron use because:\\n1. It runs for 7 hours straight\\n2. It would overlap with the next cron trigger\\n\\nFor cron use, I need a **one-shot version** that runs a single cycle quickly and exits. Let me look at what a single cycle does:\\n1. Scan skills/ - create entity pages for new skills\\n2. Scan docs/ - count raw sources\\n3. Check for dead links\\n4. Log\\n\\n\\nA single cycle would probably finish in under a second. I should create a lightweight one-shot cron script that handles skills/ → entity pages, docs/ → raw sources counting, dead link checking, and logging without the long-running loop. I'll call it `wiki-learn-once.sh` and set it to run hourly via cron. The existing `wiki-auto-learn.py` is too heavy for this since it's designed for continuous long-running cycles, so I need to build something purpose-built for hourly cron execution.\",\"thinkingSignature\":\"a03580664acc28deabe40bda13bc5699c685982f9af2c9abb9987a079f2d14ca\"},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"理解了。`wiki-7h-loop-v2.sh` 是 7 小时长循环，不适合 cron。需要一个**一次跑完**的版本。\\n\"},{\"type\":\"toolCall\",\"id\":\"call_function_0l1kj7nfjjwa_1\",\"name\":\"write\",\"arguments\":{\"path\":\"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/scripts/wiki-learn-once.sh\",\"content\":\"#!/bin/bash\\n# Wiki Auto-Learn 单次执行脚本\\n# 每次运行一个完整 cycle：扫描 → 摄取 → 写回 → Lint\\n# 配合 cron 使用，每小时触发一次\\n\\nWORKSPACE=\\\"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace\\\"\\nENTITIES=\\\"$WORKSPACE/memory/entities\\\"\\nRAW=\\\"$WORKSPACE/memory/raw\\\"\\nLOG=\\\"$WORKSPACE/memory/log.md\\\"\\nSKILLS_DIR=\\\"$WORKSPACE/skills\\\"\\n\\nmkdir -p \\\"$RAW/docs\\\" \\\"$RAW/papers\\\" \\\"$RAW/notes\\\"\\n\\necho \\\"[$(date '+%Y-%m-%d %H:%M:%S')] === wiki-learn-once 启动 ===\\\"\\n\\n# ===== 1. Ingest: 扫描 skills/ 创建实体页 =====\\nNEW_ENTITIES=0\\nfor skill in \\\"$SKILLS_DIR\\\"/*/; do\\n    if [ -d \\\"$skill\\\" ]; then\\n        name=$(basename \\\"$skill\\\")\\n        if [ ! -f \\\"$ENTITIES/${name}.md\\\" ]; then\\n            cat > \\\"$ENTITIES/${name}.md\\\" << EOF\\n---\\ntitle: $name\\ntype: skill\\nstatus: auto-ingested\\nlast_updated: $(date '+%Y-%m-%d')\\ntags: [skill, auto]\\n---\\n\\n# $name\\n\\n> 自动从 skills/ 目录摄入\\n\\n## 来源\\n\\n- 类型: skill\\n- 路径: skills/$name\\n- 摄入时间: $(date \\\"+%Y-%m-%d %H:%M\\\")\\n\\n## 相关页面\\n\\n- [[skills]] - 技能清单\\n- [[ai-usage]] - AI 使用方式\\nEOF\\n            echo \\\"  📥 新技能实体页: $name\\\"\\n            NEW_ENTITIES=$((NEW_ENTITIES + 1))\\n        fi\\n    fi\\ndone\\n\\n# 扫描 docs/ 作为 Raw Sources\\nDOCS_COUNT=$(ls \\\"$WORKSPACE/docs\\\"/*.md 2>/dev/null | wc -l)\\nPAPERS_COUNT=$(ls \\\"$WORKSPACE/docs\\\"/*.pdf 2>/dev/null | wc -l)\\necho \\\"  📂 Raw Sources: docs/$DOCS_COUNT\\\"\\n\\n# ===== 2. Lint: 死链检查与修复 =====\\nFIXED=0\\nfor link in $(grep -roh '\\\\[\\\\[[a-z0-9-]*\\\\]\\\\]' \\\"$ENTITIES\\\"/*.md 2>/dev/null | sed 's/\\\\[\\\\[//;s/\\\\]\\\\]//g' | sort -u); do\\n    if [ ! -f \\\"$ENTITIES/${link}.md\\\" ]; then\\n        sed -i \\\"s/\\\\[\\\\[$link\\\\]\\\\]//g\\\" \\\"$ENTITIES\\\"/*.md 2>/dev/null\\n        FIXED=$((FIXED + 1))\\n    fi\\ndone\\n[ $FIXED -gt 0 ] && echo \\\"  🔧 修复死链: $FIXED 个\\\"\\n\\n# ===== 3. 记录 log =====\\nENTITY_COUNT=$(ls \\\"$ENTITIES\\\"/*.md 2>/dev/null | wc -l)\\necho \\\"## [$(date '+%Y-%m-%d %H:%M')] wiki-learn-once | entities:$ENTITY_COUNT | new:$NEW_ENTITIES | fixed:$FIXED | docs:$DOCS_COUNT\\\" >> \\\"$LOG\\\"\\n\\necho \\\"  ✅ entities:$ENTITY_COUNT | new:$NEW_ENTITIES | fixed:$FIXED\\\"\\necho \\\"[$(date '+%Y-%m-%d %H:%M:%S')] === wiki-learn-once 完成 ===\\\"\\n\"}}],\"api\":\"anthropic-messages\",\"provider\":\"minimax\",\"model\":\"MiniMax-M2.7\",\"usage\":{\"input\":72669,\"output\":1041,\"cacheRead\":18714,\"cacheWrite\":0,\"totalTokens\":92424,\"cost\":{\"input\":0.0218007,\"output\":0.0012492,\"cacheRead\":0.00112284,\"cacheWrite\":0,\"total\":0.024172739999999998}},\"stopReason\":\"toolUse\",\"timestamp\":1776066721069,\"responseId\":\"062bd3a265a37594129c1726841cf6aa\"}}\n/home/ai/.openclaw/agents/main/sessions/d263827d-6dd2-4f5a-84d7-68ae11ee9e16.checkpoint.90b7186c-5bfb-4e22-a067-bc755e5453d4.jsonl:{\"type\":\"message\",\"id\":\"cdd1f01c\",\"parentId\":\"9e377c1f\",\"timestamp\":\"2026-04-13T07:46:18.993Z\",\"message\":{\"role\":\"toolResult\",\"toolCallId\":\"call_function_dousaue4jhjl_1\",\"toolName\":\"exec\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"=== knowledge目录 ===\\n\\n=== wiki-auto-learn.py ===\\n#!/usr/bin/env python3\\n\\\"\\\"\\\"\\nLLM Wiki Auto-Learning Framework\\n高鲁棒、高质量、高性能自动化学习循环\\n\\n基于需求 + LLM Wiki 原文设计\\n\\\"\\\"\\\"\\n\\nimport os\\nimport time\\nimport subprocess\\nimport re\\nfrom datetime import datetime\\nfrom pathlib import Path\\n\\n# 配置\\nWORKSPACE = \\\"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace\\\"\\nENTITIES_DIR = f\\\"{WORKSPACE}/memory/entities\\\"\\nRAW_SOURCES_DIR = f\\\"{WORKSPACE}/memory/raw\\\"\\nLOG_FILE = f\\\"{WORKSPACE}/memory/log.md\\\"\\nARCHIVE_DIR = f\\\"{WORKSPACE}/memory/entities-archive\\\"\\n\\n# LLM Wiki 原文核心要点\\nCORE_PRINCIPLES = {\\n    \\\"not_rag\\\": \\\"不是RAG，是增量构建持久wiki\\\",\\n    \\\"compile_once\\\": \\\"知识编译一次，持续更新\\\",\\n    \\\"touch_10_15\\\": \\\"一个source触发10-15页更新\\\",\\n    \\\"maintenance_zero\\\": \\\"维护成本接近零\\\",\\n    \\\"human_role\\\": \\\"人负责选源、提问、思考\\\",\\n    \\\"llm_role\\\": \\\"LLM负责执行维护\\\",\\n    \\\"query_writeback\\\": \\\"好答案写回wiki\\\",\\n    \\\"memex\\\": \\\"LLM解决维护问题\\\"\\n}\\n\\nclass WikiAutoLearn:\\n    def __init__(self):\\n        self.stats = {\\n            \\\"iterations\\\": 0,\\n            \\\"ingested\\\": 0,\\n            \\\"fixed\\\": 0,\\n\\n=== wiki-auto-learn log最新 ===\"}],\"details\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"exitCode\":0,\"durationMs\":46,\"aggregated\":\"=== knowledge目录 ===\\n\\n=== wiki-auto-learn.py ===\\n#!/usr/bin/env python3\\n\\\"\\\"\\\"\\nLLM Wiki Auto-Learning Framework\\n高鲁棒、高质量、高性能自动化学习循环\\n\\n基于需求 + LLM Wiki 原文设计\\n\\\"\\\"\\\"\\n\\nimport os\\nimport time\\nimport subprocess\\nimport re\\nfrom datetime import datetime\\nfrom pathlib import Path\\n\\n# 配置\\nWORKSPACE = \\\"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace\\\"\\nENTITIES_DIR = f\\\"{WORKSPACE}/memory/entities\\\"\\nRAW_SOURCES_DIR = f\\\"{WORKSPACE}/memory/raw\\\"\\nLOG_FILE = f\\\"{WORKSPACE}/memory/log.md\\\"\\nARCHIVE_DIR = f\\\"{WORKSPACE}/memory/entities-archive\\\"\\n\\n# LLM Wiki 原文核心要点\\nCORE_PRINCIPLES = {\\n    \\\"not_rag\\\": \\\"不是RAG，是增量构建持久wiki\\\",\\n    \\\"compile_once\\\": \\\"知识编译一次，持续更新\\\",\\n    \\\"touch_10_15\\\": \\\"一个source触发10-15页更新\\\",\\n    \\\"maintenance_zero\\\": \\\"维护成本接近零\\\",\\n    \\\"human_role\\\": \\\"人负责选源、提问、思考\\\",\\n    \\\"llm_role\\\": \\\"LLM负责执行维护\\\",\\n    \\\"query_writeback\\\": \\\"好答案写回wiki\\\",\\n    \\\"memex\\\": \\\"LLM解决维护问题\\\"\\n}\\n\\nclass WikiAutoLearn:\\n    def __init__(self):\\n        self.stats = {\\n            \\\"iterations\\\": 0,\\n            \\\"ingested\\\": 0,\\n            \\\"fixed\\\": 0,\\n\\n=== wiki-auto-learn log最新 ===\",\"cwd\":\"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/main\"},\"isError\":false,\"timestamp\":1776066378982}}\n/home/ai/.openclaw/agents/main/sessions/d263827d-6dd2-4f5a-84d7-68ae11ee9e16.checkpoint.90b7186c-5bfb-4e22-a067-bc755e5453d4.jsonl:{\"type\":\"message\",\"id\":\"3bcaddc8\",\"parentId\":\"d8516de3\",\"timestamp\":\"2026-04-13T07:46:33.281Z\",\"message\":{\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"thinking\",\"thinking\":\"So the wiki-auto-learn.log is empty (0 lines) - meaning the cron job never ran. The wiki-7h-loop log shows it ran at some point and created 19 new entity pages. But the cron job for wiki-auto-learn doesn't exist in the cron list.\\n\\nLet me get a fuller picture of the knowledge base situation.\",\"th