{"type":"message","id":"76443f65","parentId":"9b291dd7","timestamp":"2026-04-14T06:07:21.783Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants me to fix the issues step by step, thinking carefully before each step. Let me start with the most urgent issue - the wiki-auto-learn process accumulation.\n\nStep 1: Kill the zombie wiki-auto-learn.py processes\nStep 2: Verify they're gone\nStep 3: Check what created them / prevent recurrence\nStep 4: Then move to memory-maintain timeout\nStep 5: Then context-api/openclaw-router\n\nLet me start with step 1.","thinkingSignature":"dfbdd50d6e1ad72856845e01a1bca2c963ec8d7749d7fd056d27b0ebe5591c3a"},{"type":"text","text":"好，按优先级逐个处理。\n\n---\n\n## 第 1 步：清理 wiki-auto-learn 僵尸进程\n\n**思考：** 这7个进程都是孤儿进程（父进程已结束但仍在运行），直接 `pkill` 会误杀其他正常 python 进程。需要精确匹配进程名 + 排除 cron 自身的 shell 包装器。正确做法：用进程树找到所有 `python3 wiki-auto-learn.py` 命名的进程，用 `kill` 逐个清理。\n\n**执行：**\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_0ylkyomye5th_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# 精确找到所有 wiki-auto-learn.py 进程，排除 cron 自身 shell wrapper\necho \"=== 清理前 ===\"\nps aux | grep \"wiki-auto-learn\\|wiki-learn-once\" | grep -v grep\n\necho \"\"\necho \"=== 执行清理 ===\"\nfor pid in $(pgrep -f \"python3.*wiki-auto-learn.py\"); do\n  echo \"杀掉 PID $pid: $(cat /proc/$pid/cmdline 2>/dev/null | tr '\\0' ' ')\"\n  kill $pid 2>/dev/null && echo \"  → 已发送 SIGTERM\" || echo \"  → 已结束或无权限\"\ndone\n\nsleep 2\n\necho \"\"\necho \"=== 清理后 ===\"\nps aux | grep \"wiki-auto-learn\\|wiki-learn-once\" | grep -v grep || echo \"✅ 全部清理完毕\""}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":54,"output":403,"cacheRead":64534,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":64991,"cost":{"input":0.0000162,"output":0.0004836,"cacheRead":0.0038720399999999998,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00437184}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776146815704,"responseId":"062d0c83d2fab6f7feeb9da8ff5ab792"}}
