{"type":"message","id":"b285b407","parentId":"6a639479","timestamp":"2026-04-14T06:11:06.380Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good. Now let me also verify the update was saved correctly and then continue to step 4 - the context-api / openclaw-router issue.","thinkingSignature":"494c67da8866c49761ac8d193c3151208ac77a4a63b2acaefcc7f260aa4aad24"},{"type":"text","text":"✅ **第3步完成：** 消息从\"每日记忆系统维护脚本**已运行**\"（触发执行）改为\"✅ 每日记忆维护**已完成**\"（被动通知，agent 会简单回复\"好的\"）。\n\n---\n\n## 第 4 步：context-api / openclaw-router 死代码确认\n\n**思考：** 3101 端口的 context-api 收到 0 条消息，说明 `on-message.sh → 3101` 整条链路从未被 gateway 触发过。需要确认：① context-api 本身是否在监听 ② gateway 是否有 message hook 配置指向它 ③ 这条 path 是否已被废弃\n\n如果确认废弃，则关闭进程，释放资源。\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_tmi0blpk0n8n_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# 检查 context-api 进程和端口状态\necho \"=== context-api 进程 ===\"\nps aux | grep \"context-api\\|api_server\" | grep -v grep | grep -v snap\n\necho \"\"\necho \"=== 3101 端口监听 ===\"\nss -tlnp | grep 3101 2>/dev/null || echo \"3101 无监听\"\n\necho \"\"\necho \"=== context-api 目录 ===\"\nls -la /home/ai/.openclaw/context-api/"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_tmi0blpk0n8n_2","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# 检查 on-message.sh 的实际内容（gateway 是否有 message hook 触发它）\ncat /home/ai/.openclaw/hooks/on-message.sh 2>/dev/null | head -20"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":54843,"output":357,"cacheRead":19262,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":74462,"cost":{"input":0.0164529,"output":0.0004284,"cacheRead":0.0011557199999999998,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.018037019999999997}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776147053893,"responseId":"062d0d6d1dbd18df4be9e8b614bfd3e1"}}
