{"type":"message","id":"f3c93efe","parentId":"183c7e8a","timestamp":"2026-04-14T06:11:41.274Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I see the full picture:\n\n1. `pid 88283` with `python3 api_server.py` is actually the **Scene Classifier** process (3105), not the context-api. The `pt_main_thread` (Python threading) is what runs the Scene Classifier.\n\n2. The **context-api** (`api_server.py` from `/home/ai/.openclaw/context-api/index.js`) uses `PORT=3101` from env or defaults to 3101, but it's NOT in the `ss -tlnp` output. This means the context-api process is NOT running or crashed/exited.\n\n3. The `ps aux` shows `ai 88283 ... /usr/bin/python3 api_server.py` - but this IS the Scene Classifier (3105), because it's the one listening on 3105.\n   \nSo there's a process naming conflict—the context-api server was likely replaced by the Scene Classifier at some point, which would explain why 3101 isn't responding to requests from `on-message.sh`. The context-api either never started properly or was overwritten when the Scene Classifier took over port 3101.\n\nThe solution is straightforward: shut down the context-api since it's not being used anyway, and either repurpose 3101 for something active or leave it dormant. Looking at the listening ports, 3101 isn't currently in use, so I should either disable the context-api service to free it up or document why it should remain reserved.","thinkingSignature":"c655b473771bbffe427749d29029d9ed48ebadb2501b700341fabbdefb5b2903"},{"type":"text","text":"**发现：** context-api 进程**不在监听 3101**。pid 88283 虽然是 `python3 api_server.py`，但它实际是 Scene Classifier（3105 端口）。context-api 的 server 根本没在跑——它是 Apr 10 的旧残留进程，从未成功绑定 3101。\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_nu8j1nkkxq8d_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# 检查 context-api 的 PORT 环境配置\ncat /home/ai/.openclaw/context-api/.env 2>/dev/null\necho \"---\"\n# 检查 context-api 的进程是否真的是 scene-classifier\necho \"=== 验证 pid 88283 ===\"\nls -la /proc/88283/exe 2>/dev/null\necho \"=== scene-classifier 目录 ===\"\nls /home/ai/.openclaw/v8/scene-classifier/"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":57071,"output":482,"cacheRead":19262,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":76815,"cost":{"input":0.0171213,"output":0.0005784,"cacheRead":0.0011557199999999998,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.018855419999999998}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776147083584,"responseId":"062d0d8bdb623856337c60c24103f62f"}}
