{"type":"message","id":"14eebc26","parentId":"d49696f1","timestamp":"2026-04-14T06:15:12.812Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_2x9m8qpn5mfv_2","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"-rw-rw-r-- 1 ai ai 1170 Apr 13 17:07 /home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/memory/2026-04-13-session-summary.md\n\n# Session: 2026-04-13 17:00\n\n<!-- summary-only -->\n\n## 主题\n框架全面检查 + 记忆链路修复 + 知识库精简\n\n## 关键决策\n1. 修复 auto-score-classify hook：3108→3105（scene-classifier 端口）\n2. 修复 bootstrap hook：主动读 session-summary 注入新 session\n3. 修复 wiki-learn cron delivery：改 none 避免 channel 报错\n4. 建立 entity 稳定机制：blocklist 防重复摄入，稳定在 30 个\n5. 确认 session-summary 链路：ephemeral→摘要→bootstrap 已全线通\n\n## 重要发现\n1. bootstrap hook（handler.js）会在 /new 时主动读最新 session-summary 注入上下文\n2. auto-score-classify hook 在跑，每条消息更新 context.json\n3. ephemeral isMeaningful 过滤合理：高风险/拦截/显式记忆请求才入 ephemeral\n4. session-summary hook 每次 /new 时运行，从 ephemeral + session 内容提炼摘要\n5. entity 精简策略：TARGET=30，超量时删 auto-ingested 低行数模板"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":110,"aggregated":"-rw-rw-r-- 1 ai ai 1170 Apr 13 17:07 /home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/memory/2026-04-13-session-summary.md\n\n# Session: 2026-04-13 17:00\n\n<!-- summary-only -->\n\n## 主题\n框架全面检查 + 记忆链路修复 + 知识库精简\n\n## 关键决策\n1. 修复 auto-score-classify hook：3108→3105（scene-classifier 端口）\n2. 修复 bootstrap hook：主动读 session-summary 注入新 session\n3. 修复 wiki-learn cron delivery：改 none 避免 channel 报错\n4. 建立 entity 稳定机制：blocklist 防重复摄入，稳定在 30 个\n5. 确认 session-summary 链路：ephemeral→摘要→bootstrap 已全线通\n\n## 重要发现\n1. bootstrap hook（handler.js）会在 /new 时主动读最新 session-summary 注入上下文\n2. auto-score-classify hook 在跑，每条消息更新 context.json\n3. ephemeral isMeaningful 过滤合理：高风险/拦截/显式记忆请求才入 ephemeral\n4. session-summary hook 每次 /new 时运行，从 ephemeral + session 内容提炼摘要\n5. entity 精简策略：TARGET=30，超量时删 auto-ingested 低行数模板","cwd":"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/main"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1776147312799}}
{"type":"message","id":"9d21adad","parentId":"14eebc26","timestamp":"2026-04-14T06:15:29.278Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I have a clear picture. Let me compile a comprehensive critical review.\n\nKey findings:\n\n1. **ephemeral** - ✅ Working. Hourly files, latest at 14:01 today.\n\n2. **session-summary** - ⚠️ Only runs on `/new` or `/reset` commands (event type \"command\", action \"new\" or \"reset\"). Last run was Apr 13 17:07 when someone ran `/new`. Today (Apr 14) no `/new` was run, so no new summary. This is EXPECTED behavior, not a bug.\n\n3. **bootstrap hook** - ✅ Reads latest session-summary and injects on `agent:bootstrap`. If no `/new` happened today, the bootstrap would inject the Apr 13 summary. \n\n4. **auto-score-classify** - Fires on `event.type === \"message\" && event.action === \"preprocessed\"`. This is where the real issue lies: the Apr 13 review showed `classification: null` consistently. If the hook is supposed to fire on \"preprocessed\" messages but classification is null, either the hook isn't firing at all or it's failing to get a response from the classification service.\n\n5. **context.json classification null** - The Apr 13 session noted this was a problem. But we don't know if it was ever fixed. Let me check the current context.json to see what the classification state is now.","thinkingSignature":"871027beca7c4cdab0e72fb2986f116883a7daa101c5cd5f1a62b1f776c2beac"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_4qja4m5bj8xl_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# 检查当前 session 的 context.json\ncat /home/ai/.openclaw/sessions/agent\\:main\\:main/context.json 2>/dev/null | python3 -m json.tool 2>/dev/null"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_4qja4m5bj8xl_2","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# 检查 gateway 日志里的 hook 触发情况\nls -lt /home/ai/.openclaw/logs/ 2>/dev/null | head -10\necho \"---\"\n# gateway.log 最后修改时间\nstat /home/ai/.openclaw/logs/gateway.log 2>/dev/null | grep -E \"Modify|Size\""}