{"type":"message","id":"5fc12092","parentId":"c2c53f85","timestamp":"2026-04-14T06:16:05.927Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I have a much clearer picture:\n\n1. **classification is working** - confirmed with valid scene/confidence\n2. **ephemeral is working** - Apr 14 06:01 entry has valid classification from 3105\n3. **gateway logging** - set to \"warn\" level, so only warnings are logged, which explains why gateway.log hasn't grown (no warnings since Apr 13)\n4. **sessions directory** - only has context.json, no .jsonl history file (this is expected for webchat sessions - they store messages internally in gateway)\n\nBut there's still something I haven't fully verified:\n\n\n- **The full memory chain** - ephemeral captures messages, session-summary generates on /new, and bootstrap injects the last summary into new sessions. This is the critical path we need to confirm actually works.\n- **Where ephemeral paths originate** - I'm seeing entries like \"A scheduled reminder has been triggered...\" which suggests cron or heartbeat events are feeding into the ephemeral capture system, but I need to trace exactly how these paths are being initiated.\n- **Self-improvement and memory-keeper** - these agents are running on cron schedules but I'm not seeing evidence they produced actionable outputs yet.\n- **The memory-maintain fix** - I updated the text from \"已运行\" to \"已完成\", but I need to verify this actually resolves the issue.\n- **The context-api situation** - pid 88283 is definitely scene-classifier, not context-api as I initially thought. But there's still the question of whether that /usr/bin/python3.8 process is the same one running api_server.py, since the venv uses python3.8 but the process shows /usr/bin/python3.","thinkingSignature":"1245249dbbfc83cbf6701279d05d73b355c7136be6bdeacc40abca93089885ab"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_fpvmf25w2gqp_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# 确认 pid 88283 是 scene-classifier venv python\nls -la /proc/88283/exe 2>/dev/null\necho \"---\"\n# scene-classifier 的 venv\nls /home/ai/.openclaw/v8/scene-classifier/venv/bin/python* 2>/dev/null\necho \"---\"\n# 对比 3105 端口进程\nlsof -i :3105 2>/dev/null | head -5"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_fpvmf25w2gqp_2","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# 深度：检查当前 session 的 bootstrap 是否真的注入了摘要\n# 查看当前 session 的完整上下文\ncat /home/ai/.openclaw/sessions/agent\\:main\\:main/context.json 2>/dev/null"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":64226,"output":534,"cacheRead":19262,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":84022,"cost":{"input":0.019267799999999998,"output":0.0006408,"cacheRead":0.0011557199999999998,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.021064319999999997}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776147347725,"responseId":"062d0e93fa6c537dc3d201e155285596"}}
