{"type":"message","id":"8aa96025","parentId":"9246b823","timestamp":"2026-04-14T06:18:16.616Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants me to follow the steps I outlined to actually verify and close the open issues. Let me think about what needs to be done:\n\n1. **session-summary + bootstrap 链路验证** → Need to trigger `/new` to actually run the full chain\n2. **memory-maintain 今晚 3 AM 才能验证** → Can't verify yet, just confirm the fix is in place\n3. **wiki-auto-learn 无新进程** → Already confirmed clean\n\nThe most impactful action I can take right now is: trigger a `/new` to verify the session-summary → bootstrap injection chain actually works. This will generate a new session-summary file and verify the bootstrap hook injects it into the new session.\n \nI'm realizing there's a tension here—the user is asking me to work through issues I've identified, but running `/new` would reset our current conversation, which is where the verification should happen. I could verify the bootstrap hook code exists and is properly configured without actually triggering a reset, but the whole point is to see the chain working end-to-end in this session. The real insight is that I need to validate the session-summary and bootstrap chain before starting new work, so I should trigger `/new` in an isolated session first to observe how the system builds and injects context, then continue the current conversation normally.","thinkingSignature":"f84ecaab12858292b10e3d716f1a1fe7fb19e5f35109dcae71beb44ab8e7d4b6"},{"type":"text","text":"好，按步骤执行。第一步先做最重要的：**验证 session-summary → bootstrap 链路**。\n\n## 第 1 步：触发 /new 验证链路\n\n**思考：** 在 isolated session 里触发 `/new`，验证：① session-summary hook 是否生成摘要 ② bootstrap hook 是否读取并注入。这样不打断当前主 session。\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_74x0hi04fd4h_1","name":"sessions_spawn","arguments":{"task":"请执行 /new 命令触发一个新 session，然后：\n1. 检查 /new 后系统是否注入了上一页摘要（查看 session 的 system prompt 或上下文）\n2. 检查 ~/.openclaw/workspace/memory/ 目录下是否生成了新的 *-session-summary.md 文件\n3. 返回你观察到的摘要注入情况\n\n只做观察，不要做任何实际工作。完成后返回观察报告。","runtime":"subagent","runTimeoutSeconds":60,"mode":"run"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":54,"output":473,"cacheRead":19262,"cacheWrite":63739,"totalTokens":83528,"cost":{"input":0.0000162,"output":0.0005676,"cacheRead":0.0011557199999999998,"cacheWrite":0.023902125,"total":0.025641645}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776147471657,"responseId":"062d0f0e948a1d9c4b356aa1f46d4253"}}
