{"type":"message","id":"16db8816","parentId":"93da9f8f","timestamp":"2026-04-14T06:48:55.565Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I understand the problem clearly. Let me summarize the bugs found:\n\n**Bug 1: `project.js` uses `yaml.load()` instead of `yaml.loadAll()`**\n- `林枫.yaml` has 2 YAML documents (separated by `---`), so `yaml.load()` fails with \"expected a single document\"\n- The solution is to use `yaml.loadAll()` or skip multi-document files\n\n**Bug 2: `青云子.yaml` has YAML syntax error**\n- Uses Markdown with YAML-like syntax (`**姓名**: value`) which contains `**` characters that are not valid YAML\n- This is NOT valid YAML - the `**bold**` markdown syntax causes YAML parsing errors\n  \nI should also check whether the facts files need `yaml.loadAll()` instead of `yaml.load()` since they might contain multiple documents, and I need to examine how `generate-chapter.js` handles these files to see if there are additional issues in how the data flows through the system.","thinkingSignature":"2cf37c51c24b6f5c90a9f895944030c1a5e7c0e2203a627363e3d0fc054b42e8"},{"type":"text","text":"---\n\n## 第 1 步结果：发现 YAML 解析 bug\n\n**问题A：** `project.js` 的 `readCharacters()` 用 `yaml.load()`，但 `林枫.yaml` 包含 2 个 YAML 文档（被 `---` 分隔），导致 \"expected a single document\" 错误。\n\n**问题B：** `青云子.yaml` 使用 Markdown 语法（`**姓名**:`），不是合法 YAML。\n\n---\n\n## 第 2 步：验证 facts 文件格式一致性\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_gldgqleq1xj6_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"node -e \"\nconst yaml = require('/mnt/d/aafuzhi/axs/my-novel-tools/node_modules/js-yaml');\nconst fs = require('fs');\nconst content = fs.readFileSync('/mnt/d/aafuzhi/axs/my-novel/facts/characters_facts.yaml', 'utf8');\nconst lines = content.split('\\n');\nlet inDoc = false;\nlines.forEach((line, i) => {\n  if (line.trim() === '---') { inDoc = !inDoc; console.log('Line ' + (i+1) + ': --- ' + (inDoc ? 'START' : 'END')); }\n});\nconsole.log('Total --- separators:', (content.match(/^---$/gm) || []).length);\n\" 2>&1"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":97829,"output":495,"cacheRead":19262,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":117586,"cost":{"input":0.0293487,"output":0.000594,"cacheRead":0.0011557199999999998,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.031098419999999998}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776149316900,"responseId":"062d164651e8cc530e0c1860b08e4135"}}
