{"type":"message","id":"b666b754","parentId":"5460736f","timestamp":"2026-04-14T06:50:34.279Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_e3hptn3jvk7m_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# 青云子 - 角色档案\r\n\r\n## 基本信息\r\n**姓名**: 青云子\r\n**称号**: 青云宗宗主\r\n**年龄**: 外观40岁，实际年龄未知\r\n**性别**: 男\r\n**境界**: 元婴后期\r\n**阵营**: 表面正道，实际利己主义\r\n\r\n## 外貌特征\r\n**身高**: 178cm\r\n**体态**: 修长挺拔，仙风道骨\r\n**面容**: 俊朗儒雅，三缕长须\r\n**眼神**: 深邃如潭，时而温和时而锐利\r\n**服饰**: 青色道袍，绣有青云纹饰，头戴玉冠\r\n\r\n## 性格特质\r\n**MBTI人格**: ENTJ（指挥官型）\r\n**核心恐惧**: 失去权力和控制\r\n**欲望**: 追求长生和绝对力量\r\n**道德观**: 功利主义，为达目的不择手段\r\n**优点**: 智慧过人，领导力强，善于谋划\r\n**缺点**: 多疑，冷酷，缺乏真正的同情心\r\n\r\n## 背景故事\r\n**出身**: 原为世俗王朝皇子，因宫廷斗争失败被迫出家\r\n**修真之路**: 机缘巧合得到上古传承，千年苦修成就元婴\r\n**执掌青云宗**: 三百年前击败前任宗主，以铁腕手段整顿宗门\r\n**内心矛盾**: 表面维护正道秩序，实则暗中修炼禁忌功法\r\n\r\n## 能力设定\r\n### 主修功法\r\n- **青云诀**: 宗门传承功法，中正平和，进展缓慢但根基扎实\r\n- **幽冥噬魂功**: 暗中修炼的魔功，可通过吞噬他人修为快速提升\r\n- **天机衍算**: 擅长推演天机，布局长远\r\n\r\n### 法宝\r\n1. **青云剑**: 本命飞剑，七品灵器，可化九道剑光\r\n2. **阴阳镜**: 可窥探他人修为，分辨正邪之气"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":93,"aggregated":"# 青云子 - 角色档案\r\n\r\n## 基本信息\r\n**姓名**: 青云子\r\n**称号**: 青云宗宗主\r\n**年龄**: 外观40岁，实际年龄未知\r\n**性别**: 男\r\n**境界**: 元婴后期\r\n**阵营**: 表面正道，实际利己主义\r\n\r\n## 外貌特征\r\n**身高**: 178cm\r\n**体态**: 修长挺拔，仙风道骨\r\n**面容**: 俊朗儒雅，三缕长须\r\n**眼神**: 深邃如潭，时而温和时而锐利\r\n**服饰**: 青色道袍，绣有青云纹饰，头戴玉冠\r\n\r\n## 性格特质\r\n**MBTI人格**: ENTJ（指挥官型）\r\n**核心恐惧**: 失去权力和控制\r\n**欲望**: 追求长生和绝对力量\r\n**道德观**: 功利主义，为达目的不择手段\r\n**优点**: 智慧过人，领导力强，善于谋划\r\n**缺点**: 多疑，冷酷，缺乏真正的同情心\r\n\r\n## 背景故事\r\n**出身**: 原为世俗王朝皇子，因宫廷斗争失败被迫出家\r\n**修真之路**: 机缘巧合得到上古传承，千年苦修成就元婴\r\n**执掌青云宗**: 三百年前击败前任宗主，以铁腕手段整顿宗门\r\n**内心矛盾**: 表面维护正道秩序，实则暗中修炼禁忌功法\r\n\r\n## 能力设定\r\n### 主修功法\r\n- **青云诀**: 宗门传承功法，中正平和，进展缓慢但根基扎实\r\n- **幽冥噬魂功**: 暗中修炼的魔功，可通过吞噬他人修为快速提升\r\n- **天机衍算**: 擅长推演天机，布局长远\r\n\r\n### 法宝\r\n1. **青云剑**: 本命飞剑，七品灵器，可化九道剑光\r\n2. **阴阳镜**: 可窥探他人修为，分辨正邪之气","cwd":"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/main"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1776149434267}}
{"type":"message","id":"0ce0df59","parentId":"b666b754","timestamp":"2026-04-14T06:50:58.052Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I have a clear picture. `青云子.yaml` is NOT a YAML file at all - it's a Markdown file with `##` headers and `**bold**` syntax. The `**姓名**:` syntax is not valid YAML because `**` is not valid YAML key name characters.\n\nSo `yaml.load()` on `青云子.yaml` will fail. But in `project.js`, the `readCharacters()` function wraps it in a try/catch? Let me check...\n\nActually, looking at the code again:```javascript\nconst char = yaml.load(content);\n```\n\nThere's NO try/catch around this! So if `青云子.yaml` fails to parse, it will throw an error and crash. \n\nBut the error message I saw earlier was \"expected a single document in the stream, but found more\" - that's from js-yaml trying to load `林枫.yaml` with `yaml.load()` and finding multiple documents instead of one. This is the real issue: `林枫.yaml` is valid YAML with two documents separated by `---`, but `yaml.load()` expects a single document, so it throws an error before even getting to `青云子.yaml`.\n\nFor `青云子.yaml`, the error would be different - something like \"unidentified alias\" since `**姓名**:` isn't valid YAML syntax. But the specific error message I got points back to `林枫.yaml`'s multi-document structure being the culprit.\n\nLooking at the `generate-chapter.js` code, `project.readCharacters()` gets called early on line 242, which would fail when trying to parse `林枫.yaml` with `yaml.load()` instead of `yaml.loadAll()`. Let me trace through what's actually happening: the facts files load fine individually, `project.yaml` loads fine, `relationships.yaml` loads fine, but then `project.readCharacters()` hits `林枫.yaml` and crashes. So `yaml.load()` is indeed the problem - it fails on multi-document YAML files like `林枫.yaml`. Both character files have issues: one has multiple documents and the other has invalid YAML syntax. The solution is to either use `yaml.loadAll()` and take the first document, or wrap the parsing in try/catch to handle these edge cases.\n\nI've identified two key bugs: `project.js` doesn't handle multi-document YAML files properly and crashes on invalid YAML, while `generate-chapter.js` has the same vulnerability through `project.readCharacters()`. The `relationships.yaml` file appears to be fine based on our earlier checks. Now I should move on to testing the Electron desktop application to see if it builds successfully.","thinkingSignature":"3fa6247da5b89e973b3956fabd071259a845d9e3df8d3322e741406831112f01"},{"type":"text","text":"好的，第1步深度验证完成，发现了具体 bug。\n\n---\n\n## 汇总：YAML 解析 Bug（已定位）\n\n| 文件 | 问题 | 原因 |\n|------|------|------|\n| `林枫.yaml` | ❌ 多文档 YAML | `---` 分隔导致 `yaml.load()` 失败 |\n| `青云子.yaml` | ❌ 非 YAML 格式 | Markdown 语法（`**姓名**:`），非合法 YAML |\n\n**根因：** `project.js` 的 `readCharacters()` 对所有角色文件统一用 `yaml.load()`，不支持多文档 YAML，且无 try/catch 保护。\n\n---\n\n## 第 3 步：验证 Electron 桌面应用能否编译\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_l2ja17saztq1_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd /mnt/d/aafuzhi/axs && npm run build:renderer 2>&1 | tail -20"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":103580,"output":729,"cacheRead":19262,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":123571,"cost":{"input":0.031073999999999997,"output":0.0008748,"cacheRead":0.0011557199999999998,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.03310452}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776149434282,"responseId":"062d16ba1709be51f5130193a1bca1da"}}
