{"type":"message","id":"2ca51e67","parentId":"670fd017","timestamp":"2026-04-14T06:53:28.020Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_bqru3fqeua4n_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"// 策略3：Markdown 格式解析（青云子.yaml 等）\r\n    // 提取 \"**key**: value\" 格式，转换为 { key: value }\r\n    const mdFields = {};\r\n    const lines = content.split('\\n');\r\n    for (const line of lines) {\r\n      const match = line.match(/^\\*\\*(.+?)\\*\\*:\\s*(.+)$/);\r\n      if (match) {\r\n        const key = match[1].trim();\r\n        let value = match[2].trim();\r\n        // 去掉可能的 Markdown 列表标记和引号\r\n        value = value.replace(/^[-*]\\s*/, '').replace(/^['\"]|['\"]$/g, '').trim();\r\n        mdFields[key] = value;\r\n      }\r\n    }"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":74,"aggregated":"// 策略3：Markdown 格式解析（青云子.yaml 等）\r\n    // 提取 \"**key**: value\" 格式，转换为 { key: value }\r\n    const mdFields = {};\r\n    const lines = content.split('\\n');\r\n    for (const line of lines) {\r\n      const match = line.match(/^\\*\\*(.+?)\\*\\*:\\s*(.+)$/);\r\n      if (match) {\r\n        const key = match[1].trim();\r\n        let value = match[2].trim();\r\n        // 去掉可能的 Markdown 列表标记和引号\r\n        value = value.replace(/^[-*]\\s*/, '').replace(/^['\"]|['\"]$/g, '').trim();\r\n        mdFields[key] = value;\r\n      }\r\n    }","cwd":"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/main"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1776149608007}}
{"type":"message","id":"cd7a9f46","parentId":"2ca51e67","timestamp":"2026-04-14T06:53:38.550Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The issue is that the regex `\\*\\*(.+?)\\*\\*` matches `**` with anything in between, but then `: ` is required. The actual line is `**姓名**: 青云子` - which uses `**` followed by `**` (no, wait it uses `**` correctly). Let me trace through:\n\nLine: `**姓名**: 青云子`\nRegex: `/^\\*\\*(.+?)\\*\\*:\\s*(.+)$/`\n- `^` matches start\n- `\\*\\*` matches `**`\n- `(.+?)` captures `姓名` (non-greedy)\n- `\\*\\*` matches `**`\n- `:` matches the `:` after `**`\n- `\\s*` matches the space after `:`\n- `(.+)` captures `青云子`\n\n\n- `$` matches end\n\nSo this should work! Let me test it directly.","thinkingSignature":"b141b6999a8c10474c36b772cba9300cdeb817b130ba8717951f40d19ecb8f08"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_t2dyqx0bmymk_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"node -e \"\nconst line = '**姓名**: 青云子';\nconst match = line.match(/^\\*\\*(.+?)\\*\\*:\\s*(.+)$/);\nconsole.log('Match:', match ? [match[1], match[2]] : 'NO MATCH');\n\""}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":107160,"output":270,"cacheRead":19262,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":126692,"cost":{"input":0.032147999999999996,"output":0.00032399999999999996,"cacheRead":0.0011557199999999998,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.03362771999999999}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776149608030,"responseId":"062d1768702686321f5761705aede4a9"}}
