{"type":"message","id":"802a3732","parentId":"d6811724","timestamp":"2026-04-14T07:32:31.654Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The actual keys are `style`, `characteristics`, and `example` (not `tone`, `pacing`). So the dialogue.json is actually complete. My check was wrong again. The data is fine.\n\nLet me now verify the actual tool outputs more carefully and check if there are issues.","thinkingSignature":"b5945b7e11592863415f7174c6a6da86b980c256bb8c007eeab40322828b4a82"},{"type":"text","text":"✅ **dialogue.json 完整**（`style/characteristics/example`，非 `tone/pacing`）。\n\n---\n\n## 第 7 步：验证 generate-chapter.js 实际上下文注入\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_i5t993hxi6w5_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"sed -n '280,380p' /mnt/d/aafuzhi/axs/my-novel-tools/bin/generate-chapter.js"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":119639,"output":155,"cacheRead":19262,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":139056,"cost":{"input":0.0358917,"output":0.000186,"cacheRead":0.0011557199999999998,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.037233419999999996}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776151944707,"responseId":"062d2088bc601ee5ca1d5ae3664c9c12"}}
{"type":"message","id":"988be1f8","parentId":"802a3732","timestamp":"2026-04-14T07:32:31.755Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_i5t993hxi6w5_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"// 加载章节摘要\r\n      const { prevSummary, volumeSummary } = loadChapterSummaries(projectPath, options.chapter);\r\n      \r\n      // 格式化摘要为 prompt 文本\r\n      const summariesPrompt = formatSummariesForPrompt(prevSummary, volumeSummary);\r\n      \r\n      // 向量检索（如果启用）\r\n      let vectorPrompt = '';\r\n      if (options.vectorSearch) {\r\n        console.log('正在加载向量索引...');\r\n        const index = new VectorIndex(projectPath);\r\n        const loaded = await index.load();\r\n        if (loaded) {\r\n          console.log(`正在检索与\"${chapterOutline}\"相关的内容...`);\r\n          const results = await index.search(chapterOutline, options.topK);\r\n          vectorPrompt = formatVectorResults(results);\r\n          if (results.length > 0) {\r\n            console.log(`  找到 ${results.length} 条相关记忆`);\r\n          }\r\n        } else {\r\n          console.warn('向量索引不存在，请先运行：node bin/build-vector-index.js -p <项目路径>');\r\n        }\r\n      }\r\n      \r\n      // 读取最近几章作为前情提要\r\n      const recentChapters = project.readRecentChapters(options.chapter, 3);\r\n      let recentSummary = '';\r\n      if (recentChapters.length > 0) {\r\n        recentSummary = `最近${recentChapters.length}章内容概要：\\n`;\r\n        recentChapters.forEach((content, idx) => {\r\n          // 提取前 200 个字符作为概要\r\n          const text = content.replace(/^---[\\s\\S]*?---\\s*\\n/, ''); // 移除 frontmatter\r\n          const summary = text.substring(0, 200) + (text.length > 200 ? '...' : '');\r\n          recentSummary += `第${options.chapter - recentChapters.length + idx}章：${summary}\\n`;\r\n        });\r\n      }\r\n      \r\n      // 构建角色上下文（只提取相关角色，这里简化处理：使用所有角色）\r\n      const charactersContext = allCharacters.map(char => {\r\n        return `角色：${char.name}\r\nMBTI：${char.mbti || '未知'}\r\n核心恐惧：${char.core_fear || '未知'}\r\n关键属性：${JSON.stringify(char.key_attributes || {})}\r\n背景：${char.background || ''}`;\r\n      }).join('\\n\\n');\r\n      \r\n      // 构建关系上下文\r\n      const relationshipsContext = relationships.relationships.map(rel => {\r\n        return `${rel.from} 与 ${rel.to} 是 ${rel.type} 关系，强度 ${rel.strength}`;\r\n      }).join('\\n');\r\n      \r\n      // 构建设定上下文\r\n      const settingsContext = settings.map(setting => {\r\n        return `设定：${setting.name}\\n${setting.content.substring(0, 300)}...`;\r\n      }).join('\\n\\n');\r\n      \r\n      // 构建系统提示词\r\n      const systemPrompt = `你是一位资深网文作者，擅长创作各种类型的小说。\r\n请根据以下项目信息，创作小说的一个章节。\r\n要求：\r\n1. 保持角色性格一致，符合其 MBTI 类型和核心恐惧\r\n2. 遵循世界观设定，不出现矛盾\r\n3. 保持与前文情节的连贯性\r\n4. 注意章节的情绪基调和爽点设置\r\n5. 输出纯文本内容，不要包含 YAML frontmatter\r\n6. 字数在 1500 字左右\r\n\r\n项目信息：\r\n小说标题：${meta.title}\r\n类型：${meta.genre}\r\n作者：${meta.author}`;\r\n      \r\n      // 构建用户提示词\r\n      const userPrompt = `请创作第${options.chapter}章。\r\n\r\n本章大纲：${chapterOutline}\r\n\r\n${recentSummary}${factsPrompt}${summariesPrompt}${vectorPrompt}\r\n\r\n角色信息：\r\n${charactersContext}\r\n\r\n角色关系：\r\n${relationshipsContext}\r\n\r\n世界观设定：\r\n${settingsContext}\r\n\r\n请开始创作本章内容：`;\r\n      \r\n      console.log('正在生成章节内容，请稍候...');\r\n      const content = await ai.call(userPrompt, systemPrompt);\r\n      \r\n      const output = `# 第${options.chapter}章\r\n\r\n${content}`;\r\n      \r\n      if (options.output === 'stdout') {\r\n        console.log(output);\r\n      } else {"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":62,"aggregated":"// 加载章节摘要\r\n      const { prevSummary, volumeSummary } = loadChapterSummaries(projectPath, options.chapter);\r\n      \r\n      // 格式化摘要为 prompt 文本\r\n      const summariesPrompt = formatSummariesForPrompt(prevSummary, volumeSummary);\r\n      \r\n      // 向量检索（如果启用）\r\n      let vectorPrompt = '';\r\n      if (options.vectorSearch) {\r\n        console.log('正在加载向量索引...');\r\n        const index = new VectorIndex(projectPath);\r\n        const loaded = await index.load();\r\n        if (loaded) {\r\n          console.log(`正在检索与\"${chapterOutline}\"相关的内容...`);\r\n          const results = await index.search(chapterOutline, options.topK);\r\n          vectorPrompt = formatVectorResults(results);\r\n          if (results.length > 0) {\r\n            console.log(`  找到 ${results.length} 条相关记忆`);\r\n          }\r\n        } else {\r\n          console.warn('向量索引不存在，请先运行：node bin/build-vector-index.js -p <项目路径>');\r\n        }\r\n      }\r\n      \r\n      // 读取最近几章作为前情提要\r\n      const recentChapters = project.readRecentChapters(options.chapter, 3);\r\n      let recentSummary = '';\r\n      if (recentChapters.length > 0) {\r\n        recentSummary = `最近${recentChapters.length}章内容概要：\\n`;\r\n        recentChapters.forEach((content, idx) => {\r\n          // 提取前 200 个字符作为概要\r\n          const text = content.replace(/^---[\\s\\S]*?---\\s*\\n/, ''); // 移除 frontmatter\r\n          const summary = text.substring(0, 200) + (text.length > 200 ? '...' : '');\r\n          recentSummary += `第${options.chapter - recentChapters.length + idx}章：${summary}\\n`;\r\n        });\r\n      }\r\n      \r\n      // 构建角色上下文（只提取相关角色，这里简化处理：使用所有角色）\r\n      const charactersContext = allCharacters.map(char => {\r\n        return `角色：${char.name}\r\nMBTI：${char.mbti || '未知'}\r\n核心恐惧：${char.core_fear || '未知'}\r\n关键属性：${JSON.stringify(char.key_attributes || {})}\r\n背景：${char.background || ''}`;\r\n      }).join('\\n\\n');\r\n      \r\n      // 构建关系上下文\r\n      const relationshipsContext = relationships.relationships.map(rel => {\r\n        return `${rel.from} 与 ${rel.to} 是 ${rel.type} 关系，强度 ${rel.strength}`;\r\n      }).join('\\n');\r\n      \r\n      // 构建设定上下文\r\n      const settingsContext = settings.map(setting => {\r\n        return `设定：${setting.name}\\n${setting.content.substring(0, 300)}...`;\r\n      }).join('\\n\\n');\r\n      \r\n      // 构建系统提示词\r\n      const systemPrompt = `你是一位资深网文作者，擅长创作各种类型的小说。\r\n请根据以下项目信息，创作小说的一个章节。\r\n要求：\r\n1. 保持角色性格一致，符合其 MBTI 类型和核心恐惧\r\n2. 遵循世界观设定，不出现矛盾\r\n3. 保持与前文情节的连贯性\r\n4. 注意章节的情绪基调和爽点设置\r\n5. 输出纯文本内容，不要包含 YAML frontmatter\r\n6. 字数在 1500 字左右\r\n\r\n项目信息：\r\n小说标题：${meta.title}\r\n类型：${meta.genre}\r\n作者：${meta.author}`;\r\n      \r\n      // 构建用户提示词\r\n      const userPrompt = `请创作第${options.chapter}章。\r\n\r\n本章大纲：${chapterOutline}\r\n\r\n${recentSummary}${factsPrompt}${summariesPrompt}${vectorPrompt}\r\n\r\n角色信息：\r\n${charactersContext}\r\n\r\n角色关系：\r\n${relationshipsContext}\r\n\r\n世界观设定：\r\n${settingsContext}\r\n\r\n请开始创作本章内容：`;\r\n      \r\n      console.log('正在生成章节内容，请稍候...');\r\n      const content = await ai.call(userPrompt, systemPrompt);\r\n      \r\n      const output = `# 第${options.chapter}章\r\n\r\n${content}`;\r\n      \r\n      if (options.output === 'stdout') {\r\n        console.log(output);\r\n      } else {","cwd":"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/main"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1776151951743}}
{"type":"message","id":"bb98450b","parentId":"988be1f8","timestamp":"2026-04-14T07:32:44.355Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I see several issues with the generate-chapter.js:\n\n1. **No character name for 林枫.yaml** - The `_parseCharacterContent` for 林枫 returns `{\"name\":\"林枫\",...}` but wait, actually `林枫.yaml` first doc has `name: 林枫`. But `青云子.yaml` has no `name` field in its markdown format - it has `**姓名**: 青云子` which would map to `姓名`. So `readCharacters()` would return `林枫` with `name` field but `青云子` with `姓名` field instead of `name`.\n   \n2. **The character context uses `char.name`** which would be undefined for 青云子. And the MBTI field might also be missing for 青云子 since it stores `**MBTI人格**: ENTJ` instead. Plus, if `loadFacts()` fails it just logs a warning, so the facts context could be empty without affecting the generation.","thinkingSignature":"5b22913cb35880814d9bfae1fce2ab1497dec0a3d32b4772e4abc54c08321aff"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_gx0snh8kz6jq_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"node -e \"\nconst Project = require('/mnt/d/aafuzhi/axs/my-novel-tools/lib/project');\nconst p = new Project('/mnt/d/aafuzhi/axs/my-novel');\nconst chars = p.readCharacters();\nchars.forEach(c => {\n  console.log('角色: name=' + c.name + ' | 姓名=' + c['姓名'] + ' | mbti=' + c.mbti + ' | MBTI人格=' + c['MBTI人格']);\n});\n\""}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":120699,"output":330,"cacheRead":19262,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":140291,"cost":{"input":0.0362097,"output":0.000396,"cacheRead":0.0011557199999999998,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.03776142}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776151951758,"responseId":"062d208fdadd22acc39975e122cb063b"}}
