{"type":"message","id":"f6fdac27","parentId":"aee58a3a","timestamp":"2026-04-14T07:32:55.316Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"This is a critical bug! The `_parseCharacterContent` correctly parses both formats, but:\n- 林枫.yaml → has `name` and `mbti` fields ✅\n- 青云子.yaml → has `姓名` and `MBTI人格` fields, no `name` and no `mbti` field!\n\nSo when `generate-chapter.js` builds the character context using `char.name` and `char.mbti`, it will:\n- For 林枫: ✅ name=林枫, mbti=INTJ\n- For 青云子: ❌ name=undefined, mbti=undefined\n\n\nThe character context for 青云子 would show as empty with undefined values. Now I need to check how the context injection handles this and whether the facts台账 is properly feeding into the prompt.","thinkingSignature":"0cec509929c2bcfd5f27d4466cc984e98f1902fd6eeaf3091dccbd79ca8b704a"},{"type":"text","text":"**🔴 发现 P0 bug：青云子角色上下文为空**\n\n```\n林枫 → name=林枫, mbti=INTJ ✅\n青云子 → name=undefined, mbti=undefined ❌（**姓名** 和 **MBTI人格** 未映射）\n```\n\n---\n\n## 第 8 步：验证 facts 注入 generate-chapter 的实际流程\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_3mjtkbi5ljz4_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"sed -n '60,130p' /mnt/d/aafuzhi/axs/my-novel-tools/bin/generate-chapter.js"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":121098,"output":302,"cacheRead":19262,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":140662,"cost":{"input":0.0363294,"output":0.00036239999999999997,"cacheRead":0.0011557199999999998,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.037847519999999996}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776151965478,"responseId":"062d209c504c12db2df8c6bbadcd7cb2"}}
{"type":"message","id":"798a2df8","parentId":"f6fdac27","timestamp":"2026-04-14T07:32:55.440Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_3mjtkbi5ljz4_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"plots: []\r\n  };\r\n  \r\n  // 提取角色名\r\n  const charNames = Object.keys(facts.characters || {});\r\n  for (const name of charNames) {\r\n    if (outline.includes(name)) {\r\n      keywords.characters.push(name);\r\n    }\r\n  }\r\n  \r\n  // 提取地名/设定名\r\n  const settingNames = Object.keys(facts.settings || {});\r\n  for (const name of settingNames) {\r\n    if (outline.includes(name)) {\r\n      keywords.settings.push(name);\r\n    }\r\n  }\r\n  \r\n  return keywords;\r\n}\r\n\r\n// 格式化事实为文本注入到 prompt\r\nfunction formatFactsForPrompt(keywords, facts) {\r\n  let promptText = '';\r\n  \r\n  // 注入相关角色事实\r\n  if (keywords.characters.length > 0 && facts.characters) {\r\n    promptText += '\\n【相关角色事实】\\n';\r\n    for (const charName of keywords.characters) {\r\n      const char = facts.characters[charName];\r\n      if (char) {\r\n        promptText += `- ${charName}：${char.mbti || '未知'}，核心恐惧：${char.core_fear || '未知'}，能力：${(char.abilities || []).join('、') || '无'}，目标：${char.goal || '未知'}\\n`;\r\n        if (char.relationships) {\r\n          for (const [other, relation] of Object.entries(char.relationships)) {\r\n            if (keywords.characters.includes(other)) {\r\n              promptText += `  与${other}关系：${relation}\\n`;\r\n            }\r\n          }\r\n        }\r\n      }\r\n    }\r\n  }\r\n  \r\n  // 注入相关设定事实\r\n  if (keywords.settings.length > 0 && facts.settings) {\r\n    promptText += '\\n【相关设定事实】\\n';\r\n    for (const settingName of keywords.settings) {\r\n      const setting = facts.settings[settingName];\r\n      if (setting) {\r\n        promptText += `- ${settingName}：${setting.description || '无描述'}，规则：${(setting.rules || []).join(';') || '无特殊规则'}\\n`;\r\n      }\r\n    }\r\n  }\r\n  \r\n  // 注入相关伏笔\r\n  if (facts.plots && facts.plots.伏笔清单) {\r\n    const activeForeshadowing = facts.plots.伏笔清单.filter(f => f.status === '未回收');\r\n    if (activeForeshadowing.length > 0) {\r\n      promptText += '\\n【未回收伏笔】\\n';\r\n      for (const fb of activeForeshadowing) {\r\n        promptText += `- ${fb.description}（铺设于第${fb.setup_chapter || '?'}章）\\n`;\r\n      }\r\n    }\r\n  }\r\n  \r\n  return promptText;\r\n}\r\n\r\n// 加载章节摘要\r\nfunction loadChapterSummaries(projectPath, chapterNum) {"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":71,"aggregated":"plots: []\r\n  };\r\n  \r\n  // 提取角色名\r\n  const charNames = Object.keys(facts.characters || {});\r\n  for (const name of charNames) {\r\n    if (outline.includes(name)) {\r\n      keywords.characters.push(name);\r\n    }\r\n  }\r\n  \r\n  // 提取地名/设定名\r\n  const settingNames = Object.keys(facts.settings || {});\r\n  for (const name of settingNames) {\r\n    if (outline.includes(name)) {\r\n      keywords.settings.push(name);\r\n    }\r\n  }\r\n  \r\n  return keywords;\r\n}\r\n\r\n// 格式化事实为文本注入到 prompt\r\nfunction formatFactsForPrompt(keywords, facts) {\r\n  let promptText = '';\r\n  \r\n  // 注入相关角色事实\r\n  if (keywords.characters.length > 0 && facts.characters) {\r\n    promptText += '\\n【相关角色事实】\\n';\r\n    for (const charName of keywords.characters) {\r\n      const char = facts.characters[charName];\r\n      if (char) {\r\n        promptText += `- ${charName}：${char.mbti || '未知'}，核心恐惧：${char.core_fear || '未知'}，能力：${(char.abilities || []).join('、') || '无'}，目标：${char.goal || '未知'}\\n`;\r\n        if (char.relationships) {\r\n          for (const [other, relation] of Object.entries(char.relationships)) {\r\n            if (keywords.characters.includes(other)) {\r\n              promptText += `  与${other}关系：${relation}\\n`;\r\n            }\r\n          }\r\n        }\r\n      }\r\n    }\r\n  }\r\n  \r\n  // 注入相关设定事实\r\n  if (keywords.settings.length > 0 && facts.settings) {\r\n    promptText += '\\n【相关设定事实】\\n';\r\n    for (const settingName of keywords.settings) {\r\n      const setting = facts.settings[settingName];\r\n      if (setting) {\r\n        promptText += `- ${settingName}：${setting.description || '无描述'}，规则：${(setting.rules || []).join(';') || '无特殊规则'}\\n`;\r\n      }\r\n    }\r\n  }\r\n  \r\n  // 注入相关伏笔\r\n  if (facts.plots && facts.plots.伏笔清单) {\r\n    const activeForeshadowing = facts.plots.伏笔清单.filter(f => f.status === '未回收');\r\n    if (activeForeshadowing.length > 0) {\r\n      promptText += '\\n【未回收伏笔】\\n';\r\n      for (const fb of activeForeshadowing) {\r\n        promptText += `- ${fb.description}（铺设于第${fb.setup_chapter || '?'}章）\\n`;\r\n      }\r\n    }\r\n  }\r\n  \r\n  return promptText;\r\n}\r\n\r\n// 加载章节摘要\r\nfunction loadChapterSummaries(projectPath, chapterNum) {","cwd":"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/main"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1776151975430}}
{"type":"message","id":"7b39ab57","parentId":"798a2df8","timestamp":"2026-04-14T07:33:16.720Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I can see the facts system works as:\n1. `loadFacts()` reads the three YAML files and creates a `facts` object\n2. `extractKeywords()` finds relevant character/setting names in the outline\n3. `formatFactsForPrompt()` formats the relevant facts into the prompt\n\nBut the issue is: `extractKeywords()` uses `outline.includes(name)` to find relevant characters. If the outline is \"林枫重生归来\" and the characters_facts.yaml has `林枫` as a top-level key, it will match. But the facts uses the top-level key names (林枫, 青云子) which should match.\n\n\nThe real problem is that `characters_facts.yaml` stores characters as top-level keys like `林枫:` and `青云子:`, while `characters_facts.yaml` stores them as nested objects under a `characters:` key. So the `loadFacts()` function needs to read the YAML with the correct structure to access the character data properly. facts_path);\n  if (fs.existsSync(facts_path)) {\n    try {\n      facts.characters = yaml.load(fs.readFileSync(facts_path, 'utf-8'));\n    } catch (e) {\n      console.warn('读取角色事实台账失败:', e.message);\n    }\n  }\n\n  const settings_facts_path = path.join(projectPath, 'facts', 'settings_facts.yaml');\n  if (fs.existsSync(settings_facts_path)) {\n    try {\n      facts.settings = yaml.load(fs.readFileSync(settings_facts_path, 'utf-8'));\n    } catch (e) {\n      console.warn('读取设定事实台账失败:', e.message);\n    }\n  }\n\nSo `facts.characters` ends up with the YAML document's root object directly, which means the characters like 林枫 and 青云子 are top-level keys within that object.\n\nThe `extractKeywords()` function searches through those top-level keys to find character names mentioned in the outline. And `formatFactsForPrompt()` accesses the character data using those same top-level keys like `facts.characters['林枫']` to format their information for the prompt. I'm seeing the issue now—the YAML structure has nested keys like `林枫.abilities` and `林枫.important_events`, but the prompt formatting code is trying to access them as if they're top-level properties, which would cause the variable references to be undefined when the prompt is generated.\n\nI need to trace through how the facts YAML is actually structured and whether the `loadFacts()` function properly flattens or preserves the nested hierarchy when loading character data.","thinkingSignature":"ea35ccd32582220242114ef91570d8155f3a81ad4ab4288e5fe694e5a608e193"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_kr3hocdyzdv9_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"node -e \"\nconst yaml = require('/mnt/d/aafuzhi/axs/my-novel-tools/node_modules/js-yaml');\nconst fs = require('fs');\nconst content = fs.readFileSync('/mnt/d/aafuzhi/axs/my-novel/facts/characters_facts.yaml', 'utf8');\nconst facts = yaml.load(content);\nconsole.log('顶层keys:', Object.keys(facts));\nconsole.log('林枫 keys:', Object.keys(facts['林枫']));\nconsole.log('林枫 abilities:', facts['林枫'].abilities);\nconsole.log('林枫 relationships:', facts['林枫'].relationships);\n\""}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":122025,"output":684,"cacheRead":19262,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":141971,"cost":{"input":0.0366075,"output":0.0008208,"cacheRead":0.0011557199999999998,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.03858402}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776151975444,"responseId":"062d20a7b834c077eb4dfe39094eb9f5"}}
