{"type":"message","id":"c4d431d2","parentId":"872aa5b7","timestamp":"2026-04-14T07:41:14.246Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The compiled `dist/main/index.js` does NOT have the aiService/backupService references. This means either:\n1. The source `src/main/index.ts` was different when compiled\n2. The current `src/main/index.ts` has these references added but hasn't been compiled yet\n\nWait - I ran `npm run build:renderer` earlier and it succeeded. But `build:electron` wasn't run. The `tsc` compilation for electron main hasn't been done since these new references were added.\n\nLet me re-read the source `src/main/index.ts` to make sure my reading is current. The tail showed:\n```\nconst { setupAiHandlers } = require('./aiService')\n\n\nsetupAiHandlers(ipcMain)\n```\nand\n```\nconst { setupBackupHandlers } = require('./backupService')\nsetupBackupHandlers(ipcMain)\n```\n\nBut the compiled JS doesn't have these. This means either the TS source was modified after compilation OR I'm misreading something.\n\nWait - could it be that the `index.ts` source I read earlier had those lines, but those lines were added AFTER the last compilation? And the `dist/` version is stale?\n\nThe key question: when I try to run `npm run dev:electron`, will it fail? The current `src/main/index.ts` has requires for non-existent modules, so it SHOULD fail on compilation.\n\nLet me think about this differently. Rather than spend more time investigating the compilation issue, I should just fix the root problem: create the missing `aiService.ts` and `backupService.ts` modules that the current source code expects. The compiled output doesn't matter if the source is actively calling non-existent modules - that's the actual issue I need to address. I should stop analyzing why the compiled files are out of sync and just create those missing service modules to match what the current TypeScript source is trying to require. I'm going to focus on fixing the actual issues: creating the missing `aiService.ts` and `backupService.ts` modules, plus correcting the character field mapping in `generate-chapter.js`.","thinkingSignature":"e5570c6ad5cccc962916d261fd528076efe2c0bb57cb5489642e3b31b4770ae9"},{"type":"text","text":"**🔴 重大发现：** `src/main/index.ts` 引用了不存在的 `./aiService` 和 `./backupService`，但 `dist/main/index.js` 里没有——说明源码被改过、还没重新编译。\n\n---\n\n## 第 1 步：创建 `src/main/aiService.ts`\n\n**思考：** AI 服务需要：① 存储 API keys（加密）② 实现 `call` 和 `stream` 方法 ③ 调用 DeepSeek/豆包 API。参考 `lib/ai.js` 的实现，用 `@direct` 标签方式处理 SSE 流式响应。\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_qujleimfcz3x_1","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"/mnt/d/aafuzhi/axs/src/main/aiService.ts","content":"/**\n * AI 服务 - 主进程 IPC 处理器\n * 处理渲染进程发来的 AI 相关 IPC 调用\n */\n\nimport { IpcMain, BrowserWindow } from 'electron'\nimport axios, { AxiosError } from 'axios'\nimport fs from 'node:fs'\nimport path from 'node:path'\nimport os from 'node:os'\nimport { app } from 'electron'\n\n// ─── 配置路径 ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────\n\nfunction getSettingsPath(): string {\n  return path.join(app.getPath('userData'), 'ai-settings.json')\n}\n\n// ─── 配置读写 ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────\n\ninterface AiSettings {\n  deepseekApiKey?: string\n  doubaoApiKey?: string\n  [key: string]: string | undefined\n}\n\nfunction loadSettings(): AiSettings {\n  const p = getSettingsPath()\n  if (fs.existsSync(p)) {\n    try {\n      return JSON.parse(fs.readFileSync(p, 'utf-8'))\n    } catch {\n      return {}\n    }\n  }\n  return {}\n}\n\nfunction saveSettings(settings: AiSettings): void {\n  const p = getSettingsPath()\n  fs.mkdirSync(path.dirname(p), { recursive: true })\n  fs.writeFileSync(p, JSON.stringify(settings, null, 2), 'utf-8')\n}\n\n// ─── API 调用 ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────\n\ninterface CallOptions {\n  model?: string\n  systemPrompt?: string\n  temperature?: number\n  maxTokens?: number\n  topP?: number\n  presencePenalty?: number\n  frequencyPenalty?: number\n}\n\nasync function callAI(\n  prompt: string,\n  options: CallOptions = {}\n): Promise<{ success: boolean; content?: string; reasoning?: string; error?: string }> {\n  const { model = 'deepseek', systemPrompt, temperature = 0.7, maxTokens = 2000 } = options\n\n  const apiKey = loadSettings()[`${model}ApiKey`]\n    || process.env.DEEPSEEK_API_KEY\n    || process.env.DOUBAO_API_KEY\n\n  if (!apiKey) {\n    return {\n      success: false,\n      error: `未配置 API Key。请先在设置中配置 ${model} 的 API Key。`,\n    }\n  }\n\n  try {\n    if (model === 'deepseek' || model === 'deepseek-chat') {\n      const response = await axios.post(\n        'https://api.deepseek.com/v1/chat/completions',\n        {\n          model: 'deepseek-chat',\n          messages: [\n            ...(systemPrompt ? [{ role: 'system', content: systemPrompt }] : []),\n            { role: 'user', content: prompt },\n          ],\n          temperature,\n          max_tokens: maxTokens,\n        },\n        {\n          headers: {\n            Authorization: `Bearer ${apiKey}`,\n            'Content-Type': 'application/json',\n          },\n          timeout: 60000,\n        }\n      )\n      return { success: true, content: response.data.choices[0]?.message?.content || '' }\n    }\n\n    if (model === 'doubao-pro' || model === 'doubao-lite' || model === 'doubao-mini') {\n      const endpoint = model === 'doubao-pro'\n        ? 'https://ark.cn-beijing.volces.com/api/v3/chat/completions'\n        : 'https://ark.cn-beijing.volces.com/api/v3/chat/completions'\n\n      const doubaoModel = model === 'doubao-pro'\n        ? 'doubao-pro-32k'\n        : model === 'doubao-lite'\n          ? 'doubao-lite-32k'\n          : 'doubao-mini'\n\n      const response = await axios.post(\n        endpoint,\n        {\n          model: doubaoModel,\n          messages: [\n            ...(systemPrompt ? [{ role: 'system', content: systemPrompt }] : []),\n            { role: 'user', content: prompt },\n          ],\n          temperature,\n          max_tokens: maxTokens,\n        },\n        {\n          headers: {\n            Authorization: `Bearer ${apiKey}`,\n            'Content-Type': 'application/json',\n          },\n          timeout: 60000,\n        }\n      )\n      return { success: true, content: response.data.choices[0]?.message?.content || '' }\n    }\n\n    return { success: false, error: `不支持的模型: ${model}` }\n  } catch (err) {\n    const axiosErr = err as AxiosError\n    if (axiosErr.response) {\n      return { success: false, error: `API 错误 ${axiosErr.response.status}: ${JSON.stringify(axiosErr.response.data)}` }\n    }\n    return { success: false, error: `请求失败: ${axiosErr.message}` }\n  }\n}\n\nasync function streamAI(\n  prompt: string,\n  options: CallOptions,\n  sendChunk: (content: string, done: boolean, reasoning?: string) => void,\n  sendError: (error: string) => void\n): Promise<void> {\n  const { model = 'deepseek', systemPrompt, temperature = 0.7, maxTokens = 2000 } = options\n\n  const apiKey = loadSettings()[`${model}ApiKey`]\n    || process.env.DEEPSEEK_API_KEY\n    || process.env.DOUBAO_API_KEY\n\n  if (!apiKey) {\n    sendError(`未配置 API Key。请先在设置中配置 ${model} 的 API Key。`)\n    sendChunk('', true)\n    return\n  }\n\n  try {\n    const headers: Record<string, string> = {\n      'Content-Type': 'application/json',\n      Authorization: `Bearer ${apiKey}`,\n    }\n\n    const body: Record<string, unknown> = {\n      model: model === 'deepseek' || model === 'deepseek-chat' ? 'deepseek-chat' : 'doubao-pro-32k',\n      messages: [\n        ...(systemPrompt ? [{ role: 'system', content: systemPrompt }] : []),\n        { role: 'user', content: prompt },\n      ],\n      temperature,\n      max_tokens: maxTokens,\n    }\n\n    // DeepSeek 支持流式\n    if (model === 'deepseek' || model === 'deepseek-chat') {\n      body.stream = true\n\n      const response = await axios.post(\n        'https://api.deepseek.com/v1/chat/completions',\n        body,\n        {\n          headers,\n          responseType: 'stream',\n          timeout: 120000,\n        }\n      )\n\n      const stream = response.data as import('node:stream').Stream\n      let buffer = ''\n\n      await new Promise<void>((resolve, reject) => {\n        stream.on('data', (chunk: Buffer) => {\n          buffer += chunk.toString()\n          const lines = buffer.split('\\n')\n          buffer = lines.pop() || ''\n\n          for (const line of lines) {\n            const trimmed = line.trim()\n            if (!trimmed || trimmed === 'data: [DONE]') continue\n            if (!trimmed.startsWith('data: ')) continue\n            const data = trimmed.slice(6)\n            try {\n              const parsed = JSON.parse(data)\n              const content = parsed.choices?.[0]?.delta?.content || ''\n              const reasoning = parsed.choices?.[0]?.delta?.reasoning || ''\n              if (content || reasoning) {\n                sendChunk(content, false, reasoning)\n              }\n            } catch {}\n          }\n        })\n\n        stream.on('end', () => {\n          if (buffer.trim() && buffer.trim() !== '[DONE]') {\n            try {\n              const data = JSON.parse(buffer.slice(6))\n              const content = data.choices?.[0]?.delta?.content || ''\n              if (content) sendChunk(content, false)\n            } catch {}\n          }\n          sendChunk('', true)\n          resolve()\n        })\n\n        stream.on('error', (err: Error) => {\n          sendError(err.message)\n          sendChunk('', true)\n          resolve()\n        })\n      })\n    } else {\n      // 非流式降级\n      const result = await callAI(prompt, options)\n      if (result.success) {\n        sendChunk(result.content || '', false)\n        sendChunk('', true)\n      } else {\n        sendError(result.error || '未知错误')\n        sendChunk('', true)\n      }\n    }\n  } catch (err) {\n    const axiosErr = err as AxiosError\n    sendError(axiosErr.message || '请求失败')\n    sendChunk('', true)\n  }\n}\n\n// ─── IPC 处理器 ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────\n\nexport function setupAiHandlers(ipcMain: IpcMain): void {\n  // 保存 API Key\n  ipcMain.handle('ai:saveApiKey', async (_event, service: string, apiKey: string) => {\n    try {\n      const settings = loadSettings()\n      settings[`${service}ApiKey`] = apiKey\n      saveSettings(settings)\n      return { success: true }\n    } catch (e: any) {\n      return { success: false, error: e.message }\n    }\n  })\n\n  // 检查是否已配置\n  ipcMain.handle('ai:isConfigured', async (_event, service: string) => {\n    const settings = loadSettings()\n    const configured = !!(settings[`${service}ApiKey`] || process.env[`${service.toUpperCase()}_API_KEY`])\n    return { success: true, configured }\n  })\n\n  // 获取已配置的服务列表\n  ipcMain.handle('ai:getConfiguredServices', async () => {\n    const settings = loadSettings()\n    const services: string[] = []\n    if (settings.deepseekApiKey || process.env.DEEPSEEK_API_KEY) services.push('deepseek')\n    if (settings.doubaoApiKey || process.env.DOUBAO_API_KEY) services.push('doubao')\n    return { success: true, services }\n  })\n\n  // AI 调用（非流式）\n  ipcMain.handle('ai:call', async (_event, prompt: string, options?: CallOptions) => {\n    return callAI(prompt, options || {})\n  })\n\n  // AI 流式调用\n  ipcMain.handle('ai:stream', async (event, prompt: string, options?: CallOptions) => {\n    const win = BrowserWindow.fromWebContents(event.sender)\n    if (!win || win.isDestroyed()) return { success: false, error: '窗口已关闭' }\n\n    await streamAI(\n      prompt,\n      options || {},\n      (content, done, reasoning) => {\n        if (!win.isDestroyed()) {\n          win.webContents.send('ai:stream-chunk', { content, done, reasoning })\n        }\n      },\n      (error) => {\n        if (!win.isDestroyed()) {\n          win.webContents.send('ai:stream-error', error)\n        }\n      }\n    )\n\n    return { success: true }\n  })\n\n  // 测试连接\n  ipcMain.handle('ai:testConnection', async (_event, service: string) => {\n    const testPrompt = '请回复\"连接成功\"，不需要其他内容。'\n    const result = await callAI(testPrompt, { model: service, maxTokens: 50 })\n    return { success: result.success, result: result.success, error: result.error }\n  })\n\n  // 保存设置\n  ipcMain.handle('ai:saveSetting', async (_event, key: string, value: any) => {\n    try {\n      const settings = loadSettings()\n      settings[key] = value\n      saveSettings(settings)\n      return { success: true }\n    } catch (e: any) {\n      return { success: false, error: e.message }\n    }\n  })\n\n  // 读取设置\n  ipcMain.handle('ai:getSetting', async (_event, key: string, defaultValue?: any) => {\n    const settings = loadSettings()\n    return { success: true, value: settings[key] ?? defaultValue }\n  })\n}\n"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":34389,"output":3119,"cacheRead":19262,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":56770,"cost":{"input":0.0103167,"output":0.0037427999999999997,"cacheRead":0.0011557199999999998,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.015215219999999998}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776152405582,"responseId":"062d2255ccab471b1cc18437a4fac7ba"}}
