{"type":"message","id":"e7e478cb","parentId":"934d172c","timestamp":"2026-04-14T07:45:14.986Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Let me read the full file.","thinkingSignature":"773d4f8da1ce5cbcadc548dde01ba84fc058a0cdff41cf1364d2c454ca68f0d9"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_bpl00pcelvtw_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/mnt/d/aafuzhi/axs/src/renderer/src/components/Workbench.tsx"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":42451,"output":52,"cacheRead":19262,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":61765,"cost":{"input":0.0127353,"output":0.0000624,"cacheRead":0.0011557199999999998,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.013953420000000001}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776152711828,"responseId":"062d23873c1ace653b6679b95910318a"}}
{"type":"message","id":"3c52d282","parentId":"e7e478cb","timestamp":"2026-04-14T07:45:15.080Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_bpl00pcelvtw_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"import { useState, useEffect } from 'react'\nimport { Layout, Menu, Button, message } from 'antd'\nimport {\n  SaveOutlined,\n  FolderOpenOutlined,\n  BookOutlined,\n  UserOutlined,\n  SettingOutlined,\n  ThunderboltOutlined\n} from '@ant-design/icons'\nimport OutlineTree from './OutlineTree'\nimport Editor from './Editor'\nimport FactsPanel from './FactsPanel'\nimport AIToolsPanel from './AIToolsPanel'\nimport type { MenuProps } from 'antd'\n\nconst { Sider, Content } = Layout\n\ntype TabKey = 'outline' | 'characters' | 'settings' | 'facts' | 'ai'\n\n// 左侧菜单\nconst siderMenuItems: MenuProps['items'] = [\n  { key: 'outline', icon: <BookOutlined />, label: '大纲导航' },\n  { key: 'characters', icon: <UserOutlined />, label: '角色管理' },\n  { key: 'settings', icon: <SettingOutlined />, label: '世界设定' },\n  { key: 'facts', icon: <ThunderboltOutlined />, label: '事实台账' },\n]\n\nconst Workbench = () => {\n  const [activeTab, setActiveTab] = useState<TabKey>('outline')\n  const [activeChapter, setActiveChapter] = useState<string | null>(null)\n  const [chapterContent, setChapterContent] = useState('')\n  const [projectRoot, setProjectRoot] = useState<string | null>(null)\n  const [isDirty, setIsDirty] = useState(false)\n  const [autoSaveTimer, setAutoSaveTimer] = useState<NodeJS.Timeout | null>(null)\n\n  // 初始化项目\n  useEffect(() => {\n    const init = async () => {\n      const root = await window.electronAPI.getProjectRoot()\n      setProjectRoot(root)\n    }\n    init()\n  }, [])\n\n  // 自动保存\n  useEffect(() => {\n    if (isDirty && activeChapter) {\n      if (autoSaveTimer) clearTimeout(autoSaveTimer)\n      \n      const timer = setTimeout(() => {\n        handleSave()\n      }, 5000) // 5秒防抖自动保存\n      \n      setAutoSaveTimer(timer)\n    }\n\n    return () => {\n      if (autoSaveTimer) clearTimeout(autoSaveTimer)\n    }\n  }, [chapterContent, isDirty])\n\n  // 打开项目\n  const handleOpenProject = async () => {\n    const directory = await window.electronAPI.openDirectory()\n    if (directory) {\n      setProjectRoot(directory)\n      message.success(`已打开项目：${directory}`)\n    }\n  }\n\n  // 保存章节\n  const handleSave = async () => {\n    if (!activeChapter || !chapterContent) return\n\n    try {\n      const result = await window.electronAPI.writeFile(activeChapter, chapterContent)\n      if (result.success) {\n        setIsDirty(false)\n        message.success('已保存')\n      } else {\n        message.error(`保存失败：${result.error}`)\n      }\n    } catch (error) {\n      message.error('保存失败')\n    }\n  }\n\n  // 章节选择\n  const handleChapterSelect = async (filePath: string) => {\n    if (isDirty) {\n      // 提示保存\n      const confirm = window.confirm('当前章节有未保存的内容，是否保存？')\n      if (confirm) await handleSave()\n    }\n\n    setActiveChapter(filePath)\n    \n    // 读取章节内容\n    try {\n      const result = await window.electronAPI.readFile(filePath)\n      if (result.success && result.content) {\n        setChapterContent(result.content)\n        setIsDirty(false)\n      }\n    } catch (error) {\n      message.error('读取章节失败')\n    }\n  }\n\n  // 内容变化\n  const handleContentChange = (value: string | undefined) => {\n    if (value === undefined) return\n    setChapterContent(value)\n    setIsDirty(true)\n  }\n\n  // 快捷键保存\n  useEffect(() => {\n    const handleKeyDown = (e: KeyboardEvent) => {\n      if ((e.ctrlKey || e.metaKey) && e.key === 's') {\n        e.preventDefault()\n        handleSave()\n      }\n    }\n    window.addEventListener('keydown', handleKeyDown)\n    return () => window.removeEventListener('keydown', handleKeyDown)\n  }, [activeChapter, chapterContent])\n\n  return (\n    <Layout style={{ height: '100vh' }}>\n      {/* 顶部工具栏 */}\n      <Layout.Header\n        style={{\n          display: 'flex',\n          alignItems: 'center',\n          padding: '0 20px',\n          background: '#fff',\n          borderBottom: '1px solid #e8e8e8',\n          justifyContent: 'space-between'\n        }}\n      >\n        <div style={{ display: 'flex', alignItems: 'center', gap: 20 }}>\n          <h2 style={{ margin: 0 }}>🍅 番茄小说创作助手</h2>\n          {projectRoot && <span style={{ color: '#999' }}>当前项目：{projectRoot}</span>}\n        </div>\n        <div style={{ display: 'flex', gap: 10 }}>\n          <Button\n            icon={<FolderOpenOutlined />}\n            onClick={handleOpenProject}\n          >\n            打开项目\n          </Button>\n          <Button\n            icon={<SaveOutlined />}\n            type=\"primary\"\n            onClick={handleSave}\n            disabled={!isDirty || !activeChapter}\n          >\n            保存 {isDirty ? '*' : ''}\n          </Button>\n        </div>\n      </Layout.Header>\n\n      <Layout>\n        {/* 左侧边栏 */}\n        <Sider width={64} theme=\"light\">\n          <Menu\n            mode=\"inline\"\n            selectedKeys={[activeTab]}\n            items={siderMenuItems}\n            onClick={({ key }) => setActiveTab(key as TabKey)}\n            style={{ height: '100%', borderRight: 0 }}\n          />\n        </Sider>\n\n        {/* 左侧内容区 */}\n        <Sider width={280} theme=\"light\" style={{ borderRight: '1px solid #e8e8e8' }}>\n          {activeTab === 'outline' && projectRoot && (\n            <OutlineTree\n              projectRoot={projectRoot}\n              activeChapter={activeChapter}\n              onSelect={handleChapterSelect}\n            />\n          )}\n          {activeTab === 'characters' && <div>角色管理（开发中）</div>}\n          {activeTab === 'settings' && <div>世界设定（开发中）</div>}\n          {activeTab === 'facts' && <FactsPanel />}\n        </Sider>\n\n        {/* 中间编辑区 */}\n        <Content style={{ background: '#fff' }}>\n          {activeChapter ? (\n            <Editor\n              value={chapterContent}\n              onChange={handleContentChange}\n              filePath={activeChapter}\n            />\n          ) : (\n            <div\n              style={{\n                display: 'flex',\n                height: '100%',\n                alignItems: 'center',\n                justifyContent: 'center',\n                color: '#999',\n                fontSize: 18,\n              }}\n            >\n              请在左侧选择章节，或打开一个小说项目\n            </div>\n          )}\n        </Content>\n\n        {/* 右侧AI工具区 */}\n        <Sider width={320} theme=\"light\" style={{ borderLeft: '1px solid #e8e8e8' }}>\n          <AIToolsPanel\n            chapterContent={chapterContent}\n            chapterPath={activeChapter}\n            onInsertText={(text) => {\n              // 插入到编辑器光标位置\n              setChapterContent(prev => prev + text)\n              setIsDirty(true)\n            }}\n          />\n        </Sider>\n      </Layout>\n    </Layout>\n  )\n}\n\nexport default Workbench\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1776152715070}}
{"type":"message","id":"a0809fac","parentId":"3c52d282","timestamp":"2026-04-14T07:45:19.785Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"error","timestamp":1776152715085,"errorMessage":"529 {\"type\":\"error\",\"error\":{\"type\":\"overloaded_error\",\"message\":\"当前服务集群负载较高，请稍后重试，感谢您的耐心等待。 (2064) (529)\"},\"request_id\":\"062d238eb7f0a5b805d8ab2da599a34f\"}"}}
{"type":"message","id":"2f7a5642","parentId":"a0809fac","timestamp":"2026-04-14T07:45:27.586Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now let me check the OutlineTree component to see if it has the circular call issue.","thinkingSignature":"1c2928be75b4677b4ef9eaa6006942b63134a5b2af0a146d7a6a2db14d52498c"},{"type":"text","text":"Workbench 本身没问题。检查 OutlineTree 是否有循环调用：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_7xjix8f2u731_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cat /mnt/d/aafuzhi/axs/src/renderer/src/components/OutlineTree.tsx"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":44209,"output":78,"cacheRead":19262,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":63549,"cost":{"input":0.013262699999999999,"output":0.0000936,"cacheRead":0.0011557199999999998,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.014512019999999997}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776152721239,"responseId":"062d2391bbf52c8d5a5c33c1d879a615"}}
{"type":"message","id":"30fdb794","parentId":"2f7a5642","timestamp":"2026-04-14T07:45:27.680Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_7xjix8f2u731_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"import { useState, useEffect } from 'react'\nimport { Tree, Spin, Empty, message } from 'antd'\nimport { FileOutlined, FolderOutlined } from '@ant-design/icons'\nimport type { DataNode } from 'antd/es/tree'\nimport path from 'path'\n\ninterface OutlineTreeProps {\n  projectRoot: string\n  activeChapter: string | null\n  onSelect: (filePath: string) => void\n}\n\ninterface FileEntry {\n  name: string\n  isDirectory: boolean\n  isFile: boolean\n  path: string\n  children?: FileEntry[]\n}\n\nconst OutlineTree = ({ projectRoot, activeChapter, onSelect }: OutlineTreeProps) => {\n  const [treeData, setTreeData] = useState<DataNode[]>([])\n  const [loading, setLoading] = useState(false)\n  const [expandedKeys, setExpandedKeys] = useState<string[]>([])\n\n  // 读取目录结构\n  const loadDirectory = async (dirPath: string): Promise<FileEntry[]> => {\n    try {\n      const entries = await window.electronAPI.readdir(dirPath)\n      if (!Array.isArray(entries)) return []\n      \n      const result: FileEntry[] = []\n      \n      for (const entry of entries) {\n        const fullPath = path.join(dirPath, entry.name)\n        \n        if (entry.isDirectory) {\n          const children = await loadDirectory(fullPath)\n          result.push({\n            name: entry.name,\n            isDirectory: true,\n            isFile: false,\n            path: fullPath,\n            children\n          })\n        } else if (entry.isFile && entry.name.endsWith('.md')) {\n          result.push({\n            name: entry.name.replace('.md', ''),\n            isDirectory: false,\n            isFile: true,\n            path: fullPath\n          })\n        }\n      }\n      \n      return result.sort((a, b) => {\n        // 目录排在前面，然后是文件\n        if (a.isDirectory && !b.isDirectory) return -1\n        if (!a.isDirectory && b.isDirectory) return 1\n        // 按名称排序\n        return a.name.localeCompare(b.name)\n      })\n    } catch (error) {\n      console.error('读取目录失败:', error)\n      return []\n    }\n  }\n\n  // 转换为 Ant Design Tree 需要的格式\n  const convertToTreeData = (entries: FileEntry[], parentKey: string = ''): DataNode[] => {\n    return entries.map((entry, index) => {\n      const key = parentKey ? `${parentKey}-${index}` : `${index}`\n      \n      if (entry.isDirectory && entry.children) {\n        return {\n          title: entry.name,\n          key,\n          icon: <FolderOutlined />,\n          children: convertToTreeData(entry.children, key),\n          isLeaf: false\n        }\n      } else {\n        return {\n          title: entry.name,\n          key: entry.path,\n          icon: <FileOutlined />,\n          isLeaf: true\n        }\n      }\n    })\n  }\n\n  // 加载大纲\n  useEffect(() => {\n    const loadOutline = async () => {\n      if (!projectRoot) return\n      \n      setLoading(true)\n      try {\n        const plotsDir = path.join(projectRoot, 'plots')\n        // 检查 plots 目录是否存在\n        const exists = await window.electronAPI.exists(plotsDir)\n        if (!exists) {\n          // 创建 plots 目录\n          await window.electronAPI.mkdir(plotsDir)\n          setTreeData([])\n          return\n        }\n        \n        const entries = await loadDirectory(plotsDir)\n        const data = convertToTreeData(entries)\n        setTreeData(data)\n        \n        // 默认展开所有节点\n        const getAllKeys = (nodes: DataNode[]): string[] => {\n          let keys: string[] = []\n          nodes.forEach(node => {\n            keys.push(node.key as string)\n            if (node.children) keys = keys.concat(getAllKeys(node.children))\n          })\n          return keys\n        }\n        setExpandedKeys(getAllKeys(data))\n      } catch (error) {\n        message.error('加载大纲失败')\n        console.error(error)\n      } finally {\n        setLoading(false)\n      }\n    }\n\n    loadOutline()\n  }, [projectRoot])\n\n  // 监听文件变化，自动刷新大纲\n  useEffect(() => {\n    if (!projectRoot) return\n    \n    const plotsDir = path.join(projectRoot, 'plots')\n    window.electronAPI.fsWatch(plotsDir)\n    \n    const removeListener = window.electronAPI.onFsChange(() => {\n      // 文件变化时重新加载大纲\n      loadDirectory(path.join(projectRoot, 'plots')).then(entries => {\n        const data = convertToTreeData(entries)\n        setTreeData(data)\n      })\n    })\n    \n    return () => {\n      removeListener()\n      window.electronAPI.fsUnwatch()\n    }\n  }, [projectRoot])\n\n  // 处理选择\n  const handleSelect = (selectedKeys: string[]) => {\n    if (selectedKeys.length === 0) return\n    const key = selectedKeys[0]\n    // 检查是否是文件\n    if (key.startsWith('/') || key.includes('.md')) {\n      onSelect(key)\n    }\n  }\n\n  if (loading) {\n    return (\n      <div style={{ padding: 20, textAlign: 'center' }}>\n        <Spin tip=\"加载中...\" />\n      </div>\n    )\n  }\n\n  if (treeData.length === 0) {\n    return (\n      <div style={{ padding: 20 }}>\n        <Empty\n          description=\"暂无章节\"\n          image={Empty.PRESENTED_IMAGE_SIMPLE}\n        />\n      </div>\n    )\n  }\n\n  return (\n    <div style={{ height: '100%', overflow: 'auto', padding: 10 }}>\n      <Tree\n        treeData={treeData}\n        expandedKeys={expandedKeys}\n        selectedKeys={activeChapter ? [activeChapter] : []}\n        onSelect={handleSelect}\n        onExpand={setExpandedKeys}\n        showIcon\n        defaultExpandAll\n      />\n    </div>\n  )\n}\n\nexport default OutlineTree"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":59,"aggregated":"import { useState, useEffect } from 'react'\nimport { Tree, Spin, Empty, message } from 'antd'\nimport { FileOutlined, FolderOutlined } from '@ant-design/icons'\nimport type { DataNode } from 'antd/es/tree'\nimport path from 'path'\n\ninterface OutlineTreeProps {\n  projectRoot: string\n  activeChapter: string | null\n  onSelect: (filePath: string) => void\n}\n\ninterface FileEntry {\n  name: string\n  isDirectory: boolean\n  isFile: boolean\n  path: string\n  children?: FileEntry[]\n}\n\nconst OutlineTree = ({ projectRoot, activeChapter, onSelect }: OutlineTreeProps) => {\n  const [treeData, setTreeData] = useState<DataNode[]>([])\n  const [loading, setLoading] = useState(false)\n  const [expandedKeys, setExpandedKeys] = useState<string[]>([])\n\n  // 读取目录结构\n  const loadDirectory = async (dirPath: string): Promise<FileEntry[]> => {\n    try {\n      const entries = await window.electronAPI.readdir(dirPath)\n      if (!Array.isArray(entries)) return []\n      \n      const result: FileEntry[] = []\n      \n      for (const entry of entries) {\n        const fullPath = path.join(dirPath, entry.name)\n        \n        if (entry.isDirectory) {\n          const children = await loadDirectory(fullPath)\n          result.push({\n            name: entry.name,\n            isDirectory: true,\n            isFile: false,\n            path: fullPath,\n            children\n          })\n        } else if (entry.isFile && entry.name.endsWith('.md')) {\n          result.push({\n            name: entry.name.replace('.md', ''),\n            isDirectory: false,\n            isFile: true,\n            path: fullPath\n          })\n        }\n      }\n      \n      return result.sort((a, b) => {\n        // 目录排在前面，然后是文件\n        if (a.isDirectory && !b.isDirectory) return -1\n        if (!a.isDirectory && b.isDirectory) return 1\n        // 按名称排序\n        return a.name.localeCompare(b.name)\n      })\n    } catch (error) {\n      console.error('读取目录失败:', error)\n      return []\n    }\n  }\n\n  // 转换为 Ant Design Tree 需要的格式\n  const convertToTreeData = (entries: FileEntry[], parentKey: string = ''): DataNode[] => {\n    return entries.map((entry, index) => {\n      const key = parentKey ? `${parentKey}-${index}` : `${index}`\n      \n      if (entry.isDirectory && entry.children) {\n        return {\n          title: entry.name,\n          key,\n          icon: <FolderOutlined />,\n          children: convertToTreeData(entry.children, key),\n          isLeaf: false\n        }\n      } else {\n        return {\n          title: entry.name,\n          key: entry.path,\n          icon: <FileOutlined />,\n          isLeaf: true\n        }\n      }\n    })\n  }\n\n  // 加载大纲\n  useEffect(() => {\n    const loadOutline = async () => {\n      if (!projectRoot) return\n      \n      setLoading(true)\n      try {\n        const plotsDir = path.join(projectRoot, 'plots')\n        // 检查 plots 目录是否存在\n        const exists = await window.electronAPI.exists(plotsDir)\n        if (!exists) {\n          // 创建 plots 目录\n          await window.electronAPI.mkdir(plotsDir)\n          setTreeData([])\n          return\n        }\n        \n        const entries = await loadDirectory(plotsDir)\n        const data = convertToTreeData(entries)\n        setTreeData(data)\n        \n        // 默认展开所有节点\n        const getAllKeys = (nodes: DataNode[]): string[] => {\n          let keys: string[] = []\n          nodes.forEach(node => {\n            keys.push(node.key as string)\n            if (node.children) keys = keys.concat(getAllKeys(node.children))\n          })\n          return keys\n        }\n        setExpandedKeys(getAllKeys(data))\n      } catch (error) {\n        message.error('加载大纲失败')\n        console.error(error)\n      } finally {\n        setLoading(false)\n      }\n    }\n\n    loadOutline()\n  }, [projectRoot])\n\n  // 监听文件变化，自动刷新大纲\n  useEffect(() => {\n    if (!projectRoot) return\n    \n    const plotsDir = path.join(projectRoot, 'plots')\n    window.electronAPI.fsWatch(plotsDir)\n    \n    const removeListener = window.electronAPI.onFsChange(() => {\n      // 文件变化时重新加载大纲\n      loadDirectory(path.join(projectRoot, 'plots')).then(entries => {\n        const data = convertToTreeData(entries)\n        setTreeData(data)\n      })\n    })\n    \n    return () => {\n      removeListener()\n      window.electronAPI.fsUnwatch()\n    }\n  }, [projectRoot])\n\n  // 处理选择\n  const handleSelect = (selectedKeys: string[]) => {\n    if (selectedKeys.length === 0) return\n    const key = selectedKeys[0]\n    // 检查是否是文件\n    if (key.startsWith('/') || key.includes('.md')) {\n      onSelect(key)\n    }\n  }\n\n  if (loading) {\n    return (\n      <div style={{ padding: 20, textAlign: 'center' }}>\n        <Spin tip=\"加载中...\" />\n      </div>\n    )\n  }\n\n  if (treeData.length === 0) {\n    return (\n      <div style={{ padding: 20 }}>\n        <Empty\n          description=\"暂无章节\"\n          image={Empty.PRESENTED_IMAGE_SIMPLE}\n        />\n      </div>\n    )\n  }\n\n  return (\n    <div style={{ height: '100%', overflow: 'auto', padding: 10 }}>\n      <Tree\n        treeData={treeData}\n        expandedKeys={expandedKeys}\n        selectedKeys={activeChapter ? [activeChapter] : []}\n        onSelect={handleSelect}\n        onExpand={setExpandedKeys}\n        showIcon\n        defaultExpandAll\n      />\n    </div>\n  )\n}\n\nexport default OutlineTree","cwd":"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/main"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1776152727670}}
{"type":"message","id":"0d976f38","parentId":"30fdb794","timestamp":"2026-04-14T07:46:05.833Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I can see a potential issue in OutlineTree:\n\n1. In `loadDirectory`, it recursively calls `loadDirectory` for subdirectories. If there are many nested directories, this could cause issues.\n\n2. The `loadDirectory` is async and awaits each subdirectory one by one. For large directory trees, this could be slow but not circular.\n\n3. The `handleSelect` function has a bug: `if (key.startsWith('/') || key.includes('.md'))` - but the key for directory nodes is not a path, it's a generated key like \"0-1-2\". Only file nodes have the actual file path as their key (from `entry.path`). So clicking on a directory would fail this check.\n\n\nActually, looking more carefully at the Tree structure - when a directory node is clicked, the selected key is the generated key \"0-1-2\", not a path, so it wouldn't pass the path check anyway. But the real issue is that `handleSelect` doesn't actually navigate into directories when they're clicked, it just fails silently since no key would pass the validation.\n\nNow I'm spotting a critical problem: when `activeTab` switches away from 'outline', the OutlineTree unmounts but the file watcher never gets cleaned up. The watcher stops, but there's no `fsUnwatch()` call to properly shut it down, and the `removeListener()` returns a cleanup function that needs to be called.\n\nActually, looking at the logic again - when OutlineTree remounts due to tab switching, the cleanup function from the useEffect will run and properly remove the listener. That's fine.\n\nThe real issue I'm seeing is that `handleSelect` uses path-based checks to determine if something is a file or directory, but directory nodes use synthetic keys like \"0-1-2\" while files use actual paths. So when clicking a directory, it tries to call `onSelect()` with those synthetic keys instead of actual file paths.\n\nBut the bigger concern is the recursive `loadDirectory` calls - each one fires off a separate `readdir` IPC call synchronously in a loop, which could create a cascade of blocking operations if the directory tree is deep or has many subdirectories.\n\nLooking at the bigger picture though, the actual bug list shows the Workbench FileTree issue was already addressed, and what remains are legitimate feature gaps like missing batch generation UI and consistency checking, not architectural problems.\n\nNow I need to verify the facts extraction pipeline to ensure it's properly integrated throughout the workflow.","thinkingSignature":"8a08e828bb971a8e239fea99dca3bbcfb7a00f914bb58346d6c7176271a0ebf4"},{"type":"text","text":"OutlineTree 本身没有循环调用 bug，是正常的递归目录加载。真正的缺口在 **facts 提取链路**——`factExtractor.ts` 有 172 行代码但从没有被触发。\n\n---\n\n## 第 2 步：验证 facts 提取链路\n\n**思考：** `factExtractor.ts` 需要在章节保存时自动触发，从新章节内容中提取事实并写入 facts YAML。但目前没有看到任何地方调用它。\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_55876ax52u9j_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"grep -rn \"factExtractor\\|extractFacts\\|extract.*facts\" /mnt/d/aafuzhi/axs/src/ 2>/dev/null"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":45606,"output":653,"cacheRead":19262,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":65521,"cost":{"input":0.0136818,"output":0.0007836,"cacheRead":0.0011557199999999998,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.015621119999999999}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776152727682,"responseId":"062d23a1abf9d1f71070da8abe11c071"}}
