{"type":"message","id":"1997f56d","parentId":"956bac77","timestamp":"2026-04-14T07:46:11.392Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Interesting! So `factExtractor` IS used in AIToolsPanel and FactsPanel. Let me look at how it's used.\n\nAlso, importantly - I don't see any call to `factExtractor.extract()` when a chapter is saved in Workbench. The facts extraction seems to be triggered only in AIToolsPanel (when AI generates content?) and FactsPanel. Let me check AIToolsPanel.","thinkingSignature":"77275a09627dc7eded2c2666a80c805852508fa53ff422636a94e2d51e995ee3"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_soi6709tzpxp_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"sed -n '135,160p' /mnt/d/aafuzhi/axs/src/renderer/src/components/AIToolsPanel.tsx"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":46435,"output":136,"cacheRead":19262,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":65833,"cost":{"input":0.0139305,"output":0.00016319999999999998,"cacheRead":0.0011557199999999998,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.01524942}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776152766034,"responseId":"062d23bd490be8e694d82e8e6fa731ed"}}
{"type":"message","id":"bf01f673","parentId":"1997f56d","timestamp":"2026-04-14T07:46:11.592Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_soi6709tzpxp_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"setResult('')\n\n    try {\n      // 提取章节号\n      const chapterMatch = chapterPath.match(/第(\\d+)章/)\n      const chapterNumber = chapterMatch ? parseInt(chapterMatch[1]) : 1\n\n      const facts = await factExtractor.extract(chapterContent, chapterNumber)\n      \n      if (facts.length === 0) {\n        setResult('未提取到任何事实')\n        return\n      }\n\n      // 格式化结果\n      let output = `提取到 ${facts.length} 条事实：\\n\\n`\n      facts.forEach((fact, index) => {\n        output += `${index + 1}. [${fact.type}] ${fact.subject}${fact.object ? ' → ' + fact.object : ''}\\n`\n        output += `   ${fact.content} (置信度: ${(fact.confidence * 100).toFixed(0)}%)\\n\\n`\n      })\n\n      output += `是否保存到事实台账？`\n      setResult(output)\n    } catch (error) {\n      message.error('事实提取失败')\n    } finally {"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":125,"aggregated":"setResult('')\n\n    try {\n      // 提取章节号\n      const chapterMatch = chapterPath.match(/第(\\d+)章/)\n      const chapterNumber = chapterMatch ? parseInt(chapterMatch[1]) : 1\n\n      const facts = await factExtractor.extract(chapterContent, chapterNumber)\n      \n      if (facts.length === 0) {\n        setResult('未提取到任何事实')\n        return\n      }\n\n      // 格式化结果\n      let output = `提取到 ${facts.length} 条事实：\\n\\n`\n      facts.forEach((fact, index) => {\n        output += `${index + 1}. [${fact.type}] ${fact.subject}${fact.object ? ' → ' + fact.object : ''}\\n`\n        output += `   ${fact.content} (置信度: ${(fact.confidence * 100).toFixed(0)}%)\\n\\n`\n      })\n\n      output += `是否保存到事实台账？`\n      setResult(output)\n    } catch (error) {\n      message.error('事实提取失败')\n    } finally {","cwd":"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/main"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1776152771562}}
{"type":"message","id":"f9a680d0","parentId":"bf01f673","timestamp":"2026-04-14T07:46:16.056Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I see - `factExtractor.extract()` is called when the user triggers the \"提取事实\" button in AIToolsPanel. But it's not automatically called when saving a chapter. This is a design choice - the user has to manually trigger facts extraction.\n\nLet me now check what the actual issue is with the facts system. Let me look at the full factExtractor.ts to understand its capabilities and limitations.","thinkingSignature":"2ea00e160a78d5472da795b1621b0b1c583cafd503fd3b5b118f4e2799407415"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_optmkco87byk_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"head -100 /mnt/d/aafuzhi/axs/src/renderer/src/services/factExtractor.ts"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":46814,"output":128,"cacheRead":19262,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":66204,"cost":{"input":0.0140442,"output":0.0001536,"cacheRead":0.0011557199999999998,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.015353519999999999}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776152771595,"responseId":"062d23c37243e659a9cd0c6951cc5d61"}}
{"type":"message","id":"ba069062","parentId":"f9a680d0","timestamp":"2026-04-14T07:46:16.211Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_optmkco87byk_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"/**\n * 事实提取服务\n * 自动从章节内容中提取战力、物品、关系、伏笔等事实\n */\n\nimport aiModelService from './aiModels'\nimport db, { Fact } from '../db'\n\n// 提取结果类型\nexport interface ExtractedFact extends Omit<Fact, 'id' | 'createdAt'> {\n  confidence: number // 置信度 0-1\n}\n\nclass FactExtractor {\n  /**\n   * 从章节内容提取事实\n   */\n  async extract(\n    chapterContent: string,\n    chapterNumber: number\n  ): Promise<ExtractedFact[]> {\n    try {\n      const systemPrompt = `\n你是小说事实提取专家。请从以下章节内容中提取关键事实信息，返回严格的JSON格式数组。\n\n提取规则：\n1. 战力信息(type=\"power\")：角色的等级、实力、功法等\n2. 物品信息(type=\"item\")：武器、丹药、宝物等\n3. 关系信息(type=\"relation\")：角色之间的关系（朋友、敌人、师徒、夫妻等）\n4. 伏笔信息(type=\"foreshadow\")：后续可能用到的线索、未解开的谜团\n\n每个事实必须包含：\n- type: 类型（power/item/relation/foreshadow）\n- subject: 主体（如\"林枫\"）\n- object: 客体（可选，如\"青云子\"）\n- content: 事实描述（如\"林枫修炼到炼气三层\"）\n- chapterStart: 章节号（传入的 ${chapterNumber}）\n- chapterEnd: 章节号（传入的 ${chapterNumber}）\n- confidence: 置信度 0-1\n\n返回格式示例：\n[\n  {\n    \"type\": \"power\",\n    \"subject\": \"林枫\",\n    \"object\": \"\",\n    \"content\": \"林枫突破到炼气三层，实力提升三倍\",\n    \"chapterStart\": ${chapterNumber},\n    \"chapterEnd\": ${chapterNumber},\n    \"confidence\": 0.95\n  }\n]\n\n只返回JSON，不要其他内容。\n`\n\n      const result = await aiModelService.call(\n        'extraction',\n        chapterContent,\n        { systemPrompt }\n      )\n\n      if (!result.success || !result.content) {\n        return []\n      }\n\n      // 解析提取结果\n      let extractedFacts: ExtractedFact[]\n      try {\n        extractedFacts = JSON.parse(result.content.trim())\n      } catch (parseError) {\n        console.error('解析提取结果失败:', parseError)\n        return []\n      }\n\n      return extractedFacts\n    } catch (error) {\n      console.error('事实提取失败:', error)\n      return []\n    }\n  }\n\n  /**\n   * 批量保存事实到数据库\n   */\n  async saveFacts(facts: Omit<Fact, 'id' | 'createdAt'>[]): Promise<string[]> {\n    const savedIds: string[] = []\n\n    for (const fact of facts) {\n      const result = await db.addFact(fact)\n      if (result.success && result.id) {\n        savedIds.push(result.id)\n      }\n    }\n\n    return savedIds\n  }\n\n  /**\n   * 自动提取并保存（用户确认后调用）"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":106,"aggregated":"/**\n * 事实提取服务\n * 自动从章节内容中提取战力、物品、关系、伏笔等事实\n */\n\nimport aiModelService from './aiModels'\nimport db, { Fact } from '../db'\n\n// 提取结果类型\nexport interface ExtractedFact extends Omit<Fact, 'id' | 'createdAt'> {\n  confidence: number // 置信度 0-1\n}\n\nclass FactExtractor {\n  /**\n   * 从章节内容提取事实\n   */\n  async extract(\n    chapterContent: string,\n    chapterNumber: number\n  ): Promise<ExtractedFact[]> {\n    try {\n      const systemPrompt = `\n你是小说事实提取专家。请从以下章节内容中提取关键事实信息，返回严格的JSON格式数组。\n\n提取规则：\n1. 战力信息(type=\"power\")：角色的等级、实力、功法等\n2. 物品信息(type=\"item\")：武器、丹药、宝物等\n3. 关系信息(type=\"relation\")：角色之间的关系（朋友、敌人、师徒、夫妻等）\n4. 伏笔信息(type=\"foreshadow\")：后续可能用到的线索、未解开的谜团\n\n每个事实必须包含：\n- type: 类型（power/item/relation/foreshadow）\n- subject: 主体（如\"林枫\"）\n- object: 客体（可选，如\"青云子\"）\n- content: 事实描述（如\"林枫修炼到炼气三层\"）\n- chapterStart: 章节号（传入的 ${chapterNumber}）\n- chapterEnd: 章节号（传入的 ${chapterNumber}）\n- confidence: 置信度 0-1\n\n返回格式示例：\n[\n  {\n    \"type\": \"power\",\n    \"subject\": \"林枫\",\n    \"object\": \"\",\n    \"content\": \"林枫突破到炼气三层，实力提升三倍\",\n    \"chapterStart\": ${chapterNumber},\n    \"chapterEnd\": ${chapterNumber},\n    \"confidence\": 0.95\n  }\n]\n\n只返回JSON，不要其他内容。\n`\n\n      const result = await aiModelService.call(\n        'extraction',\n        chapterContent,\n        { systemPrompt }\n      )\n\n      if (!result.success || !result.content) {\n        return []\n      }\n\n      // 解析提取结果\n      let extractedFacts: ExtractedFact[]\n      try {\n        extractedFacts = JSON.parse(result.content.trim())\n      } catch (parseError) {\n        console.error('解析提取结果失败:', parseError)\n        return []\n      }\n\n      return extractedFacts\n    } catch (error) {\n      console.error('事实提取失败:', error)\n      return []\n    }\n  }\n\n  /**\n   * 批量保存事实到数据库\n   */\n  async saveFacts(facts: Omit<Fact, 'id' | 'createdAt'>[]): Promise<string[]> {\n    const savedIds: string[] = []\n\n    for (const fact of facts) {\n      const result = await db.addFact(fact)\n      if (result.success && result.id) {\n        savedIds.push(result.id)\n      }\n    }\n\n    return savedIds\n  }\n\n  /**\n   * 自动提取并保存（用户确认后调用）","cwd":"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/main"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1776152776199}}
{"type":"message","id":"3db5402f","parentId":"ba069062","timestamp":"2026-04-14T07:46:28.421Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I see - `factExtractor` uses `aiModelService.call('extraction', ...)` which will call the AI. But the AI service was just fixed with `aiService.ts` - however `aiModelService` in the renderer uses `window.electronAPI.ai.call()` which goes through IPC to the main process. The main process now has `ai:call` handler from `aiService.ts`.\n\nBUT wait - `aiModelService.call()` in the renderer is a TypeScript module that calls `window.electronAPI.ai.call()`. This is correct. And now `aiService.ts` handles `ai:call` in the main process. So this should work.\n \nActually, looking more carefully at the renderer-side AI service - it's calling the preload API which routes through IPC to the main process handler. The main process then makes actual HTTP calls to the AI provider. The factExtractor depends on `aiModels.ts` in the renderer which is `window.electronAPI.ai.call()`. This chain should work since we've now implemented `aiService.ts` in the main process.\n\nLet me verify what the actual blocker is - the main issue is that the factExtractor relies on the AI service, and there was a missing IPC handler that's now fixed. There's also the question of whether the facts extraction actually gets persisted to YAML files or just stored in the SQLite database that the main process references.","thinkingSignature":"192b93566797d674bd7b6b193d10abb4bd44c0e8c146b7b4255f7a82a2596261"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_w2vr24vhgtmg_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"find /mnt/d/aafuzhi/axs/src -name \"*.ts\" | xargs grep -l \"yaml\\|YAML\" 2>/dev/null"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":47616,"output":341,"cacheRead":19262,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":67219,"cost":{"input":0.014284799999999999,"output":0.00040919999999999997,"cacheRead":0.0011557199999999998,