{"type":"message","id":"c29a025a","parentId":"68e06b44","timestamp":"2026-04-14T07:46:41.102Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Interesting - so the renderer-side code doesn't use YAML at all for facts storage. The facts system in the Electron app uses SQLite (via `db` from `../db`), while the command-line tools use YAML files (`facts/characters_facts.yaml`, etc.).\n\nThis means there are TWO separate facts systems:\n1. **YAML facts system** (command-line tools) - stored in `my-novel/facts/*.yaml`\n2. **SQLite facts system** (Electron GUI) - stored in `better-sqlite3` database\n\nThe `factExtractor.ts` in the renderer saves to SQLite, NOT to the YAML files that `generate-chapter.js` reads from.","thinkingSignature":"3cccc794c33ae2e346e76573fdccf4d01edde06c61a8b3e958d83afbc2dd45c7"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_xx0ictybannx_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"ls /mnt/d/aafuzhi/axs/src/renderer/src/db* 2>/dev/null\necho \"---\"\ncat /mnt/d/aafuzhi/axs/src/renderer/src/db/index.ts 2>/dev/null | head -50"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":48086,"output":218,"cacheRead":19262,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":67566,"cost":{"input":0.014425799999999999,"output":0.00026159999999999996,"cacheRead":0.0011557199999999998,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.01584312}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776152791958,"responseId":"062d23d76e1b1eee71a64c9393a32957"}}
{"type":"message","id":"4fb016ab","parentId":"c29a025a","timestamp":"2026-04-14T07:46:41.230Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_xx0ictybannx_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"index.ts\n---\n/**\n * SQLite 数据库集成\n * 用于存储事实台账和角色信息\n */\n\n// 数据库类型定义\nexport interface Fact {\n  id: string\n  type: 'power' | 'item' | 'relation' | 'foreshadow'\n  subject: string\n  object: string\n  content: string\n  chapterStart: number\n  chapterEnd: number\n  createdAt: number\n}\n\nexport interface Role {\n  id: string\n  name: string\n  tags: string[]\n  goldenFinger: string\n  createdAt: number\n}\n\n// 初始化数据库\nclass Database {\n  private db: any | null = null\n  private initialized: boolean = false\n\n  constructor() {\n    // 在 Electron 环境中使用 better-sqlite3\n    if (window.electronAPI) {\n      this.initializeElectronDB()\n    }\n  }\n\n  private async initializeElectronDB() {\n    try {\n      // 通过 IPC 获取项目根路径\n      const projectRoot = await window.electronAPI.getProjectRoot()\n      if (!projectRoot) return\n\n      // 数据库文件路径\n      const dbPath = `${projectRoot}/facts.db`\n\n      // 检查是否存在数据库\n      const exists = await window.electronAPI.exists(dbPath)\n      if (!exists) {\n        await this.createTables()"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":75,"aggregated":"index.ts\n---\n/**\n * SQLite 数据库集成\n * 用于存储事实台账和角色信息\n */\n\n// 数据库类型定义\nexport interface Fact {\n  id: string\n  type: 'power' | 'item' | 'relation' | 'foreshadow'\n  subject: string\n  object: string\n  content: string\n  chapterStart: number\n  chapterEnd: number\n  createdAt: number\n}\n\nexport interface Role {\n  id: string\n  name: string\n  tags: string[]\n  goldenFinger: string\n  createdAt: number\n}\n\n// 初始化数据库\nclass Database {\n  private db: any | null = null\n  private initialized: boolean = false\n\n  constructor() {\n    // 在 Electron 环境中使用 better-sqlite3\n    if (window.electronAPI) {\n      this.initializeElectronDB()\n    }\n  }\n\n  private async initializeElectronDB() {\n    try {\n      // 通过 IPC 获取项目根路径\n      const projectRoot = await window.electronAPI.getProjectRoot()\n      if (!projectRoot) return\n\n      // 数据库文件路径\n      const dbPath = `${projectRoot}/facts.db`\n\n      // 检查是否存在数据库\n      const exists = await window.electronAPI.exists(dbPath)\n      if (!exists) {\n        await this.createTables()","cwd":"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/main"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1776152801213}}
{"type":"message","id":"a407e450","parentId":"4fb016ab","timestamp":"2026-04-14T07:46:48.112Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Interesting! The renderer-side SQLite database uses the project root path to store `facts.db`. But wait - `window.electronAPI.getProjectRoot()` returns the project root, and then `facts.db` would be at `{projectRoot}/facts.db`. But this path is not chroot-restricted! The renderer can write to `{projectRoot}/facts.db`.\n\nAlso, I notice `initializeElectronDB` is an async method that's called in the constructor. But the constructor can't be async! So `initializeElectronDB()` is called but the `await` inside it won't work properly - the method returns a Promise but it's not awaited.","thinkingSignature":"6cd094b6bc35da69bce4b0c8888acebce62f59da3c50ce12e64525c6cd36081b"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_dcdzc0n7tlxf_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"sed -n '40,90p' /mnt/d/aafuzhi/axs/src/renderer/src/db/index.ts"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":48594,"output":181,"cacheRead":19262,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":68037,"cost":{"input":0.0145782,"output":0.0002172,"cacheRead":0.0011557199999999998,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.01595112}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776152801232,"responseId":"062d23e04cb64edfb6e7d48ae6cbb024"}}
{"type":"message","id":"77bd2721","parentId":"a407e450","timestamp":"2026-04-14T07:46:48.243Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_dcdzc0n7tlxf_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"// 通过 IPC 获取项目根路径\n      const projectRoot = await window.electronAPI.getProjectRoot()\n      if (!projectRoot) return\n\n      // 数据库文件路径\n      const dbPath = `${projectRoot}/facts.db`\n\n      // 检查是否存在数据库\n      const exists = await window.electronAPI.exists(dbPath)\n      if (!exists) {\n        await this.createTables()\n      }\n\n      this.initialized = true\n    } catch (error) {\n      console.error('数据库初始化失败:', error)\n    }\n  }\n\n  // 创建数据库表\n  private async createTables() {\n    // 通过 IPC 执行 SQL 创建表\n    await window.electronAPI.writeFile(\n      `${projectRoot}/facts.db`,\n      `CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS facts (\n        id TEXT PRIMARY KEY,\n        type TEXT NOT NULL,\n        subject TEXT NOT NULL,\n        object TEXT,\n        content TEXT NOT NULL,\n        chapter_start INTEGER NOT NULL,\n        chapter_end INTEGER NOT NULL,\n        created_at INTEGER NOT NULL\n      );\n\n      CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS roles (\n        id TEXT PRIMARY KEY,\n        name TEXT NOT NULL,\n        tags TEXT,\n        golden_finger TEXT,\n        created_at INTEGER NOT NULL\n      );`\n    )\n  }\n\n  // ========== 事实表操作 ==========\n\n  // 添加事实\n  async addFact(fact: Omit<Fact, 'id' | 'createdAt'>): Promise<{ success: boolean; id?: string; error?: string }> {\n    try {\n      const id = crypto.randomUUID()"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":71,"aggregated":"// 通过 IPC 获取项目根路径\n      const projectRoot = await window.electronAPI.getProjectRoot()\n      if (!projectRoot) return\n\n      // 数据库文件路径\n      const dbPath = `${projectRoot}/facts.db`\n\n      // 检查是否存在数据库\n      const exists = await window.electronAPI.exists(dbPath)\n      if (!exists) {\n        await this.createTables()\n      }\n\n      this.initialized = true\n    } catch (error) {\n      console.error('数据库初始化失败:', error)\n    }\n  }\n\n  // 创建数据库表\n  private async createTables() {\n    // 通过 IPC 执行 SQL 创建表\n    await window.electronAPI.writeFile(\n      `${projectRoot}/facts.db`,\n      `CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS facts (\n        id TEXT PRIMARY KEY,\n        type TEXT NOT NULL,\n        subject TEXT NOT NULL,\n        object TEXT,\n        content TEXT NOT NULL,\n        chapter_start INTEGER NOT NULL,\n        chapter_end INTEGER NOT NULL,\n        created_at INTEGER NOT NULL\n      );\n\n      CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS roles (\n        id TEXT PRIMARY KEY,\n        name TEXT NOT NULL,\n        tags TEXT,\n        golden_finger TEXT,\n        created_at INTEGER NOT NULL\n      );`\n    )\n  }\n\n  // ========== 事实表操作 ==========\n\n  // 添加事实\n  async addFact(fact: Omit<Fact, 'id' | 'createdAt'>): Promise<{ success: boolean; id?: string; error?: string }> {\n    try {\n      const id = crypto.randomUUID()","cwd":"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/main"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1776152808226}}
{"type":"message","id":"e5389873","parentId":"77bd2721","timestamp":"2026-04-14T07:46:54.303Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Found a serious bug! The `createTables` method is trying to use `window.electronAPI.writeFile` to write SQL statements directly to a `.db` file! This won't create a proper SQLite database - it just writes SQL text to a file named `facts.db`. And it references `projectRoot` without `this.projectRoot` - it's a closure variable from `initializeElectronDB`.\n\nLet me check if there's a better-sqlite3 usage or if this is all wrong.","thinkingSignature":"b32311ec1dc8abe957a09152ff799ad95d91c069f643718fbdf96ccea1eb4022"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_qljdmqj05awv_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cat /mnt/d/aafuzhi/axs/src/renderer/src/db/index.ts"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":49106,"output":142,"cacheRead":19262,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":68510,"cost":{"input":0.0147318,"output":0.0001704,"cacheRead":0.0011557199999999998,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.01605792}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776152808245,"responseId":"062d23e8d2a4d34f79850c57104f1c76"}}
{"type":"message","id":"357c98af","parentId":"e5389873","timestamp":"2026-04-14T07:46:54.428Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_qljdmqj05awv_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"/**\n * SQLite 数据库集成\n * 用于存储事实台账和角色信息\n */\n\n// 数据库类型定义\nexport interface Fact {\n  id: string\n  type: 'power' | 'item' | 'relation' | 'foreshadow'\n  subject: string\n  object: string\n  content: string\n  chapterStart: number\n  chapterEnd: number\n  createdAt: number\n}\n\nexport interface Role {\n  id: string\n  name: string\n  tags: string[]\n  goldenFinger: string\n  createdAt: number\n}\n\n// 初始化数据库\nclass Database {\n  private db: any | null = null\n  private initialized: boolean = false\n\n  constructor() {\n    // 在 Electron 环境中使用 better-sqlite3\n    if (window.electronAPI) {\n      this.initializeElectronDB()\n    }\n  }\n\n  private async initializeElectronDB() {\n    try {\n      // 通过 IPC 获取项目根路径\n      const projectRoot = await window.electronAPI.getProjectRoot()\n      if (!projectRoot) return\n\n      // 数据库文件路径\n      const dbPath = `${projectRoot}/facts.db`\n\n      // 检查是否存在数据库\n      const exists = await window.electronAPI.exists(dbPath)\n      if (!exists) {\n        await this.createTables()\n      }\n\n      this.initialized = true\n    } catch (error) {\n      console.error('数据库初始化失败:', error)\n    }\n  }\n\n  // 创建数据库表\n  private async createTables() {\n    // 通过 IPC 执行 SQL 创建表\n    await window.electronAPI.writeFile(\n      `${projectRoot}/facts.db`,\n      `CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS facts (\n        id TEXT PRIMARY KEY,\n        type TEXT NOT NULL,\n        subject TEXT NOT NULL,\n        object TEXT,\n        content TEXT NOT NULL,\n        chapter_start INTEGER NOT NULL,\n        chapter_end INTEGER NOT NULL,\n        created_at INTEGER NOT NULL\n      );\n\n      CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS roles (\n        id TEXT PRIMARY KEY,\n        name TEXT NOT NULL,\n        tags TEXT,\n        golden_finger TEXT,\n        created_at INTEGER NOT NULL\n      );`\n    )\n  }\n\n  // ========== 事实表操作 ==========\n\n  // 添加事实\n  async addFact(fact: Omit<Fact, 'id' | 'createdAt'>): Promise<{ success: boolean; id?: string; error?: string }> {\n    try {\n      const id = crypto.randomUUID()\n      const createdAt = Date.now()\n      \n      // 执行插入操作\n      const insertSQL = `\n        INSERT INTO facts (id, type, subject, object, content, chapter_start, chapter_end, created_at)\n        VALUES ('${id}', '${fact.type}', '${fact.subject}', '${fact.object || ''}', '${fact.content.replace(/'/g, \"''\")}', ${fact.chapterStart}, ${fact.chapterEnd}, ${createdAt})\n      `\n      \n      // 通过 IPC 执行 SQL\n      await window.electronAPI.ai.call(insertSQL, { type: 'sql' })\n      \n      return { success: true, id }\n    } catch (error: any) {\n      return { success: false, error: error.message }\n    }\n  }\n\n  // 查询事实\n  async getFacts(filters?: { type?: string; subject?: string; chapter?: number }): Promise<Fact[]> {\n    try {\n      let sql = 'SELECT * FROM facts'\n      const conditions: string[] = []\n      \n      if (filters?.type) conditions.push(`type = '${filters.type}'`)\n      if (filters?.subject) conditions.push(`subject = '${filters.subject}' OR object = '${filters.subject}'`)\n      if (filters?.chapter) conditions.push(`chapter_start <= ${filters.chapter} AND (chapter_end >= ${filters.chapter} OR chapter_end IS NULL)`)\n      \n      if (conditions.length > 0) sql += ` WHERE ${conditions.join(' AND ')}`\n      sql += ' ORDER BY created_at DESC'\n      \n      const result = await window.electronAPI.ai.call(sql, { type: 'sql' })\n      if (result.success) {\n        return JSON.parse(result.content).map((row: any) => ({\n          id: row.id,\n          type: row.type,\n          subject: row.subject,\n          object: row.object,\n          content: row.content,\n          chapterStart: row.chapter_start,\n          chapterEnd: row.chapter_end,\n          createdAt: row.created_at\n        }))\n      }\n      return []\n    } catch (error) {\n      console.error('查询事实失败:', error)\n      return []\n    }\n  }\n\n  // 删除事实\n  async deleteFact(id: string): Promise<boolean> {\n    try {\n      const sql = `DELETE FROM facts WHERE id = '${id}'`\n      const result = await window.electronAPI.ai.call(sql, { type: 'sql' })\n      return result.success\n    } catch (error) {\n      console.error('删除事实失败:', error)\n      return false\n    }\n  }\n\n  // ========== 角色表操作 ==========\n\n  // 添加角色\n  async addRole(role: Omit<Role, 'id' | 'createdAt'>): Promise<{ success: boolean; id?: string; error?: string }> {\n    try {\n      const id = crypto.randomUUID()\n      const createdAt = Date.now()\n      const tags = JSON.stringify(role.tags)\n      \n      const sql = `\n        INSERT INTO roles (id, name, tags, golden_finger, created_at)\n        VALUES ('${id}', '${role.name}', '${tags}', '${role.goldenFinger.replace(/'/g, \"''\")}', ${createdAt})\n      `\n      \n      const result = await window.electronAPI.ai.call(sql, { type: 'sql' })\n      if (result.success) {\n        return { success: true, id }\n      }\n      return { success: false, error: result.error }\n    } catch (error: any) {\n      return { success: false, error: error.message }\n    }\n  }\n\n  // 查询角色\n  async getRoles(): Promise<Role[]> {\n    try {\n      const sql = 'SELECT * FROM roles ORDER BY name'\n      const result = await window.electronAPI.ai.call(sql, { type: 'sql' })\n      if (result.success) {\n        return JSON.parse(result.content).map((row: any) => ({\n          id: row.id,\n          name: row.name,\n          tags: JSON.parse(row.tags),\n          goldenFinger: row.golden_finger,\n          createdAt: row.created_at\n        }))\n      }\n      return []\n    } catch (error) {\n      console.error('查询角色失败:', error)\n      return []\n    }\n  }\n}\n\n// 单例导出\nconst db = new Database()\nexport default db"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":82,"aggregated":"/**\n * SQLite 数据库集成\n * 用于存储事实台账和角色信息\n */\n\n// 数据库类型定义\nexport interface Fact {\n  id: string\n  type: 'power' | 'item' | 'relation' | 'foreshadow'\n  subject: string\n  object: string\n  content: string\n  chapterStart: number\n  chapterEnd: number\n  createdAt: number\n}\n\nexport interface Role {\n  id: string\n  name: string\n  tags: string[]\n  goldenFinger: string\n  createdAt: number\n}\n\n// 初始化数据库\nclass Database {\n  private db: any | null = null\n  private initialized: boolean = false\n\n  constructor() {\n    // 在 Electron 环境中使用 better-sqlite3\n    if (window.electronAPI) {\n      this.initializeElectronDB()\n    }\n  }\n\n  private async initializeElectronDB() {\n    try {\n      // 通过 IPC 获取项目根路径\n      const projectRoot = await window.electronAPI.getProjectRoot()\n      if (!projectRoot) return\n\n      // 数据库文件路径\n      const dbPath = `${projectRoot}/facts.db`\n\n      // 检查是否存在数据库\n      const exists = await window.electronAPI.exists(dbPath)\n      if (!exists) {\n        await this.createTables()\n      }\n\n      this.initialized = true\n    } catch (error) {\n      console.error('数据库初始化失败:', error)\n    }\n  }\n\n  // 创建数据库表\n  private async createTables() {\n    // 通过 IPC 执行 SQL 创建表\n    await window.electronAPI.writeFile(\n      `${projectRoot}/facts.db`,\n      `CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS facts (\n        id TEXT PRIMARY KEY,\n        type TEXT NOT NULL,\n        subject TEXT NOT NULL,\n        object TEXT,\n        content TEXT NOT NULL,\n        chapter_start INTEGER NOT NULL,\n        chapter_end INTEGER NOT NULL,\n        created_at INTEGER NOT NULL\n      );\n\n      CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS roles (\n        id TEXT PRIMARY KEY,\n        name TEXT NOT NULL,\n        tags TEXT,\n        golden_finger TEXT,\n        created_at INTEGER NOT NULL\n      );`\n    )\n  }\n\n  // ========== 事实表操作 ==========\n\n  // 添加事实\n  async addFact(fact: Omit<Fact, 'id' | 'createdAt'>): Promise<{ success: boolean; id?: string; error?: string }> {\n    try {\n      const id = crypto.randomUUID()\n      const createdAt = Date.now()\n      \n      // 执行插入操作\n      const insertSQL = `\n        INSERT INTO facts (id, type, subject, object, content, chapter_start, chapter_end, created_at)\n        VALUES ('${id}', '${fact.type}', '${fact.subject}', '${fact.object || ''}', '${fact.content.replace(/'/g, \"''\")}', ${fact.chapterStart}, ${fact.chapterEnd}, ${createdAt})\n      `\n      \n      // 通过 IPC 执行 SQL\n      await window.electronAPI.ai.call(insertSQL, { type: 'sql' })\n      \n      return { success: true, id }\n    } catch (error: any) {\n      return { success: false, error: error.message }\n    }\n  }\n\n  // 查询事实\n  async getFacts(filters?: { type?: string; subject?: string; chapter?: number }): Promise<Fact[]> {\n    try {\n      let sql = 'SELECT * FROM facts'\n      const conditions: string[] = []\n      \n      if (filters?.type) conditions.push(`type = '${filters.type}'`)\n      if (filters?.subject) conditions.push(`subject = '${filters.subject}' OR object = '${filters.subject}'`)\n      if (filters?.chapter) conditions.push(`chapter_start <= ${filters.chapter} AND (chapter_end >= ${filters.chapter} OR chapter_end IS NULL)`)\n      \n      if (conditions.length > 0) sql += ` WHERE ${conditions.join(' AND ')}`\n      sql += ' ORDER BY created_at DESC'\n      \n      const result = await window.electronAPI.ai.call(sql, { type: 'sql' })\n      if (result.success) {\n        return JSON.parse(result.content).map((row: any) => ({\n          id: row.id,\n          type: row.type,\n          subject: row.subject,\n          object: row.object,\n          content: row.content,\n          chapterStart: row.chapter_start,\n          chapterEnd: row.chapter_end,\n          createdAt: row.created_at\n        }))\n      }\n      return []\n    } catch (error) {\n      console.error('查询事实失败:', error)\n      return []\n    }\n  }\n\n  // 删除事实\n  async deleteFact(id: string): Promise<boolean> {\n    try {\n      const sql = `DELETE FROM facts WHERE id = '${id}'`\n      const result = await window.electronAPI.ai.call(sql, { type: 'sql' })\n      return result.success\n    } catch (error) {\n      console.error('删除事实失败:', error)\n      return false\n    }\n  }\n\n  // ========== 角色表操作 ==========\n\n  // 添加角色\n  async addRole(role: Omit<Role, 'id' | 'createdAt'>): Promise<{ success: boolean; id?: string; error?: string }> {\n    try {\n      const id = crypto.randomUUID()\n      const createdAt = Date.now()\n      const tags = JSON.stringify(role.tags)\n      \n      const sql = `\n        INSERT INTO roles (id, name, tags, golden_finger, created_at)\n        VALUES ('${id}', '${role.name}', '${tags}', '${role.goldenFinger.replace(/'/g, \"''\")}', ${createdAt})\n      `\n      \n      const result = await window.electronAPI.ai.call(sql, { type: 'sql' })\n      if (result.success) {\n        return { success: true, id }\n      }\n      return { success: false, error: result.error }\n    } catch (error: any) {\n      return { success: false, error: error.message }\n    }\n  }\n\n  // 查询角色\n  async getRoles(): Promise<Role[]> {\n    try {\n      const sql = 'SELECT * FROM roles ORDER BY name'\n      const result = await window.electronAPI.ai.call(sql, { type: 'sql' })\n      if (result.success) {\n        return JSON.parse(result.content).map((row: any) => ({\n          id: row.id,\n          name: row.name,\n          tags: JSON.parse(row.tags),\n          goldenFinger: row.golden_finger,\n          createdAt: row.created_at\n        }))\n      }\n      return []\n    } catch (error) {\n      console.error('查询角色失败:', error)\n      return []\n    }\n  }\n}\n\n// 单例导出\nconst db = new Database()\nexport default db","cwd":"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/main"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1776152814416}}
{"type":"message","id":"b74232e6","parentId":"357c98af","timestamp":"2026-04-14T07:47:27.656Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I found multiple critical bugs in `db/index.ts`:\n\n1. **`createTables` uses `window.electronAPI.writeFile` to write SQL to a `.db` file** - This doesn't create a SQLite database at all! SQLite databases are binary files, not SQL text files. `writeFile` just writes the SQL text as raw bytes to a file named `facts.db`, which is completely wrong.\n\n2. **`projectRoot` is a closure variable in `initializeElectronDB`, not stored** - `createTables()` references `projectRoot` which is a local variable in `initializeElectronDB`, not `this.projectRoot`. \n\n3. **SQL execution bypasses the database entirely** - Methods like `addFact`, `getFacts`, `deleteFact`, `addRole`, and `getRoles` all send SQL strings through `window.electronAPI.ai.call()` with `{ type: 'sql' }`, treating the AI as a database engine rather than actually executing the queries against SQLite.\n\n4. **SQL injection vulnerabilities throughout** - Every query builder directly interpolates user input into SQL strings without any sanitization.\n\n5. **The database is never actually initialized** - Since `initializeElectronDB` is called without awaiting in the constructor and `initialized` stays false, all operations fail silently.\n\nThe core issue is that this is fundamentally broken: the code pretends to use SQLite but actually sends SQL through an AI API call that isn't designed to execute database operations. There's no actual SQLite database implementation—just a fake one built on AI API calls. I need to be direct about what's broken here rather than continuing to catalog the problems.","thinkingSignature":"d77b903e24dee370cbed802f2442cf0cc05cd259a2672b61d9e65b66a4519e10"},{"type":"text","text":"🔴 **发现 P0 数据库断层——`db/index.ts` 是完全错误的设计**\n\n---\n\n## 第 3 步：确认 facts 系统架构的根本问题\n\n**思考：** 核心问题——命令行工具和 Electron GUI 用的是**两套完全不同的 facts 存储**，且 Electron GUI 那套根本没有连接真正的数据库。\n\n| 层 | 命令行工具 | Electron GUI |\n|---|-----------|-------------|\n| 存储介质 | `my-novel/facts/*.yaml` | `facts.db` (文本，非二进制 SQLite) |\n| 数据库 | 无（YAML 文件） | ❌ 用 `writeFile` 写 SQL 文本 |\n| SQL 执行 | 无 SQL | ❌ 走 `window.electronAPI.ai.call(sql)` |\n| AI 提取 | `generate-chapter.js` 内部调用 | `factExtractor.ts` 调用 `aiModels` |\n| facts 注入 | `generate-chapter.js` prompt 注入 | ❌ 无注入链路 |\n\n**最严重的 bug：**\n- `db.addFact()` 调用 `window.electronAPI.ai.call(sql, { type: 'sql' })` — 把 SQL 发给 AI API 执行，而不是数据库\n- `createTables()` 用 `writeFile` 写 SQL 文本到 `.db` 文件 — 不是真正的 SQLite 数据库\n\n**结论：** facts 系统在 Electron GUI 里完全不可用。需要重构。\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_08dn2e06b8a6_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"grep -n \"better-sqlite3\\|sqlite3\\|sql.js\\|dexie\" /mnt/d/aafuzhi/axs/package.json 2>/dev/null\necho \"---\"\ngrep -n \"better-sqlite3\\|sqlite3\\|sql.js\" /mnt/d/aafuzhi/axs/src/main/index.ts 2>/dev/null"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":50674,"output":714,"cacheRead":19262,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":70650,"cost":{"input":0.015202199999999999,"output":0.0008568,"cacheRead":0.0011557199999999998,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.01721472}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776152814430,"responseId":"062d23f2f73d04af69b2049dc91d90cd"}}
{"type":"message","id":"510cb3b7","parentId":"b74232e6","timestamp":"2026-04-14T07:47:27.798Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_08dn2e06b8a6_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\n\n(Command exited with code 1)"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":1,"durationMs":80,"aggregated":"---\n\n(Command exited with code 1)","cwd":"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/main"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1776152847784}}
{"type":"message","id":"10a893c9","parentId":"510cb3b7","timestamp":"2026-04-14T07:48:22.580Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"No SQLite dependency at all. The project has no database dependency. The `db/index.ts` is completely fake - it doesn't use any actual database.\n\nThe architecture decision is clear: the facts should be stored as YAML files (to match the command-line tools) or JSON. The simplest fix: write facts to YAML files via the same `fs` IPC that already works.\n\nLet me now propose the fix and implement it. The goal is:1. facts 提取结果 → 追加写入 `facts/characters_facts.yaml` 等 YAML 文件2. `generate-chapter.js` 读取 YAML → 注入 prompt（已有链路）\n\n\n3. 重构 `db/index.ts` → 移除假 SQL，改为读写 YAML 文件\n\nI'm leaning toward using the IPC filesystem handlers we already have rather than spinning up a new database process through IPC, since the YAML approach keeps things simpler and aligns with how the command-line tools already work. My plan is to replace `db/index.ts` with a YAML-based implementation and add an IPC handler to merge extracted facts back into the YAML files.","thinkingSignature":"43d9c6f02a182c6a478e9a80c21da3cc6525a0657d19d2722a5bbf816c9f07e5"},{"type":"text","text":"---\n\n## 架构确认与修复方案\n\n**问题根源：** `db/index.ts` 声称\"SQl 数据库\"但零依赖、零真正数据库。facts 数据流断裂。\n\n**正确架构应该是：** Electron GUI 提取 facts → 追加写入 `my-novel/facts/*.yaml` → `generate-chapter.js` 读取同文件 → 注入 AI prompt。\n\n**第 3 步（实施）：重构 facts 存储为 YAML 文件**\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_cgmoff6i34v8_1","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"/mnt/d/aafuzhi/axs/src/renderer/src/db/index.ts","content":"/**\n * Facts 持久化层\n * 直接读写 facts/*.yaml 文件，与命令行工具共用同一数据源\n */\n\nimport type { Fact } from '../db/index'\n\n// Re-export types for consumers\nexport type { Fact }\n\ninterface CharactersFacts {\n  [charName: string]: {\n    mbti?: string\n    core_fear?: string\n    abilities?: string[]\n    relationships?: Record<string, string>\n    important_events?: Array<{ chapter: number; event: string; version: string }>\n    personality_traits?: string[]\n    goal?: string\n    [key: string]: unknown\n  }\n}\n\ninterface PlotFacts {\n  伏笔清单?: Array<{\n    id: string\n    description: string\n    setup_chapter: number\n    status: string\n    related_characters?: string[]\n  }>\n  [key: string]: unknown\n}\n\ninterface SettingsFacts {\n  [settingName: string]: {\n    description?: string\n    rules?: string[]\n    [key: string]: unknown\n  }\n}\n\nclass FactsStore {\n  private projectRoot: string | null = null\n\n  async setProjectRoot(root: string): Promise<void> {\n    this.projectRoot = root\n  }\n\n  private factsDir(): string {\n    if (!this.projectRoot) throw new Error('未设置项目根路径')\n    return `${this.projectRoot}/facts`\n  }\n\n  // ─── 读取 facts ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────\n\n  async loadCharactersFacts(): Promise<CharactersFacts> {\n    try {\n      const result = await window.electronAPI.readFile(`${this.factsDir()}/characters_facts.yaml`)\n      if (result.success && result.content) {\n        return this.parseYamlFacts(result.content) as CharactersFacts\n      }\n    } catch {}\n    return {}\n  }\n\n  async loadPlotFacts(): Promise<PlotFacts> {\n    try {\n      const result = await window.electronAPI.readFile(`${this.factsDir()}/plot_facts.yaml`)\n      if (result.success && result.content) {\n        return this.parseYamlFacts(result.content) as PlotFacts\n      }\n    } catch {}\n    return {}\n  }\n\n  async loadSettingsFacts(): Promise<SettingsFacts> {\n    try {\n      const result = await window.electronAPI.readFile(`${this.factsDir()}/settings_facts.yaml`)\n      if (result.success && result.content) {\n        return this.parseYamlFacts(result.content) as SettingsFacts\n      }\n    } catch {}\n    return {}\n  }\n\n  // ─── 写入 facts ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────\n\n  /** 从 AI 提取结果追加到 facts YAML */\n  async appendFacts(facts: Array<{\n    type: string\n    subject: string\n    object?: string\n    content: string\n    chapterStart: number\n    chapterEnd: number\n    confidence: number\n  }>): Promise<{ success: boolean; error?: string }> {\n    try {\n      if (!this.projectRoot) {\n        // 尝试从文件系统获取\n        const root = await window.electronAPI.getProjectRoot()\n        if (root) this.projectRoot = root\n        else return { success: false, error: '未设置项目根路径' }\n      }\n\n      const charFacts = await this.loadCharactersFacts()\n      const plotFacts = await this.loadPlotFacts()\n      const settingFacts = await this.loadSettingsFacts()\n\n      for (const fact of facts) {\n        if (fact.type === 'power' || fact.type === 'item' || fact.type === 'relation') {\n          // 追加到角色 facts\n          if (!charFacts[fact.subject]) {\n            charFacts[fact.subject] = {}\n          }\n          const char = charFacts[fact.subject]\n\n          if (fact.type === 'power' && fact.content) {\n            // 战力事实 → abilities\n            if (!char.abilities) char.abilities = []\n            if (!char.abilities.includes(fact.content)) {\n              char.abilities.push(fact.content)\n            }\n          }\n          if (fact.type === 'relation' && fact.object) {\n            // 关系事实 → relationships\n            if (!char.relationships) char.relationships = {}\n            char.relationships[fact.object] = fact.content\n          }\n          if (fact.type === 'item' && fact.content) {\n            // 物品事实 → 追加到备注\n            const note = fact.content\n            if (!char.personality_traits) char.personality_traits = []\n            if (!char.personality_traits.includes(note)) {\n              char.personality_traits.push(note)\n            }\n          }\n        }\n\n        if (fact.type === 'foreshadow') {\n          // 伏笔事实 → plot_facts.yaml\n          if (!plotFacts.伏笔清单) plotFacts.伏笔清单 = []\n          // 检查是否已存在相同伏笔\n          const exists = plotFacts.伏笔清单.some(\n            p => p.description === fact.content && p.setup_chapter === fact.chapterStart\n          )\n          if (!exists) {\n            plotFacts.伏笔清单.push({\n              id: `F${Date.now()}-${Math.random().toString(36).slice(2, 6)}`,\n              description: fact.content,\n              setup_chapter: fact.chapterStart,\n              status: '待回收',\n              related_characters: fact.subject ? [fact.subject] : [],\n            })\n          }\n        }\n      }\n\n      // 写回 YAML 文件\n      await this.saveYaml(`${this.factsDir()}/characters_facts.yaml`, charFacts)\n      await this.saveYaml(`${this.factsDir()}/plot_facts.yaml`, plotFacts)\n\n      return { success: true }\n    } catch (e: any) {\n      return { success: false, error: e.message }\n    }\n  }\n\n  // ─── YAML 序列化（不依赖外部库） ─────────────────────────────────────────────\n\n  private serializeYaml(obj: unknown, indent = 0): string {\n    const pad = '  '.repeat(indent)\n    const lines: string[] = []\n\n    if (obj === null || obj === undefined) return ''\n\n    if (typeof obj !== 'object') {\n      // 基础类型直接输出\n      return String(obj)\n    }\n\n    if (Array.isArray(obj)) {\n      for (const item of obj) {\n        if (typeof item === 'object' && item !== null) {\n          lines.push(`${pad}-`)\n          lines.push(this.serializeYaml(item, indent + 1))\n        } else {\n          lines.push(`${pad}- ${item}`)\n        }\n      }\n    } else {\n      for (const [key, value] of Object.entries(obj)) {\n        if (value === undefined || value === null) continue\n        if (typeof value === 'object' && value !== null) {\n          if (Array.isArray(value)) {\n            lines.push(`${pad}${key}:`)\n            lines.push(this.serializeYaml(value, indent + 1))\n          } else {\n            lines.push(`${pad}${key}:`)\n            lines.push(this.serializeYaml(value, indent + 1))\n          }\n        } else {\n          // 基础类型，需要 YAML 安全转义\n          const val = String(value)\n          if (val.includes(':') || val.includes('#') || val.includes('\\n') || val.startsWith(' ') || val.endsWith(' ')) {\n            lines.push(`${pad}${key}: \"${val.replace(/\"/g, '\\\\\"')}\"`)\n          } else {\n            lines.push(`${pad}${key}: ${val}`)\n          }\n        }\n      }\n    }\n\n    return lines.join('\\n')\n  }\n\n  private async saveYaml(filePath: string, data: object): Promise<void> {\n    const yaml = this.serializeYaml(data)\n    const result = await window.electronAPI.writeFile(filePath, yaml)\n    if (!result.success) throw new Error(result.error || '写入失败')\n  }\n\n  /** 简单解析 YAML（仅处理本次用到的结构） */\n  private parseYamlFacts(content: string): object {\n    // 使用 eval 风格解析（仅处理 { key: value } 结构，facts 文件格式已知）\n    // facts YAML 格式固定，不存在复杂标签\n    try {\n      // 替换 YAML 注释\n      const clean = content.replace(/#.*/g, '')\n      // 替换单引号和双引号包裹的字符串\n      const processed = clean\n        .replace(/'([^']*)'/g, '\"$1\"')\n        .replace(/-\\s+(\\w+):/g, '- \"$1\":')\n        .replace(/^(\\w+):/gm, '\"$1\":')\n      return JSON.parse(processed)\n    } catch {\n      return {}\n    }\n  }\n}\n\nconst factsStore = new FactsStore()\nexport default factsStore\n"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":51411,"output":2191,"cacheRead":19262,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":72864,"cost":{"input":0.0154233,"output":0.0026292,"cacheRead":0.0011557199999999998,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.019208219999999998}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776152847801,"responseId":"062d240f81e337887615fabffaedec3b"}}
