{"type":"message","id":"57d435e8","parentId":"a9bc65a0","timestamp":"2026-04-14T07:52:48.117Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Renderer built successfully. Let me now provide a summary of all the fixes that were made in this session.","thinkingSignature":"b72b07730042eaf6aaace1387e0937eb7885a8256a0cf12e5c16a059a8f2059e"},{"type":"text","text":"✅ **编译通过。**\n\n---\n\n## 本轮修复汇总\n\n| 步骤 | 内容 | 状态 |\n|------|------|------|\n| ① `src/main/aiService.ts` | 注册 `ai:call/stream/saveApiKey/testConnection` IPC 处理器 | ✅ |\n| ② `src/main/backupService.ts` | 注册 `backup:create/list/restore/delete` IPC 处理器 | ✅ |\n| ③ `src/main/index.ts` | `fs.promises.rmdir` → `fs.promises.rm`（Node 16+ API） | ✅ |\n| ④ `project.js` | `_normalizeCharacter()` 字段映射（姓名→name、MBTI人格→mbti） | ✅ |\n| ⑤ `db/index.ts` 重构 | 移除假 SQL 调用，改为读写 `facts/*.yaml` 文件 | ✅ |\n| ⑥ `factExtractor.ts` | `saveFacts()` 改用 `factsStore.appendFacts()` | ✅ |\n| ⑦ `FactsPanel.tsx` | 改用 `factsStore.getFacts()` | ✅ |\n| ⑧ `Workbench.tsx` | 打开项目时初始化 `factsStore.setProjectRoot()` | ✅ |\n\n**修复后的 facts 数据流：**\n```\nAI 提取事实（factExtractor）\n    ↓\nfactsStore.appendFacts() 追加写入\n    ↓\nfacts/characters_facts.yaml（角色能力/关系）\nfacts/plot_facts.yaml（伏笔）\n    ↓\ngenerate-chapter.js 读取并注入 AI prompt ✅\n```"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":59137,"output":350,"cacheRead":19262,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":78749,"cost":{"input":0.0177411,"output":0.00041999999999999996,"cacheRead":0.0011557199999999998,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.01931682}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776153157262,"responseId":"062d2545fca459934b194027197e9f31"}}
