{"type":"message","id":"b9bc769c","parentId":"27aad9b9","timestamp":"2026-04-14T07:58:06.077Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants another comprehensive, strict review of every aspect of the project. Let me do a thorough review covering all the layers: architecture, data quality, code quality, security, and system integrity.\n\nLet me systematically check everything:\n\n1. The compiled code\n2. The actual runtime behavior\n3. Security issues\n4. Data consistency\n5. The facts YAML serialization I just wrote\n6. The AI service implementation\n7. The backup service implementation\n8. Any remaining dead code or inconsistencies\n\nLet me start with the most critical: my new code. The YAML serializer I wrote is particularly suspicious since I hand-rolled it without proper YAML library.","thinkingSignature":"da6ad0d26b6f1665e4ffe5ceadd8979699ab7e289266e2fa8476588859ca9c25"},{"type":"text","text":"好，上一轮修了问题，这次专门针对**刚写的代码**做最严苛的审查。\n\n---\n\n## 第 1 步：审查我刚写的 `factsStore` 的 YAML 序列化\n\n**思考：** 我手写了 `serializeYaml`，这最容易出 bug。先验证它序列化出来的 YAML 是否真的能被 `yaml.load()` 正确解析。\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_54zn1vtm59ou_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"node -e \"\nconst yaml = require('/mnt/d/aafuzhi/axs/my-novel-tools/node_modules/js-yaml');\nconst fs = require('fs');\n\n// 模拟 factsStore.serializeYaml 的逻辑\nfunction serializeYaml(obj, indent = 0) {\n  const pad = '  '.repeat(indent);\n  const lines = [];\n  if (obj === null || obj === undefined) return '';\n  if (typeof obj !== 'object') return String(obj);\n  if (Array.isArray(obj)) {\n    for (const item of obj) {\n      if (typeof item === 'object' && item !== null) {\n        lines.push(pad + '-');\n        lines.push(serializeYaml(item, indent + 1));\n      } else {\n        lines.push(pad + '- ' + item);\n      }\n    }\n  } else {\n    for (const [key, value] of Object.entries(obj)) {\n      if (value === undefined || value === null) continue;\n      if (typeof value === 'object') {\n        lines.push(pad + key + ':');\n        lines.push(serializeYaml(value, indent + 1));\n      } else {\n        const val = String(value);\n        if (val.includes(':') || val.includes('#') || val.includes('\\n') || val.startsWith(' ') || val.endsWith(' ')) {\n          lines.push(pad + key + ': \\\"' + val.replace(/\\\"/g, '\\\\\\\"') + '\\\"');\n        } else {\n          lines.push(pad + key + ': ' + val);\n        }\n      }\n    }\n  }\n  return lines.join('\\n');\n}\n\n// 测试用例：characters_facts.yaml 标准结构\nconst testData = {\n  '林枫': {\n    mbti: 'INTJ',\n    core_fear: '恐惧感官失控',\n    abilities: ['剑术天才', '重生记忆'],\n    relationships: { '青云子': '师父', '血魔': '仇敌' }\n  }\n};\n\nconst serialized = serializeYaml(testData);\nconsole.log('=== 序列化结果 ===');\nconsole.log(serialized);\nconsole.log('=== 重新解析 ===');\ntry {\n  const reparsed = yaml.load(serialized);\n  console.log('✅ 解析成功');\n  console.log('林枫 abilities:', reparsed['林枫'].abilities);\n  console.log('林枫 relationships:', JSON.stringify(reparsed['林枫'].relationships));\n} catch(e) {\n  console.log('❌ 解析失败:', e.message);\n}\n\""}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":54,"output":746,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":75874,"totalTokens":76674,"cost":{"input":0.0000162,"output":0.0008952,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0.028452750000000002,"total":0.029364150000000002}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776153459469,"responseId":"062d267482fc73b8b29224f5288f2460"}}
