{"type":"message","id":"029be197","parentId":"2342dce4","timestamp":"2026-04-14T07:59:46.156Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_nnkxhmt4k6d2_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"import { app, BrowserWindow, ipcMain, dialog, shell, safeStorage } from 'electron'\nimport path from 'path'\nimport fs, { FSWatcher } from 'fs'\n\n// 重新导出 main.ts 的功能\n// 这是为了保持统一的导入路径：import { createWindow } from '../src/main/index'\n\n// 保持对窗口对象的全局引用，避免被垃圾回收\nlet mainWindow: BrowserWindow | null = null"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":74,"aggregated":"import { app, BrowserWindow, ipcMain, dialog, shell, safeStorage } from 'electron'\nimport path from 'path'\nimport fs, { FSWatcher } from 'fs'\n\n// 重新导出 main.ts 的功能\n// 这是为了保持统一的导入路径：import { createWindow } from '../src/main/index'\n\n// 保持对窗口对象的全局引用，避免被垃圾回收\nlet mainWindow: BrowserWindow | null = null","cwd":"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/main"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1776153586141}}
{"type":"message","id":"9d82a6cc","parentId":"029be197","timestamp":"2026-04-14T07:59:56.491Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I see the imports. I need to add the yamlService import. But there's a complication - the code uses `require()` for aiService and backupService (CommonJS style), but the file starts with ES module imports. Let me check how it handles this discrepancy.\n\nActually, TypeScript with `\"module\": \"CommonJS\"` means all imports are compiled to CommonJS `require()`. So I can use either ES module import or CommonJS require. Let me just add the import alongside the existing require style.\n\nActually, looking at the file more carefully, it uses `require('./aiService')` and `require('./backupService')` in the function body. \n\nSince tsconfig enforces CommonJS, I'll add the yamlService import to match the existing pattern, then integrate it into the setupIpcHandlers function where aiService and backupService are already being initialized.","thinkingSignature":"37cbf98091483083f1d1dc50a16f4ede8c2aace26568cdb0fab9bfc46274a326"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_59us8lnkzzl3_1","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"/mnt/d/aafuzhi/axs/src/main/index.ts","edits":[{"oldText":"import { app, BrowserWindow, ipcMain, dialog, shell, safeStorage } from 'electron'\nimport path from 'path'\nimport fs, { FSWatcher } from 'fs'","newText":"import { app, BrowserWindow, ipcMain, dialog, shell, safeStorage } from 'electron'\nimport path from 'path'\nimport fs, { FSWatcher } from 'fs'\nimport { setupYamlHandlers } from './yamlService'"}]}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":61134,"output":329,"cacheRead":19262,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":80725,"cost":{"input":0.018340199999999997,"output":0.0003948,"cacheRead":0.0011557199999999998,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.019890719999999997}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776153586164,"responseId":"062d26f157674c5d81fabd4b041351d4"}}
