{"type":"message","id":"02aa3b3b","parentId":"c8cf71ce","timestamp":"2026-04-14T08:10:52.506Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"FactsPanel is using `factsStore.getFacts(filters)` correctly. Let me now check the Editor.tsx to make sure it's not doing anything problematic.","thinkingSignature":"f63d223a1a51bb8868720537e5781752181cb574b018cb48a9ccbdaf9a4106e8"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_d0rsoc2jipix_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cat /mnt/d/aafuzhi/axs/src/renderer/src/components/Editor.tsx"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":70310,"output":76,"cacheRead":19262,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":89648,"cost":{"input":0.021093,"output":0.0000912,"cacheRead":0.0011557199999999998,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.02233992}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776154249063,"responseId":"062d2988a6df1ed880c93f7a44f125a0"}}
{"type":"message","id":"2fce33fe","parentId":"02aa3b3b","timestamp":"2026-04-14T08:10:52.772Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_d0rsoc2jipix_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"import { useEffect, useRef, useState } from 'react'\nimport * as monaco from 'monaco-editor'\nimport { Spin } from 'antd'\nimport { loader } from '@monaco-editor/react'\n\n// 配置 Monaco Editor 加载路径\nloader.config({\n  paths: {\n    vs: 'https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/monaco-editor@0.45.0/min/vs'\n  }\n})\n\ninterface EditorProps {\n  value: string\n  onChange: (value: string | undefined) => void\n  filePath?: string\n}\n\nconst Editor = ({ value, onChange, filePath }: EditorProps) => {\n  const editorRef = useRef<HTMLDivElement>(null)\n  const monacoEditorRef = useRef<monaco.editor.IStandaloneCodeEditor | null>(null)\n  const [loading, setLoading] = useState(true)\n\n  // 初始化编辑器\n  useEffect(() => {\n    if (!editorRef.current) return\n\n    let isMounted = true\n    \n    const initEditor = async () => {\n      try {\n        // 加载 Monaco Editor\n        await loader.init()\n\n        if (!isMounted || !editorRef.current) return\n\n        // 创建编辑器实例\n        const editor = monaco.editor.create(editorRef.current, {\n          value,\n          language: 'markdown',\n          theme: 'vs-light',\n          fontSize: 16,\n          lineHeight: 1.8,\n          lineNumbers: 'on',\n          wordWrap: 'on',\n          wrappingIndent: 'indent',\n          automaticLayout: true,\n          minimap: { enabled: false },\n          scrollBeyondLastLine: false,\n          tabSize: 2,\n          insertSpaces: true,\n          renderWhitespace: 'none',\n          renderLineHighlight: 'line',\n          scrollbar: {\n            verticalScrollbarSize: 10,\n            horizontalScrollbarSize: 10,\n          },\n        })\n\n        // 监听内容变化\n        editor.onDidChangeModelContent(() => {\n          const newValue = editor.getValue()\n          onChange(newValue)\n        })\n\n        // 保存快捷键\n        editor.addCommand(monaco.KeyMod.CtrlCmd | monaco.KeyCode.KeyS, () => {\n          // 保存由 Workbench 处理\n          const saveEvent = new KeyboardEvent('keydown', {\n            key: 's',\n            ctrlKey: true,\n            bubbles: true\n          })\n          window.dispatchEvent(saveEvent)\n        })\n\n        monacoEditorRef.current = editor\n        setLoading(false)\n      } catch (error) {\n        console.error('初始化编辑器失败:', error)\n        setLoading(false)\n      }\n    }\n\n    initEditor()\n\n    return () => {\n      isMounted = false\n      if (monacoEditorRef.current) {\n        monacoEditorRef.current.dispose()\n        monacoEditorRef.current = null\n      }\n    }\n  }, [])\n\n  // 当外部 value 变化时更新编辑器内容\n  useEffect(() => {\n    if (!monacoEditorRef.current) return\n    \n    const currentValue = monacoEditorRef.current.getValue()\n    if (currentValue !== value) {\n      monacoEditorRef.current.setValue(value)\n    }\n  }, [value])\n\n  // 根据文件类型切换语言模式\n  useEffect(() => {\n    if (!monacoEditorRef.current || !filePath) return\n    \n    const model = monacoEditorRef.current.getModel()\n    if (!model) return\n    \n    if (filePath.endsWith('.md') || filePath.endsWith('.markdown')) {\n      monaco.editor.setModelLanguage(model, 'markdown')\n    } else if (filePath.endsWith('.yaml') || filePath.endsWith('.yml')) {\n      monaco.editor.setModelLanguage(model, 'yaml')\n    } else if (filePath.endsWith('.json')) {\n      monaco.editor.setModelLanguage(model, 'json')\n    }\n  }, [filePath])\n\n  if (loading) {\n    return (\n      <div style={{ height: '100%', display: 'flex', alignItems: 'center', justifyContent: 'center' }}>\n        <Spin tip=\"加载编辑器中...\" />\n      </div>\n    )\n  }\n\n  return (\n    <div ref={editorRef} style={{ width: '100%', height: '100%' }} />\n  )\n}\n\nexport default Editor"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":172,"aggregated":"import { useEffect, useRef, useState } from 'react'\nimport * as monaco from 'monaco-editor'\nimport { Spin } from 'antd'\nimport { loader } from '@monaco-editor/react'\n\n// 配置 Monaco Editor 加载路径\nloader.config({\n  paths: {\n    vs: 'https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/monaco-editor@0.45.0/min/vs'\n  }\n})\n\ninterface EditorProps {\n  value: string\n  onChange: (value: string | undefined) => void\n  filePath?: string\n}\n\nconst Editor = ({ value, onChange, filePath }: EditorProps) => {\n  const editorRef = useRef<HTMLDivElement>(null)\n  const monacoEditorRef = useRef<monaco.editor.IStandaloneCodeEditor | null>(null)\n  const [loading, setLoading] = useState(true)\n\n  // 初始化编辑器\n  useEffect(() => {\n    if (!editorRef.current) return\n\n    let isMounted = true\n    \n    const initEditor = async () => {\n      try {\n        // 加载 Monaco Editor\n        await loader.init()\n\n        if (!isMounted || !editorRef.current) return\n\n        // 创建编辑器实例\n        const editor = monaco.editor.create(editorRef.current, {\n          value,\n          language: 'markdown',\n          theme: 'vs-light',\n          fontSize: 16,\n          lineHeight: 1.8,\n          lineNumbers: 'on',\n          wordWrap: 'on',\n          wrappingIndent: 'indent',\n          automaticLayout: true,\n          minimap: { enabled: false },\n          scrollBeyondLastLine: false,\n          tabSize: 2,\n          insertSpaces: true,\n          renderWhitespace: 'none',\n          renderLineHighlight: 'line',\n          scrollbar: {\n            verticalScrollbarSize: 10,\n            horizontalScrollbarSize: 10,\n          },\n        })\n\n        // 监听内容变化\n        editor.onDidChangeModelContent(() => {\n          const newValue = editor.getValue()\n          onChange(newValue)\n        })\n\n        // 保存快捷键\n        editor.addCommand(monaco.KeyMod.CtrlCmd | monaco.KeyCode.KeyS, () => {\n          // 保存由 Workbench 处理\n          const saveEvent = new KeyboardEvent('keydown', {\n            key: 's',\n            ctrlKey: true,\n            bubbles: true\n          })\n          window.dispatchEvent(saveEvent)\n        })\n\n        monacoEditorRef.current = editor\n        setLoading(false)\n      } catch (error) {\n        console.error('初始化编辑器失败:', error)\n        setLoading(false)\n      }\n    }\n\n    initEditor()\n\n    return () => {\n      isMounted = false\n      if (monacoEditorRef.current) {\n        monacoEditorRef.current.dispose()\n        monacoEditorRef.current = null\n      }\n    }\n  }, [])\n\n  // 当外部 value 变化时更新编辑器内容\n  useEffect(() => {\n    if (!monacoEditorRef.current) return\n    \n    const currentValue = monacoEditorRef.current.getValue()\n    if (currentValue !== value) {\n      monacoEditorRef.current.setValue(value)\n    }\n  }, [value])\n\n  // 根据文件类型切换语言模式\n  useEffect(() => {\n    if (!monacoEditorRef.current || !filePath) return\n    \n    const model = monacoEditorRef.current.getModel()\n    if (!model) return\n    \n    if (filePath.endsWith('.md') || filePath.endsWith('.markdown')) {\n      monaco.editor.setModelLanguage(model, 'markdown')\n    } else if (filePath.endsWith('.yaml') || filePath.endsWith('.yml')) {\n      monaco.editor.setModelLanguage(model, 'yaml')\n    } else if (filePath.endsWith('.json')) {\n      monaco.editor.setModelLanguage(model, 'json')\n    }\n  }, [filePath])\n\n  if (loading) {\n    return (\n      <div style={{ height: '100%', display: 'flex', alignItems: 'center', justifyContent: 'center' }}>\n        <Spin tip=\"加载编辑器中...\" />\n      </div>\n    )\n  }\n\n  return (\n    <div ref={editorRef} style={{ width: '100%', height: '100%' }} />\n  )\n}\n\nexport default Editor","cwd":"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/main"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1776154252740}}
{"type":"message","id":"c0125bf0","parentId":"2fce33fe","timestamp":"2026-04-14T08:10:59.445Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Editor.tsx looks clean. It's properly using:\n1. `loader.config` to set Monaco Editor CDN path\n2. Proper cleanup in useEffect\n3. `isMounted` flag to prevent state updates after unmount\n4. Proper dispose of Monaco editor on cleanup\n5. External value changes handled correctly\n\nNow let me check the AIToolsPanel.tsx.","thinkingSignature":"d6e9adfc94355d8cfdda57a0a79b91109b5ecf7f4c5a99654f732142718cd7a8"},{"type":"text","text":"Editor.tsx 干净，无问题。\n\n---\n\n## 第 3 步：审查 AIToolsPanel 的 facts 提取调用\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_oas6b8sm6vls_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cat /mnt/d/aafuzhi/axs/src/renderer/src/components/AIToolsPanel.tsx"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":71313,"output":151,"cacheRead":19262,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":90726,"cost":{"input":0.0213939,"output":0.00018119999999999999,"cacheRead":0.0011557199999999998,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.02273082}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776154252776,"responseId":"062d298d9e5ba7bbb662b906ccfddc8e"}}
{"type":"message","id":"bd320016","parentId":"c0125bf0","timestamp":"2026-04-14T08:10:59.650Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_oas6b8sm6vls_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"import { useState } from 'react'\nimport { Button, Space, Card, Input, message, Spin } from 'antd'\nimport {\n  EditOutlined,\n  ExpandOutlined,\n  CheckCircleOutlined,\n  ThunderboltOutlined\n} from '@ant-design/icons'\nimport aiModelService from '../services/aiModels'\nimport factExtractor from '../services/factExtractor'\n\nconst { TextArea } = Input\n\ninterface AIToolsPanelProps {\n  chapterContent: string\n  chapterPath: string | null\n  onInsertText: (text: string) => void\n}\n\nconst AIToolsPanel = ({ chapterContent, chapterPath, onInsertText }: AIToolsPanelProps) => {\n  const [generating, setGenerating] = useState(false)\n  const [result, setResult] = useState('')\n  const [prompt, setPrompt] = useState('')\n\n  // 智能续写\n  const handleContinue = async () => {\n    if (!chapterContent) {\n      message.warning('请先选择章节并编写内容')\n      return\n    }\n\n    setGenerating(true)\n    setResult('')\n    \n    try {\n      // 获取最后500个字符作为上下文\n      const context = chapterContent.slice(-500)\n      const fullPrompt = `请继续写下面的小说内容，风格保持一致，衔接自然：\n\n${context}\n\n续写内容：`\n\n      await aiModelService.stream(\n        'creative',\n        fullPrompt,\n        (chunk, done) => {\n          setResult(prev => prev + chunk)\n        },\n        (error) => {\n          message.error(`续写失败：${error}`)\n        }\n      )\n    } catch (error) {\n      message.error('续写失败')\n    } finally {\n      setGenerating(false)\n    }\n  }\n\n  // 定向扩写\n  const handleExpand = async () => {\n    if (!prompt) {\n      message.warning('请输入扩写要求')\n      return\n    }\n\n    setGenerating(true)\n    setResult('')\n\n    try {\n      const fullPrompt = `请根据以下要求扩写小说内容：\n要求：${prompt}\n上下文：\n${chapterContent.slice(-1000)}\n\n扩写后的内容：`\n\n      await aiModelService.stream(\n        'creative',\n        fullPrompt,\n        (chunk, done) => {\n          setResult(prev => prev + chunk)\n        },\n        (error) => {\n          message.error(`扩写失败：${error}`)\n        }\n      )\n    } catch (error) {\n      message.error('扩写失败')\n    } finally {\n      setGenerating(false)\n    }\n  }\n\n  // 逻辑校验\n  const handleCheck = async () => {\n    if (!chapterContent) {\n      message.warning('请先选择章节')\n      return\n    }\n\n    setGenerating(true)\n    setResult('')\n\n    try {\n      const result = await aiModelService.call(\n        'logic',\n        chapterContent,\n        {\n          systemPrompt: `请检查以下小说章节内容的逻辑一致性，找出矛盾点、战力崩坏、情节不合理的地方，给出修改建议。`\n        }\n      )\n\n      if (result.success && result.content) {\n        setResult(result.content)\n      } else {\n        message.error(result.error || '校验失败')\n      }\n    } catch (error) {\n      message.error('逻辑校验失败')\n    } finally {\n      setGenerating(false)\n    }\n  }\n\n  // 提取事实\n  const handleExtract = async () => {\n    if (!chapterContent || !chapterPath) {\n      message.warning('请先选择章节')\n      return\n    }\n\n    setGenerating(true)\n    setResult('')\n\n    try {\n      // 提取章节号\n      const chapterMatch = chapterPath.match(/第(\\d+)章/)\n      const chapterNumber = chapterMatch ? parseInt(chapterMatch[1]) : 1\n\n      const facts = await factExtractor.extract(chapterContent, chapterNumber)\n      \n      if (facts.length === 0) {\n        setResult('未提取到任何事实')\n        return\n      }\n\n      // 格式化结果\n      let output = `提取到 ${facts.length} 条事实：\\n\\n`\n      facts.forEach((fact, index) => {\n        output += `${index + 1}. [${fact.type}] ${fact.subject}${fact.object ? ' → ' + fact.object : ''}\\n`\n        output += `   ${fact.content} (置信度: ${(fact.confidence * 100).toFixed(0)}%)\\n\\n`\n      })\n\n      output += `是否保存到事实台账？`\n      setResult(output)\n    } catch (error) {\n      message.error('事实提取失败')\n    } finally {\n      setGenerating(false)\n    }\n  }\n\n  // 应用生成结果\n  const handleApply = () => {\n    if (!result) return\n    onInsertText(result)\n    message.success('已插入内容')\n    setResult('')\n  }\n\n  return (\n    <div style={{ height: '100%', display: 'flex', flexDirection: 'column' }}>\n      <div style={{ padding: 16, borderBottom: '1px solid #e8e8e8' }}>\n        <h3 style={{ margin: '0 0 10px 0' }}>AI 工具</h3>\n        <Space direction=\"vertical\" style={{ width: '100%' }}>\n          <Button\n            type=\"primary\"\n            block\n            icon={<EditOutlined />}\n            onClick={handleContinue}\n            loading={generating}\n            disabled={!chapterContent}\n          >\n            智能续写\n          </Button>\n          <Button\n            block\n            icon={<ExpandOutlined />}\n            onClick={handleExpand}\n            loading={generating}\n            disabled={!chapterContent}\n          >\n            定向扩写\n          </Button>\n          <Button\n            block\n            icon={<CheckCircleOutlined />}\n            onClick={handleCheck}\n            loading={generating}\n            disabled={!chapterContent}\n          >\n            逻辑校验\n          </Button>\n          <Button\n            block\n            icon={<ThunderboltOutlined />}\n            onClick={handleExtract}\n            loading={generating}\n            disabled={!chapterContent}\n          >\n            提取事实\n          </Button>\n\n          <TextArea\n            placeholder=\"输入扩写/修改要求（可选）\"\n            rows={3}\n            value={prompt}\n            onChange={(e) => setPrompt(e.target.value)}\n          />\n        </Space>\n      </div>\n\n      <div style={{ flex: 1, overflow: 'auto', padding: 16 }}>\n        {generating ? (\n          <div style={{ textAlign: 'center', padding: 40 }}>\n            <Spin tip=\"AI 生成中...\" />\n          </div>\n        ) : result ? (\n          <Card\n            size=\"small\"\n            title=\"AI 生成结果\"\n            extra={\n              <Button\n                type=\"link\"\n                size=\"small\"\n                onClick={handleApply}\n              >\n                插入到编辑器\n              </Button>\n            }\n            style={{ whiteSpace: 'pre-wrap', wordBreak: 'break-all' }}\n          >\n            {result}\n          </Card>\n        ) : (\n          <div style={{ color: '#999', textAlign: 'center', padding: 40 }}>\n            选择上方工具开始使用 AI 辅助创作\n          </div>\n        )}\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  )\n}\n\nexport default AIToolsPanel"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":117,"aggregated":"import { useState } from 'react'\nimport { Button, Space, Card, Input, message, Spin } from 'antd'\nimport {\n  EditOutlined,\n  ExpandOutlined,\n  CheckCircleOutlined,\n  ThunderboltOutlined\n} from '@ant-design/icons'\nimport aiModelService from '../services/aiModels'\nimport factExtractor from '../services/factExtractor'\n\nconst { TextArea } = Input\n\ninterface AIToolsPanelProps {\n  chapterContent: string\n  chapterPath: string | null\n  onInsertText: (text: string) => void\n}\n\nconst AIToolsPanel = ({ chapterContent, chapterPath, onInsertText }: AIToolsPanelProps) => {\n  const [generating, setGenerating] = useState(false)\n  const [result, setResult] = useState('')\n  const [prompt, setPrompt] = useState('')\n\n  // 智能续写\n  const handleContinue = async () => {\n    if (!chapterContent) {\n      message.warning('请先选择章节并编写内容')\n      return\n    }\n\n    setGenerating(true)\n    setResult('')\n    \n    try {\n      // 获取最后500个字符作为上下文\n      const context = chapterContent.slice(-500)\n      const fullPrompt = `请继续写下面的小说内容，风格保持一致，衔接自然：\n\n${context}\n\n续写内容：`\n\n      await aiModelService.stream(\n        'creative',\n        fullPrompt,\n        (chunk, done) => {\n          setResult(prev => prev + chunk)\n        },\n        (error) => {\n          message.error(`续写失败：${error}`)\n        }\n      )\n    } catch (error) {\n      message.error('续写失败')\n    } finally {\n      setGenerating(false)\n    }\n  }\n\n  // 定向扩写\n  const handleExpand = async () => {\n    if (!prompt) {\n      message.warning('请输入扩写要求')\n      return\n    }\n\n    setGenerating(true)\n    setResult('')\n\n    try {\n      const fullPrompt = `请根据以下要求扩写小说内容：\n要求：${prompt}\n上下文：\n${chapterContent.slice(-1000)}\n\n扩写后的内容：`\n\n      await aiModelService.stream(\n        'creative',\n        fullPrompt,\n        (chunk, done) => {\n          setResult(prev => prev + chunk)\n        },\n        (error) => {\n          message.error(`扩写失败：${error}`)\n        }\n      )\n    } catch (error) {\n      message.error('扩写失败')\n    } finally {\n      setGenerating(false)\n    }\n  }\n\n  // 逻辑校验\n  const handleCheck = async () => {\n    if (!chapterContent) {\n      message.warning('请先选择章节')\n      return\n    }\n\n    setGenerating(true)\n    setResult('')\n\n    try {\n      const result = await aiModelService.call(\n        'logic',\n        chapterContent,\n        {\n          systemPrompt: `请检查以下小说章节内容的逻辑一致性，找出矛盾点、战力崩坏、情节不合理的地方，给出修改建议。`\n        }\n      )\n\n      if (result.success && result.content) {\n        setResult(result.content)\n      } else {\n        message.error(result.error || '校验失败')\n      }\n    } catch (error) {\n      message.error('逻辑校验失败')\n    } finally {\n      setGenerating(false)\n    }\n  }\n\n  // 提取事实\n  const handleExtract = async () => {\n    if (!chapterContent || !chapterPath) {\n      message.warning('请先选择章节')\n      return\n    }\n\n    setGenerating(true)\n    setResult('')\n\n    try {\n      // 提取章节号\n      const chapterMatch = chapterPath.match(/第(\\d+)章/)\n      const chapterNumber = chapterMatch ? parseInt(chapterMatch[1]) : 1\n\n      const facts = await factExtractor.extract(chapterContent, chapterNumber)\n      \n      if (facts.length === 0) {\n        setResult('未提取到任何事实')\n        return\n      }\n\n      // 格式化结果\n      let output = `提取到 ${facts.length} 条事实：\\n\\n`\n      facts.forEach((fact, index) => {\n        output += `${index + 1}. [${fact.type}] ${fact.subject}${fact.object ? ' → ' + fact.object : ''}\\n`\n        output += `   ${fact.content} (置信度: ${(fact.confidence * 100).toFixed(0)}%)\\n\\n`\n      })\n\n      output += `是否保存到事实台账？`\n      setResult(output)\n    } catch (error) {\n      message.error('事实提取失败')\n    } finally {\n      setGenerating(false)\n    }\n  }\n\n  // 应用生成结果\n  const handleApply = () => {\n    if (!result) return\n    onInsertText(result)\n    message.success('已插入内容')\n    setResult('')\n  }\n\n  return (\n    <div style={{ height: '100%', display: 'flex', flexDirection: 'column' }}>\n      <div style={{ padding: 16, borderBottom: '1px solid #e8e8e8' }}>\n        <h3 style={{ margin: '0 0 10px 0' }}>AI 工具</h3>\n        <Space direction=\"vertical\" style={{ width: '100%' }}>\n          <Button\n            type=\"primary\"\n            block\n            icon={<EditOutlined />}\n            onClick={handleContinue}\n            loading={generating}\n            disabled={!chapterContent}\n          >\n            智能续写\n          </Button>\n          <Button\n            block\n            icon={<ExpandOutlined />}\n            onClick={handleExpand}\n            loading={generating}\n            disabled={!chapterContent}\n          >\n            定向扩写\n          </Button>\n          <Button\n            block\n            icon={<CheckCircleOutlined />}\n            onClick={handleCheck}\n            loading={generating}\n            disabled={!chapterContent}\n          >\n            逻辑校验\n          </Button>\n          <Button\n            block\n            icon={<ThunderboltOutlined />}\n            onClick={handleExtract}\n            loading={generating}\n            disabled={!chapterContent}\n          >\n            提取事实\n          </Button>\n\n          <TextArea\n            placeholder=\"输入扩写/修改要求（可选）\"\n            rows={3}\n            value={prompt}\n            onChange={(e) => setPrompt(e.target.value)}\n          />\n        </Space>\n      </div>\n\n      <div style={{ flex: 1, overflow: 'auto', padding: 16 }}>\n        {generating ? (\n          <div style={{ textAlign: 'center', padding: 40 }}>\n            <Spin tip=\"AI 生成中...\" />\n          </div>\n        ) : result ? (\n          <Card\n            size=\"small\"\n            title=\"AI 生成结果\"\n            extra={\n              <Button\n                type=\"link\"\n                size=\"small\"\n                onClick={handleApply}\n              >\n                插入到编辑器\n              </Button>\n            }\n            style={{ whiteSpace: 'pre-wrap', wordBreak: 'break-all' }}\n          >\n            {result}\n          </Card>\n        ) : (\n          <div style={{ color: '#999', textAlign: 'center', padding: 40 }}>\n            选择上方工具开始使用 AI 辅助创作\n          </div>\n        )}\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  )\n}\n\nexport default AIToolsPanel","cwd":"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/main"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1776154259629}}
{"type":"message","id":"a897a8d0","parentId":"bd320016","timestamp":"2026-04-14T08:11:05.459Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"error","timestamp":1776154259656,"errorMessage":"529 {\"type\":\"error\",\"error\":{\"type\":\"overloaded_error\",\"message\":\"当前服务集群负载较高，请稍后重试，感谢您的耐心等待。 (2064) (529)\"},\"request_id\":\"062d2997a1ac59f85d27d983de852265\"}"}}
{"type":"message","id":"5c4ab65e","parentId":"a897a8d0","timestamp":"2026-04-14T08:11:29.188Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I see a critical issue! In AIToolsPanel, `handleExtract` extracts facts using `factExtractor.extract()` but then it only displays the result with `是否保存到事实台账？` prompt. But there's NO \"Save\" button! The user is asked whether to save but there's no actual save action triggered.\n\nLooking at the result display:\n```output += `是否保存到事实台账？` ```\nThen the \"插入到编辑器\" button just calls `onInsertText(result)` which inserts the text into the editor.\n\nThis means the \"extract facts\" feature is incomplete - it extracts facts but never actually saves them to the YAML files via `factsStore.appendFacts()`.\n\n\nThe save functionality needs to be added to actually persist the facts to storage.","thinkingSignature":"a0d0a16d689984e4654fbe48507417f3d7b7b632252e029b547fa0f5be58dc68"},{"type":"text","text":"\n🔴 **发现 P1 bug：facts 提取后\"保存\"按钮缺失。**\n\n`handleExtract` 显示 `是否保存到事实台账？` 但没有实际保存逻辑。需要加保存按钮。\n\n---\n\n## 第 4 步：审查 package.json 依赖 vs 实际使用\n\n**思考：** `@monaco-editor/react` 是我们刚装的，但其他依赖是否有缺失或版本冲突？\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_qgcm1dwltnza_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd /mnt/d/aafuzhi/axs && node -e \"\nconst fs = require('fs');\nconst pkg = JSON.parse(fs.readFileSync('package.json', 'utf8'));\n\n// 获取 package.json 中所有依赖\nconst deps = Object.keys({...pkg.dependencies, ...pkg.devDependencies});\nconst missing = [];\nconst present = [];\n\ndeps.forEach(dep => {\n  try {\n    require.resolve(dep, { paths: ['node_modules'] });\n    present.push(dep);\n  } catch {\n    missing.push(dep);\n  }\n});\n\nconsole.log('✅ 已安装:', present.length);\nconsole.log('❌ 缺失:');\nmissing.forEach(m => console.log('  -', m));\n\""}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":73045,"output":410,"cacheRead":19262,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":92717,"cost":{"input":0.02191