{"type":"message","id":"2ac9781d","parentId":"5c4ab65e","timestamp":"2026-04-14T08:11:29.929Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_qgcm1dwltnza_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"✅ 已安装: 31\n❌ 缺失:\n  - @types/js-yaml\n  - @types/node\n  - @types/react\n  - @types/react-dom"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":655,"aggregated":"✅ 已安装: 31\n❌ 缺失:\n  - @types/js-yaml\n  - @types/node\n  - @types/react\n  - @types/react-dom","cwd":"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/main"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1776154289906}}
{"type":"message","id":"3a4f4f1d","parentId":"2ac9781d","timestamp":"2026-04-14T08:11:39.385Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The missing ones are type packages (`@types/*`), not runtime packages. These are `devDependencies` so they're listed in `devDependencies` in package.json. The reason `require.resolve` fails is that it looks for the package root `index.js`, but type packages don't have that. This is expected behavior for `@types/*` packages - they don't need runtime resolution.\n\nLet me verify these are actually in devDependencies.","thinkingSignature":"5888de028b9e1ebef6dad86a5982893366141159c9c1bf00b3d3d4c242a29767"},{"type":"text","text":"`@types/*` 包没有 runtime 入口，`require.resolve` 失败是正常的。确认它们在 devDependencies 里：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_g18gny212d0h_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd /mnt/d/aafuzhi/axs && node -e \"\nconst pkg = JSON.parse(require('fs').readFileSync('package.json', 'utf8'));\nconst devDeps = Object.keys(pkg.devDependencies || {});\nconst typePkgs = ['@types/js-yaml', '@types/node', '@types/react', '@types/react-dom'];\ntypePkgs.forEach(p => {\n  const found = devDeps.includes(p);\n  console.log((found?'✅':'❌') + ' ' + p + ':', found ? pkg.devDependencies[p] : 'NOT IN devDependencies');\n});\n\""}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":73509,"output":263,"cacheRead":19262,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":93034,"cost":{"input":0.022052699999999998,"output":0.0003156,"cacheRead":0.0011557199999999998,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.023524019999999996}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776154289935,"responseId":"062d29b1089e5f45fa2b2b638dd89658"}}
