{"type":"message","id":"f74cee6d","parentId":"e445f326","timestamp":"2026-04-14T08:13:10.760Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I see several issues:1. **豆包 endpoint 错误**：所有豆包模型都用同一个 endpoint `https://ark.cn-beijing.volces.com/api/v3/chat/completions`，但 doubao-lite 和 doubao-mini 可能需要不同的模型名称。\n2. **`doubao-lite` 没有专属 endpoint**：它被设为 `'doubao-lite-32k'`，但请求还是发到同一个 endpoint。\n3. **DeepSeek 流式和非流式模型映射不一致**：非流式用 `deepseek-chat`，流式也用 `deepseek-chat`，但实际上应该都是 `deepseek-chat`（这是正确的）。But the bigger problem: The `deepseek-reasoner` is used for `logic` task type, but aiService.ts doesn't have a handler for `deepseek-reasoner`! When `aiModelsService.call('logic', ...)` is called, it selects `deepseek-reasoner` but then aiService only has cases for `deepseek` and `doubao-*`. So `deepseek-reasoner` would fall through to the error case, even though deepseek-reasoner IS a valid DeepSeek model and should be handled. Looking at line 75, it only checks for `deepseek` or `deepseek-chat`, so the logic task would fail silently.","thinkingSignature":"528adabc5c2f3b6c7ca20f848e7c77e28336ed6537c83ef22c306a87daffc633"},{"type":"text","text":"\n🔴 **P0：`aiService.ts` 不支持 `deepseek-reasoner` 模型。**\n\n`aiModels.ts` 的 `logic` 任务映射到 `deepseek-reasoner`，但 aiService 只处理 `deepseek` 和 `deepseek-chat`。\n\n---\n\n## 第 9 步：修复 aiService.ts 的模型覆盖\n\n**思考：** 补充 `deepseek-reasoner` 分支，复用 DeepSeek API，只是 model 名称不同。\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_3dd9jtyhzvvs_1","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"/mnt/d/aafuzhi/axs/src/main/aiService.ts","edits":[{"oldText":"    if (model === 'deepseek' || model === 'deepseek-chat') {","newText":"    if (model === 'deepseek' || model === 'deepseek-chat' || model === 'deepseek-reasoner') {"}]}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":78354,"output":485,"cacheRead":19262,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":98101,"cost":{"input":0.023506199999999998,"output":0.0005819999999999999,"cacheR