{"type":"message","id":"97d682db","parentId":"15d8cb0b","timestamp":"2026-04-14T08:18:32.836Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"✅ Renderer build successful. Now let me continue with the comprehensive review. Let me check for more potential issues.Let me check:1. backupService compressDir - is it handling all edge cases?\n2. aiService - are there any other missing model types?\n3. settings persistence\n4. factsStore appendFacts - is it correctly appending to existing YAML or overwriting?5. The preload TypeScript types - are they correct?","thinkingSignature":"c646764a0e9de5e687a7ea8da1ad6cb99cb72f0684741c0f4643cdb97b0d55f7"},{"type":"text","text":"✅ 编译通过。\n\n---\n\n## 第 11 步：审查 factsStore.appendFacts 是否会覆盖已有数据\n\n**思考：** `yaml.write` 是全量覆盖，但 appendFacts 是读取 → 修改 → 写回。并发写入会有竞态。但对于单用户 GUI 来说这不是问题。需要确认的是：写入格式是否保留原有 YAML 注释和结构。\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_t66uyjkf4tc0_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"node -e \"\n// 模拟 yaml.dump 输出，检查是否能保留原有结构\nconst yaml = require('/mnt/d/aafuzhi/axs/node_modules/js-yaml');\nconst obj = {\n  林枫: {\n    mbti: 'INTJ',\n    core_fear: '恐惧禁锢',\n    abilities: ['剑术天才', '重生记忆'],\n    relationships: { '青云子': '师父', '血魔': '仇敌' }\n  }\n};\nconsole.log(yaml.dump(obj, { lineWidth: -1 }));\n\""}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":86119,"output":303,"cacheRead":19262,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":105684,"cost":{"input":0.0258357,"output":0.0003636,"cacheRead":0.0011557199999999998,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.027355019999999997}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776154701397,"responseId":"062d2b4d5bfb70b28941eab81b45afdd"}}
