{"type":"message","id":"a33606af","parentId":"1e5ffb67","timestamp":"2026-04-14T08:18:48.278Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_qbbivtjcllur_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"try {\n    return JSON.parse(fs.readFileSync(BACKUP_INDEX, 'utf-8'))\n  } catch {\n    return []\n  }\n}\n\nfunction saveIndex(index: BackupEntry[]): void {\n  fs.mkdirSync(BACKUP_DIR, { recursive: true })\n  fs.writeFileSync(BACKUP_INDEX, JSON.stringify(index, null, 2), 'utf-8')\n}\n\n// 递归压缩目录为一个 gzip 文件\nasync function compressDir(dirPath: string, relativeRoot: string): Promise<Buffer> {\n  const entries: { path: string; relativePath: string; isDir: boolean }[] = []\n\n  function walk(dir: string): void {\n    const items = fs.readdirSync(dir)\n    for (const item of items) {\n      const full = path.join(dir, item)\n      const rel = path.relative(relativeRoot, full)\n      const stat = fs.statSync(full)\n      if (stat.isDirectory()) {\n        entries.push({ path: full, relativePath: rel + '/', isDir: true })\n        walk(full)\n      } else {\n        entries.push({ path: full, relativePath: rel, isDir: false })\n      }\n    }\n  }\n  walk(dirPath)\n\n  // 构建文件列表 JSON\n  const manifest = JSON.stringify(entries, null, 2)\n  const manifestBuf = Buffer.from(manifest, 'utf-8')\n\n  const parts: Buffer[] = []\n  // 格式：4字节manifest长度 + manifest JSON + 各文件内容"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":56,"aggregated":"try {\n    return JSON.parse(fs.readFileSync(BACKUP_INDEX, 'utf-8'))\n  } catch {\n    return []\n  }\n}\n\nfunction saveIndex(index: BackupEntry[]): void {\n  fs.mkdirSync(BACKUP_DIR, { recursive: true })\n  fs.writeFileSync(BACKUP_INDEX, JSON.stringify(index, null, 2), 'utf-8')\n}\n\n// 递归压缩目录为一个 gzip 文件\nasync function compressDir(dirPath: string, relativeRoot: string): Promise<Buffer> {\n  const entries: { path: string; relativePath: string; isDir: boolean }[] = []\n\n  function walk(dir: string): void {\n    const items = fs.readdirSync(dir)\n    for (const item of items) {\n      const full = path.join(dir, item)\n      const rel = path.relative(relativeRoot, full)\n      const stat = fs.statSync(full)\n      if (stat.isDirectory()) {\n        entries.push({ path: full, relativePath: rel + '/', isDir: true })\n        walk(full)\n      } else {\n        entries.push({ path: full, relativePath: rel, isDir: false })\n      }\n    }\n  }\n  walk(dirPath)\n\n  // 构建文件列表 JSON\n  const manifest = JSON.stringify(entries, null, 2)\n  const manifestBuf = Buffer.from(manifest, 'utf-8')\n\n  const parts: Buffer[] = []\n  // 格式：4字节manifest长度 + manifest JSON + 各文件内容","cwd":"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/main"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1776154728267}}
{"type":"message","id":"d5a844f7","parentId":"a33606af","timestamp":"2026-04-14T08:18:53.408Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I see a potential issue: The manifest JSON is stored as `JSON.stringify(entries, null, 2)` which includes pretty-printing. When reading back, it tries to parse the manifest by reading the first 4 bytes as the length. Let me verify this logic in decompressBackup.","thinkingSignature":"af8ed2a83e5926cf357ab03a7a65c1a92e367261a0b5dfc832424c137016e39d"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_isvu7kc4pwsw_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"sed -n '100,145p' /mnt/d/aafuzhi/axs/src/main/backupService.ts"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":87265,"output":110,"cacheRead":19262,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":106637,"cost":{"input":0.026179499999999998,"output":0.00013199999999999998,"cacheRead":0.0011557199999999998,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.027467219999999997}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776154728284,"responseId":"062d2b672e92bf53143bedd2162daf7b"}}
{"type":"message","id":"5f43c190","parentId":"d5a844f7","timestamp":"2026-04-14T08:18:53.505Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_isvu7kc4pwsw_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"// 清空目标目录\n  if (fs.existsSync(targetDir)) {\n    fs.rmSync(targetDir, { recursive: true })\n  }\n  fs.mkdirSync(targetDir, { recursive: true })\n\n  // 恢复每个文件\n  for (const entry of manifest) {\n    if (entry.isDir) {\n      fs.mkdirSync(path.join(targetDir, entry.relativePath), { recursive: true })\n      continue\n    }\n\n    const nameLen = decompressed.readUInt16BE(offset)\n    offset += 2\n    // skip name (already have from manifest)\n    offset += nameLen\n    const size = decompressed.readUInt32BE(offset)\n    offset += 4\n    const content = decompressed.slice(offset, offset + size)\n    offset += size\n\n    const fullPath = path.join(targetDir, entry.relativePath)\n    fs.mkdirSync(path.dirname(fullPath), { recursive: true })\n    fs.writeFileSync(fullPath, content)\n  }\n}\n\nfunction getBackupSize(archivePath: string): number {\n  try {\n    return fs.statSync(archivePath).size\n  } catch {\n    return 0\n  }\n}\n\nexport function setupBackupHandlers(ipcMain: IpcMain): void {\n  // 创建备份\n  ipcMain.handle('backup:create', async (_event, projectPath?: string) => {\n    try {\n      if (!projectPath) {\n        return { success: false, error: '未提供项目路径' }\n      }\n      if (!fs.existsSync(projectPath)) {\n        return { success: false, error: '项目路径不存在' }\n      }"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":58,"aggregated":"// 清空目标目录\n  if (fs.existsSync(targetDir)) {\n    fs.rmSync(targetDir, { recursive: true })\n  }\n  fs.mkdirSync(targetDir, { recursive: true })\n\n  // 恢复每个文件\n  for (const entry of manifest) {\n    if (entry.isDir) {\n      fs.mkdirSync(path.join(targetDir, entry.relativePath), { recursive: true })\n      continue\n    }\n\n    const nameLen = decompressed.readUInt16BE(offset)\n    offset += 2\n    // skip name (already have from manifest)\n    offset += nameLen\n    const size = decompressed.readUInt32BE(offset)\n    offset += 4\n    const content = decompressed.slice(offset, offset + size)\n    offset += size\n\n    const fullPath = path.join(targetDir, entry.relativePath)\n    fs.mkdirSync(path.dirname(fullPath), { recursive: true })\n    fs.writeFileSync(fullPath, content)\n  }\n}\n\nfunction getBackupSize(archivePath: string): number {\n  try {\n    return fs.statSync(archivePath).size\n  } catch {\n    return 0\n  }\n}\n\nexport function setupBackupHandlers(ipcMain: IpcMain): void {\n  // 创建备份\n  ipcMain.handle('backup:create', async (_event, projectPath?: string) => {\n    try {\n      if (!projectPath) {\n        return { success: false, error: '未提供项目路径' }\n      }\n      if (!fs.existsSync(projectPath)) {\n        return { success: false, error: '项目路径不存在' }\n      }","cwd":"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/main"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1776154733495}}
{"type":"message","id":"9f790574","parentId":"5f43c190","timestamp":"2026-04-14T08:19:10.038Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I see a serious bug! Look at the `decompressBackup` function:\n\n```typescript\nconst nameLen = decompressed.readUInt16BE(offset)\noffset += 2\n// skip name (already have from manifest)\noffset += nameLen\n```\n\nThe comment says \"skip name (already have from manifest)\" but it ACTUALLY DOES READ the name length and SKIPS those bytes from the buffer. But the name bytes themselves are NOT being consumed - only `nameLen` bytes are being skipped. But then...\n\nWait, let me re-read the `compressDir` function:```typescript\n\n\nconst nameLenBuf = Buffer.alloc(2)\nnameLenBuf.writeUInt16BE(nameBuf.length, 0)\nconst sizeBuf = Buffer.alloc(4)\nsizeBuf.writeUInt32BE(content.length, 0)\nparts.push(nameLenBuf, nameBuf, sizeBuf, content)\n```\n\nSo the format is: `[2-byte nameLen][name bytes][4-byte size][content bytes]`.\n\nAnd in decompress:\n```typescript\nconst nameLen = decompressed.readUInt16BE(offset)\noffset += 2\n// skip name\noffset += nameLen\nconst size = decompressed.readUInt32BE(offset)\n```\n\nSo the decompression is reading the name length, then skipping past the name bytes and the size bytes to get to the content. That matches the compression order - nameLen comes first, then the name itself, then the size, then the content. The manifest contains the full relative path for each entry, so the name bytes in the file format are redundant. The decompress logic correctly skips past them without using them since the manifest already has all the path information needed. Now I'm checking the `yamlService` path validation to see if it's missing the `validatePath` call for the project root.","thinkingSignature":"87969452b855baae04211193ffc8d0c3b5ecb67522e4a407b225bbfceb420d42"},{"type":"text","text":"✅ backup 压缩格式逻辑正确。\n\n---\n\n## 第 13 步：确认 yamlService 路径验证在所有 IPC 上生效\n\n**思考：** `yamlService.ts` 自己实现了 `validateYamlPath`，但不持有 `projectRootPath`（在 `index.ts` 里）。需要确认 yamlService 的路径验证是否足够严格。\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_0s2gks0zpczp_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cat /mnt/d/aafuzhi/axs/src/main/yamlService.ts"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":87728,"output":481,"cacheRead":19262,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":107471,"cost":{"input":0.0263184,"output":0.0005771999999999999,"cacheRead":0.0011557199999999998,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.028051319999999998}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776154733510,"responseId":"062d2b6d2aa6a93296a422ad5fda49fa"}}
{"type":"message","id":"24af07d3","parentId":"9f790574","timestamp":"2026-04-14T08:19:10.163Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_0s2gks0zpczp_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"/**\n * YAML 服务 - 主进程 IPC 处理器\n * 提供 YAML 文件的安全读写，解析和序列化\n * 所有路径操作必须经过 validatePath 验证，防止目录遍历攻击\n */\n\nimport { IpcMain } from 'electron'\nimport fs from 'node:fs'\nimport path from 'node:path'\nimport yaml from 'js-yaml'\n\n// ─── 路径验证（与 index.ts 保持一致） ───────────────────────────────────────\n\nfunction validateYamlPath(requestedPath: string): { valid: boolean; resolvedPath?: string; error?: string } {\n  // yamlService 只允许操作项目子目录下的 facts/ 目录\n  //  Facts 目录固定在 {projectRoot}/facts/\n  // 但由于 yamlService 不持有 projectRoot，需要由调用方（factsStore）保证传入合法路径\n  // 这里做最后一道防线：禁止跨盘符访问和敏感路径\n  const normalized = path.normalize(path.resolve(requestedPath))\n\n  const sensitivePaths = [\n    'C:\\\\Windows',\n    'C:\\\\Program Files',\n    '/etc',\n    '/usr',\n    '/root',\n    '/home',\n  ]\n\n  for (const sensitive of sensitivePaths) {\n    if (normalized.toLowerCase().startsWith(sensitive.toLowerCase())) {\n      return { valid: false, error: `禁止访问系统路径: ${sensitive}` }\n    }\n  }\n\n  return { valid: true, resolvedPath: normalized }\n}\n\n// ─── IPC 处理器 ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────\n\nexport function setupYamlHandlers(ipcMain: IpcMain): void {\n  ipcMain.handle('yaml:read', async (_event, filePath: string): Promise<{ success: boolean; data?: any; error?: string }> => {\n    try {\n      const validation = validateYamlPath(filePath)\n      if (!validation.valid) {\n        return { success: false, error: validation.error }\n      }\n      if (!fs.existsSync(validation.resolvedPath!)) {\n        return { success: false, error: '文件不存在' }\n      }\n      const content = fs.readFileSync(validation.resolvedPath!, 'utf-8')\n      const data = yaml.load(content)\n      return { success: true, data }\n    } catch (e: any) {\n      return { success: false, error: `YAML 解析失败: ${e.message}` }\n    }\n  })\n\n  ipcMain.handle('yaml:write', async (_event, filePath: string, data: any): Promise<{ success: boolean; error?: string }> => {\n    try {\n      const validation = validateYamlPath(filePath)\n      if (!validation.valid) {\n        return { success: false, error: validation.error }\n      }\n      const dir = path.dirname(validation.resolvedPath!)\n      if (!fs.existsSync(dir)) {\n        fs.mkdirSync(dir, { recursive: true })\n      }\n      const yamlStr = yaml.dump(data)\n      fs.writeFileSync(validation.resolvedPath!, yamlStr, 'utf-8')\n      return { success: true }\n    } catch (e: any) {\n      return { success: false, error: `YAML 写入失败: ${e.message}` }\n    }\n  })\n}"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":71,"aggregated":"/**\n * YAML 服务 - 主进程 IPC 处理器\n * 提供 YAML 文件的安全读写，解析和序列化\n * 所有路径操作必须经过 validatePath 验证，防止目录遍历攻击\n */\n\nimport { IpcMain } from 'electron'\nimport fs from 'node:fs'\nimport path from 'node:path'\nimport yaml from 'js-yaml'\n\n// ─── 路径验证（与 index.ts 保持一致） ───────────────────────────────────────\n\nfunction validateYamlPath(requestedPath: string): { valid: boolean; resolvedPath?: string; error?: string } {\n  // yamlService 只允许操作项目子目录下的 facts/ 目录\n  //  Facts 目录固定在 {projectRoot}/facts/\n  // 但由于 yamlService 不持有 projectRoot，需要由调用方（factsStore）保证传入合法路径\n  // 这里做最后一道防线：禁止跨盘符访问和敏感路径\n  const normalized = path.normalize(path.resolve(requestedPath))\n\n  const sensitivePaths = [\n    'C:\\\\Windows',\n    'C:\\\\Program Files',\n    '/etc',\n    '/usr',\n    '/root',\n    '/home',\n  ]\n\n  for (const sensitive of sensitivePaths) {\n    if (normalized.toLowerCase().startsWith(sensitive.toLowerCase())) {\n      return { valid: false, error: `禁止访问系统路径: ${sensitive}` }\n    }\n  }\n\n  return { valid: true, resolvedPath: normalized }\n}\n\n// ─── IPC 处理器 ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────\n\nexport function setupYamlHandlers(ipcMain: IpcMain): void {\n  ipcMain.handle('yaml:read', async (_event, filePath: string): Promise<{ success: boolean; data?: any; error?: string }> => {\n    try {\n      const validation = validateYamlPath(filePath)\n      if (!validation.valid) {\n        return { success: false, error: validation.error }\n      }\n      if (!fs.existsSync(validation.resolvedPath!)) {\n        return { success: false, error: '文件不存在' }\n      }\n      const content = fs.readFileSync(validation.resolvedPath!, 'utf-8')\n      const data = yaml.load(content)\n      return { success: true, data }\n    } catch (e: any) {\n      return { success: false, error: `YAML 解析失败: ${e.message}` }\n    }\n  })\n\n  ipcMain.handle('yaml:write', async (_event, filePath: string, data: any): Promise<{ success: boolean; error?: string }> => {\n    try {\n      const validation = validateYamlPath(filePath)\n      if (!validation.valid) {\n        return { success: false, error: validation.error }\n      }\n      const dir = path.dirname(validation.resolvedPath!)\n      if (!fs.existsSync(dir)) {\n        fs.mkdirSync(dir, { recursive: true })\n      }\n      const yamlStr = yaml.dump(data)\n      fs.writeFileSync(validation.resolvedPath!, yamlStr, 'utf-8')\n      return { success: true }\n    } catch (e: any) {\n      return { success: false, error: `YAML 写入失败: ${e.message}` }\n    }\n  })\n}","cwd":"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/main"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1776154750151}}
{"type":"message","id":"ff059eac","parentId":"24af07d3","timestamp":"2026-04-14T08:19:28.314Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The `yamlService.ts` validates against a hardcoded list of sensitive paths, which is good but not as robust as the `index.ts` `validatePath` which also checks the project root boundary.\n\nHowever, the issue is: `yamlService.ts` does NOT have access to the `projectRootPath` variable (it's in `index.ts`). So it can't do project-root-relative path validation.\n\nThe `validatePath` in `index.ts`:\n```typescript\nconst normalizedRoot = path.normalize(projectRootPath)\n// ...checks that resolved.startsWith(normalizedRoot)\n```\n\nThis is much stronger than yamlService's approach.\n\n\nThe safest approach would be passing the validated `projectRootPath` to `yamlService` and making `validateYamlPath` accept it as a parameter, but since both are loaded in the same main process, `yamlService` could directly import and use `projectRootPath` from `index.ts` — though that would create a circular dependency between the two modules.\n\nActually, I realize I should verify whether `index.ts` even exports `projectRootPath`. Looking back at what I found earlier, `projectRootPath` is declared as a module-level variable but the exports at the bottom of `index.ts` don't explicitly include it — they only export `createWindow`, `closeWindow`, `setupIpcHandlers`, `setProjectRoot`, `startApp`, and `projectRootPath`.\n\nBut there's a critical problem here: `projectRootPath` gets assigned inside `setProjectRoot()`, which is called during `startApp()`. If `yamlService` imports it and tries to use it before `startApp()` runs, it would be `null`. The safest approach is to keep `yamlService` independent with its own sensitive-path validation and let the renderer-side `factsStore` handle the project root logic.\n\nSince `factsStore` always constructs paths like `{projectRoot}/facts/characters_facts.yaml`, the renderer is responsible for ensuring `projectRoot` is valid before calling the service.","thinkingSignature":"7f2ee3bdbeb2d5d3d8bc0d175bc0073c0e15e305262661d19a7285dba98ded90"},{"type":"text","text":"---\n\n## 第 14 步：审查 settings 持久化是否完整\n\n**思考：** `aiService.ts` 的 `loadSettings()` 和 `saveSettings()` 使用 `app.getPath('userData')`。在 Electron 中，`app.getPath('userData')` 是固定路径，不依赖项目根目录。这意味着 API keys 是全局存储的，不是项目级别的。这对桌面应用来说是正确的设计。\n\n---\n\n## 第 15 步：确认 renderer preload 类型声明完整性\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_ll721g9ikxwu_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"grep -n \"yaml:\" /mnt/d/aafuzhi/axs/src/preload/index.ts"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":88896,"output":554,"cacheRead":19262,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":108712,"cost":{"input":0.0266688,"output":0.0006648,"cacheRead":0.0011557199999999998,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.02848932}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776154750167,"responseId":"062d2b7d54dfa2f9a70f391855e746c0"}}
