{"type":"message","id":"7b928b37","parentId":"dc5d61ca","timestamp":"2026-04-14T08:20:00.375Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now let me compile the comprehensive review findings into a structured summary.\n\nFindings:\n1. ✅ Renderer build: successful (only CSS warnings, no errors)\n2. ✅ FactsPanel: correctly uses `factsStore.getFacts()`\n3. ✅ Editor.tsx: clean, proper Monaco setup, cleanup correct\n4. ✅ AIToolsPanel: had missing save button bug → **FIXED** (added `handleSaveFacts` + save button)\n5. ✅ Dependencies: all type packages in devDependencies\n6. ⚠️ No renderer tsconfig.json → type errors only caught at runtime\n\n\n7. ✅ factExtractor: uses `factsStore.appendFacts()` correctly\n8. ✅ aiModels.ts: `deepseek-reasoner` not handled → **FIXED** (added support in aiService.ts)\n9. ✅ YAML serialization: correct round-trip\n10. ✅ backup compress/decompress: format is correct\n11. ✅ yamlService: has sensitive-path validation (but not project-root-relative)\n12. ⚠️ yamlService: doesn't have project root boundary check (but renderer passes project-relative paths)\n\nThe critical issues are the missing save button in AIToolsPanel and the unhandled `deepseek-reasoner` in aiModels—these are the ones that need immediate attention.","thinkingSignature":"3fd459833588daf480eea2e269320ddbd841165209442aab599fd150d2e64af4"},{"type":"text","text":"---\n\n## 全面评审完毕 — 结果汇总\n\n### 🔴 本轮发现并修复的 P0/P1 问题\n\n| # | 问题 | 严重性 | 修复状态 |\n|---|------|--------|---------|\n| 1 | `db/index.ts` 手写 YAML 解析器无法解析真实 facts 文件 | P0 | ✅ 已修复：重写为 IPC `yaml:read/write` |\n| 2 | `yamlService.ts` 无路径验证（路径遍历漏洞） | P0 | ✅ 已修复：敏感路径拦截 |\n| 3 | `backup:restore` 缺少目标路径验证 | P1 | ✅ 已修复：系统路径检查 |\n| 4 | `deepseek-reasoner` 模型未处理（logic 任务会失败） | P0 | ✅ 已修复：aiService.ts 添加分支 |\n| 5 | AIToolsPanel facts 提取后\"保存\"按钮缺失 | P1 | ✅ 已修复：添加 `handleSaveFacts` + 按钮 |\n\n### ⚠️ 已识别但未修复的架构问题\n\n| 问题 | 说明 | 影响 |\n|------|------|------|\n| renderer 无 tsconfig.json | Vite/esbuild 编译不做完整类型检查 | 类型错误