{"type":"message","id":"c30bf02f","parentId":"a86e3dd8","timestamp":"2026-04-14T08:36:50.715Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking me to continue the harsh, strict review and inspection of the project. They've already seen multiple rounds of review from me. Let me think about what else could be scrutinized:\n\nWhat hasn't been fully checked yet:\n1. The OutlineTree component - potential performance issues with deep directory traversal\n2. The Workbench component - initialization and state management\n3. The package.json scripts - are they all correct?\n4. The bin/* command line tools - need to verify each one actually works\n5. The relationship between my-novel-tools and the Electron app - is data shared?\n6. Memory-bank documentation - is it still accurate?\n7. Potential race conditions in factsStore\n8. Error handling completeness\n9. Testing the actual execution of all CLI tools end-to-end\n\nLet me do a comprehensive check of things that haven't been properly verified yet:\n1. Test ALL bin/* CLI tools actually work\n2. Check the package.json scripts\n3. Check OutlineTree for performance bugs\n4. Check for any untested edge cases\n5. Verify the relationship between the CLI and the Electron app data\n\nLet me start with testing all the CLI tools - this is critical because the user has been relying on these.\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n继续严格评审。这次重点检查之前未验证的 CLI 工具完整性和潜在边界问题。\n\n---\n\n## 第 1 步：逐一测试所有 CLI 工具执行\n\n**思考：** `bin/` 下有 13 个工具，之前只抽检了部分。需要全部验证是否能正常执行。\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"019d8b22c62e8867f73d1cfdc33058e8","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd /mnt/d/aafuzhi/axs/my-novel-tools\nfor tool in personality fear structure world-seed complement catharsis emotion template dialogue; do\n  echo \"=== $tool.js ===\"\n  timeout 10 node bin/${tool}.js INTJ 2>&1 | head -5\n  echo \"\"\ndone"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2