{"type":"message","id":"5c30fab2","parentId":"8d4d2fd6","timestamp":"2026-04-14T08:42:20.305Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Confirmed: `build-vector-index.js`, `generate-summary.js`, `generate-volume-summary.js` are NOT registered in package.json's `bin` field. They can only be run with `node bin/...` directly, not as `generate-summary ...` commands.\n\nAlso, `generate-chapter` IS registered. Let me verify the remaining ones.\n\nNow let me also verify that `generate-summary.js` and `generate-volume-summary.js` actually work (I tested them above with `node bin/...` and they did work, falling back to mock mode).\n\nActually, I already tested them above:\n- `generate-summary.js` ✅ - falls back to mock mode correctly  \n\n\n- `generate-volume-summary.js` ✅ - falls back to mock mode correctly\n\nNow I need to verify that `generate-chapter.js` is actually registered as a bin command.","thinkingSignature":"46f955a299cd1f9df5fb7606b9a705b41472a1449f4cbd2e91d73c797e917334"},{"type":"text","text":"`generate-summary` / `generate-volume-summary` / `build-vector-index` 这 3 个不在 `bin` 注册里，必须用 `node bin/generate-summary.js` 才能运行。\n\n---\n\n## 🔴 P1: `build-vector-index.js` 的依赖未声明，依赖父目录 node_modules\n\n`@xenova/transformers` 未在 `my-novel-tools/package.json` 中声明，是从父目录 `axs/node_modules/` 泄露过来的隐式依赖。\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_2z02hcpyfqf2_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"node -e \"\nconst path = require('path');\n// 模拟 my-novel-tools/bin/generate-summary.js 的模块解析\ntry {\n  const r = require.resolve('@xenova/transformers', { paths: ['/mnt/d/aafuzhi/axs/my-novel-tools'] });\n  console.log('✅ @xenova/transformers resolved to:', r);\n} catch(e) {\n  console.log('❌ 无法解析:', e.message);\n}\n\n// 模拟 vectorIndex.js 的模块解析\ntry {\n  const r2 = require.resolve('sharp', { paths: ['/mnt/d/aafuzhi/axs/my-novel-tools'] });\n  console.log('✅ sharp resolved to:', r2);\n} catch(e) {\n  console.log('❌ 无法解析 sharp:', e.message);\n}\n\""}}],"