{"type":"message","id":"7dc22f8f","parentId":"a5f50b40","timestamp":"2026-04-14T08:42:39.780Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Both `@xenova/transformers` and `sharp` are resolved from the parent `axs/node_modules/`. This is a fragile dependency - if someone runs `my-novel-tools` from a different location or removes the parent node_modules, these will stop working.\n\nAlso, `sharp` has native binaries that aren't properly installed (the Linux binary is missing). This will cause `build-vector-index.js` to fail whenever it's run.\n\nNow let me compile all the issues found and provide a complete report.\n\nAlso, let me quickly verify the `generate-summary.js` and `generate-volume-summary.js` work (I tested them above). \n\nI've already confirmed they work. Now I need to wrap up and give the user a full report of what I found.","thinkingSignature":"48ce1980631ffbe1a5ee19494c390d6fb907733cfde82631312c1a263ba8f214"},{"type":"text","text":"---\n\n## 评审汇总：CLI 工具深度审查\n\n### ✅ 已验证正常工作的工具（10/13）\n\n| 工具 | 状态 |\n|------|------|\n| personality.js | ✅ 正常 |\n| fear.js | ✅ 正常（接受认知功能如 Se/Ni） |\n| structure.js | ✅ 正常 |\n| world-seed.js | ✅ 正常（接受 genre + fear） |\n| complement.js | ✅ 正常 |\n| catharsis.js | ✅ 正常 |\n| emotion.js | ✅ 正常 |\n| template.js | ✅ 正常（接受 climax/standard/transition...） |\n| dialogue.js | ✅ 正常 |\n| generate-chapter.js | ✅ 正常（fallback 模拟模式正常） |\n| generate-summary.js | ✅ 正常 |\n| generate-volume-summary.js | ✅ 正常 |\n\n### 🔴 发现的问题\n\n| # | 问题 | 严重性 |\n|---|------|--------|\n| 1 | `package.json` bin 注册缺少 3 个工具：`build-vector-index`、`generate-summary`、`generate-volume-summary` | P0 |\n| 2 | `@xenova/transformers` 和 `sharp` 未在 `my-novel-tools/package.json` 声明，依赖父目录 `axs/node_modules/` 的隐式传递依赖 | P0 |\n| 3 | `build-vector-index.js` 运行时 sharp 原生二进制损坏（WSL 平台），无法构建向量索引 | P1 |\n| 4 | `sharp` native module 在 WSL 环境缺失，`build-vector-index` 不可用 | P1 |\n\n### 建议修复\n\n**对于问题 1**（bin 注册），需要补充：\n\n```json\n{\n  \"bin\": {\n    \"personality\": \"./bin/personality.js\",\n    \"generate-summary\": \"./bin/generate-summary.js\",\n    \"generate-volume-summary\": \"./bin/generate-volume-summary.js\",\n    \"build-vector-index\": \"./bin/build-vector-index.js\"\n    // ... 其余9个\n  }\n}\n```\n\n**对于问题 2**（依赖声明），需要在 `my-novel-tools/package.json` 中添加：\n\n```json\n\"dependencies\": {\n  \"@xenova/transformers\": \"^2.17.0\"\n}\n```\n\n或者移除 `vectorIndex.js` 中对 `@xenova/transformers` 的隐式依赖，改为可选特性。\n\n---\n\n需要我修复这些问题吗？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":93497,"output":654,"cacheRead":19262,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":113413,"cost":{"input":0.0280491,"output":0.0007848,"cacheRead":0.0011557199999999998,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.029989619999999998}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776156140631,"responseId":"062d30ec5380059f7fb1ae46ebec5612"}}
