{"type":"message","id":"d332d94d","parentId":"b3cb9772","timestamp":"2026-04-14T09:34:02.503Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"This is a UX bug - the `--volume-chapters` option defaults to 30, but the five-volume structure would have 6 chapters per volume for 30 total chapters. This means users who don't read the help would get misleading output.\n\nLet me document this as a P1 UX issue.\n\nNow let me check a few more things:1. Check if the IPC channel count is still correct\n2. Check for any obvious issues in the remaining files\n\nLet me also check the facts flow more carefully.","thinkingSignature":"78fb8ff336480a908f2cf8676e52a8b6205dffd9dacf226774876ce5bcdd98a0"},{"type":"text","text":"🔴 **发现 P1 UX bug：`catharsis.js` 默认 `--volume-chapters 30`，用户运行 `catharsis.js 30` 得出\"每卷30章\"的误导输出。**\n\n---\n\n## 第 3 步：facts 数据流端到端验证\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_gtcb9o08q57w_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"echo \"=== facts 文件现状 ===\"\nls /mnt/d/aafuzhi/axs/my-novel/facts/\necho \"\"\necho \"=== characters_facts 角色数 ===\"\nnode -e \"const yaml=require('/mnt/d/aafuzhi/axs/my-novel-tools/node_modules/js-yaml'); const d=yaml.load(require('fs').readFileSync('/mnt/d/aafuzhi/axs/my-novel/facts/characters_facts.yaml','utf8')); console.log('角色:', Object.keys(d).join(', '));\""}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":102453,"output":305,"cacheRead":19262,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":122020,"cost":{"input":0.0307359,"output":0.000366,"cacheRead":0.0011557199999999998,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.03225762}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776159230347,"responseId":"062d3cfe35628d4be7bdd86787aca0cc"}}
