{"type":"message","id":"b47ad820","parentId":"59869a36","timestamp":"2026-04-14T09:35:08.603Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The problem is clear: the default `--volume-chapters` is 30, but the user typically specifies 30 as total chapters. So the calculation `chapter % volumeChapters === 0` would only trigger at chapter 30, not at chapters 6, 12, 18, 24.\n\nThe fix: change the default to `6` (since the five-volume template has 5 volumes, 30/5 = 6). But this assumes a five-volume structure. Actually, looking at the structure-templates.json, the five-volume template doesn't even have a `chapters` field! So the catharsis tool has no way to know the volume structure unless the user specifies `--volume-chapters`.\n \nThe most straightforward solution would be to infer volume-chapters from the structure template if it existed, but since that field isn't there, I should just change the default to `6` as a more sensible starting point for a 30-chapter five-volume work.","thinkingSignature":"98e218c6974f1d59e01355d43874eb4f8f93f25505a62f7431e9eaef5866212c"},{"type":"text","text":"🔴 **P1：`catharsis.js` 默认值 `30` 导致误导输出。** 修复：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_rnfz320hr6bz_1","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"/mnt/d/aafuzhi/axs/my-novel-tools/bin/catharsis.js","edits":[{"oldText":"  .option('-v, --volume-chapters <number>', '每卷章节数（用于计算大爽点）', parseInt, 30)","newText":"  .option('-v, --volume-chapters <number>', '每卷章节数（用于计算大爽点爆发位置），五卷结构默认6（即30章÷5卷）', parseInt, 6)"}]}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":104997,"output":365,"cacheRead":19262,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":124624,"cost":{"input":0.031499099999999995,"output":0.00043799999999999997,"cacheRead":0.0011557199999999998,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.033092819999999995}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776159295571,"responseId":"062d3d3fd1e3688a123883928782e5cd"}}
