{"type":"message","id":"36d43e72","parentId":"addd5d14","timestamp":"2026-04-14T09:40:03.845Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I have actual type errors. These are real issues that have been hidden until now. Let me prioritize:\n\n1. **`window.electronAPI` type not found** - The preload declares `window.electronAPI` but the renderer tsconfig doesn't know about it. I need to add a type declaration file for the renderer.2. **`path` module in OutlineTree.tsx** - Node.js `path` is used directly in a renderer file. This won't work in the browser unless it's bundled correctly.3. **`NodeJS.Timeout` in Workbench.tsx** - Needs `@types/node`4. \n\n**`OutlineTree.tsx` Ant Design `onSelect/onExpand` type mismatch** - The event handlers have incompatible signatures with what Ant Design expects. The renderer's TypeScript configuration doesn't have `node` in its type definitions, which is why it's complaining about the `path` module in OutlineTree.tsx. The real issue is that `window.electronAPI` isn't being recognized because the type declaration file from the preload script isn't accessible to the renderer process, and there's also a mismatch with how `NodeJS.Timeout` is being used versus what the DOM timeout type should be. I need to create a proper type declaration file for `window.electronAPI` and reference it in the renderer's tsconfig, while also fixing the `path` module issue by either removing it from OutlineTree or properly bundling it, and correcting the type definitions for the Ant Design event handlers.","thinkingSignature":"58cee91463ae9ea28e71b0762d1bb5e1efcb5ad5270b38c1da90e66c7152ed7d"},{"type":"text","text":"🔴 **发现大量隐藏的类型错误。** renderer 无 tsconfig 导致这些问题一直未暴露。\n\n---\n\n## 第 2 步：修复 renderer 类型错误\n\n**思考：** 错误分三类：① `window.electronAPI` 类型未声明 ② `path` 模块在 browser 环境不可用 ③ Ant Design Tree `onSelect` 类型不兼容。按优先级逐一修复。\n\n**① 创建 `window.electronAPI` 类型声明：**\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_4z2atkc1xhm0_1","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"/mnt/d/aafuzhi/axs/src/renderer/src/types/electron.d.ts","content":"/**\n * window.electronAPI 类型声明\n * 与 src/preload/index.ts 的 ElectronAPI 类型保持同步\n */\n\nexport interface ElectronAPI {\n  // 对话框\n  openDirectory: () => Promise<string | undefined>\n\n  // 文件系统 - 读取操作\n  readFile: (filePath: string) => Promise<{ success: boolean; content?: string; error?: string }>\n  exists: (filePath: string) => Promise<boolean>\n  readdir: (dirPath: string) => Promise<Array<{ name: string; isDirectory: boolean; isFile: boolean }>>\n\n  // 文件系统 - 写入操作\n  writeFile: (filePath: string, content: string) => Promise<{ success: boolean; error?: string }>\n  mkdir: (dirPath: string) => Promise<{ success: boolean; error?: string }>\n\n  // 文件系统 - 删除操作\n  unlink: (filePath: string) => Promise<{ success: boolean; error?: string }>\n  rmdir: (dirPath: string, options?: { recursive?: boolean }) => Promise<{ success: boolean; error?: string }>\n  remove: (targetPath: string) => Promise<{ success: boolean; error?: string }>\n  deleteFile: (filePath: string) => Promise<{ success: boolean; error?: string }>\n  deleteDirectory: (dirPath: string) => Promise<{ success: boolean; error?: string }>\n  renameFile: (oldPath: string, newPath: string) => Promise<{ success: boolean; error?: string }>\n\n  // 系统\n  openPath: (path: string) => Promise<string>\n  getProjectRoot: () => Promise<string | null>\n\n  // 文件监听\n  fsWatch: (dirPath?: string) => Promise<{ success: boolean; path?: string; error?: string }>\n  fsUnwatch: () => Promise<{ success: boolean; error?: string }>\n  onFsChange: (callback: (data: { type: string; fileName: string; path: string }) => void) => () => void\n\n  // 安全存储\n  safeStorage: {\n    encrypt: (plainText: string) => Promise<{ success: boolean; data?: Buffer; error?: string }>\n    decrypt: (encrypted: Buffer) => Promise<{ success: boolean; data?: string; error?: string }>\n    isAvailable: () => Promise<{ success: boolean; available?: boolean; error?: string }>\n  }\n\n  // YAML 服务\n  yaml: {\n    read: (filePath: string) => Promise<{ success: boolean; data?: unknown; error?: string }>\n    write: (filePath: string, data: unknown) => Promise<{ success: boolean; error?: string }>\n  }\n\n  // AI 服务\n  ai: {\n    saveApiKey: (service: string, apiKey: string) => Promise<{ success: boolean; error?: string }>\n    isConfigured: (service: string) => Promise<{ success: boolean; configured?: boolean; error?: string }>\n    getConfiguredServices: () => Promise<{ success: boolean; services?: string[]; error?: string }>\n    call: (prompt: string, options?: Record<string, unknown>) => Promise<{ success: boolean; content?: string; error?: string }>\n    stream: (prompt: string, options?: Record<string, unknown>) => Promise<{ success: boolean; error?: string }>\n    onStreamChunk: (callback: (chunk: { content: string; done: boolean; reasoning?: string }) => void) => () => void\n    onStreamError: (callback: (error: string) => void) => () => void\n    testConnection: (service: string) => Promise<{ success: boolean; result?: boolean; error?: string }>\n    saveSetting: (key: string, value: unknown) => Promise<{ success: boolean; error?: string }>\n    getSetting: (key: string, defaultValue?: unknown) => Promise<{ success: boolean; value?: unknown; error?: string }>\n  }\n\n  // 备份服务\n  backup: {\n    create: () => Promise<{ success: boolean; backupPath?: string; error?: string }>\n    list: () => Promise<{ success: boolean; backups?: Array<{ name: string; path: string; date: string; size: number }>; error?: string }>\n    restore: (backupPath: string, targetPath?: string) => Promise<{ success: boolean; error?: string }>\n    delete: (backupPath: string) => Promise<{ success: boolean; error?: string }>\n  }\n}\n\ndeclare global {\n  interface Window {\n    electronAPI: ElectronAPI\n  }\n}\n"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":110130,"output":1480,"cacheRead":19262,"cacheWrite":