{"type":"message","id":"1abc76e0","parentId":"827d087b","timestamp":"2026-04-14T11:05:27.289Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now let me check if electron-builder is needed for running the app in dev mode. In development mode, electron just loads the compiled main process and the vite dev server.\n\nLet me give the user a clear answer about how to start the application.","thinkingSignature":"500c015b3463de38220c6adec0473f12a1c23d6a8429f4a9b5c8ef6740a70566"},{"type":"text","text":"---\n\n## 启动方式\n\n### 方式一：Electron 桌面应用（GUI）\n\n**第一步：编译 Electron 主进程**\n```bash\ncd D:\\aafuzhi\\axs\nnpm run build:electron\n```\n\n**第二步：启动（两个终端）**\n\n**终端 1 — 前端热重载开发服务器：**\n```bash\nnpm run dev:renderer\n```\n启动后访问 `http://localhost:5173`\n\n**终端 2 — Electron 主进程：**\n```bash\nnpm run dev:electron\n```\n\n**或者一键启动（需先安装 `concurrently`）：**\n```bash\nnpm run dev\n```\n\n---\n\n### 方式二：命令行工具（无需 Electron）\n\n完全独立，不依赖 GUI：\n\n```bash\ncd D:\\aafuzhi\\axs\\my-novel-tools\n\n# 生成章节草稿\nnode bin/generate-chapter.js -p ../my-novel -c 1\n\n# 规划小说结构\nnode bin/structure.js 30\n\n# 生成世界观\nnode bin/world-seed.js fantasy Ni\n\n# 生成爽点规划\nnode bin/catharsis.js 30\n```\n\n---\n\n### 方式三：自动化全面检查\n\n```bash\nbash /mnt/d/aafuzhi/axs/auto-review.sh\n```\n\n---\n\n**当前状态：**\n- TypeScript 编译 ✅\n- renderer 构建 ✅\n- 13个 CLI 工具 ✅\n- IPC 链路 ✅\n\nElectron GUI 可以启动，但需要确保 `electron` 包已安装（npm 正在后台安装）。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":128180,"output":374,"cacheRead":19262,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":147816,"cost":{"input":0.038453999999999995,"output":0.00044879999999999996,"cacheRead":0.0011557199999999998,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.04005851999999999}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776164714317,"responseId":"062d526a3733225e8bff1d1c28083d9e"}}
