{"type":"message","id":"166a7870","parentId":"94f83bd0","timestamp":"2026-04-14T12:21:50.492Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is saying the app was modified/brought back with many bugs. I need to investigate what happened. Let me think about what could have gone wrong.\n\nLooking at the session history, we made many changes:\n1. Fixed preload path in main/index.ts\n2. Fixed electron-builder config (removed icons, added npmRebuild: false, etc.)\n3. Fixed tsconfig.main.json (removed composite)\n4. Fixed various TypeScript errors in renderer components\n5. Created types/electron.d.ts\n6. Created types/css.d.ts\n7. Fixed facts YAML 青云子 mbti\n\n\n8. Removed icon requirements from electron-builder config\n\nNow the user says it's full of bugs and面目全非 - the original UI might have been significantly altered. I should check the source files to see what actually changed, particularly in the renderer components and electron-builder configuration, since that's likely where the damage occurred.","thinkingSignature":"66084bcefc7d243236b01a9789f013a2d69306f12c2ff1c8926107d67367365b"},{"type":"text","text":"我需要检查都改了什么导致出问题。让我看源码对比：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_qkjqyspfkozg_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"echo \"=== 检查OutlineTree.tsx当前状态 ===\"\nhead -30 /mnt/d/aafuzhi/axs/src/renderer/src/components/OutlineTree.tsx\n\necho \"\"\necho \"=== 检查AIToolsPanel.tsx ===\"\nhead -30 /mnt/d/aafuzhi/axs/src/renderer/src/components/AIToolsPanel.tsx\n\necho \"\"\necho \"=== 检查electron-builder配置 ===\"\ngrep -A 20 '\"build\"' /mnt/d/aafuzhi/axs/package.json | head -25"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":54,"output":333,"cacheRead":95636,"cacheWrite":112,"totalTokens":96135,"cost":{"input":0.0000162,"output":0.00039959999999999996,"cacheRead":0.005738159999999999,"cacheWrite":0.000042000000000000004,"total":0.0061959599999999995}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":177616